</node>
<node id="Tòa án">
  <data key="d0">Tòa án</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tòa án, which refers to the court system in Vietnam, plays a crucial role in the judicial system. It is responsible for making decisions on a wide range of legal matters, including the use of images, missing persons, divorce, and declaring death. Tòa án acts as a legal authority that respects and protects the civil rights of individuals and legal entities. It manages the assets of a missing person and can declare a person missing. Additionally, Tòa án makes decisions regarding the rights and responsibilities of guardians and can appoint a guardian in case of disputes or if there is no natural guardian.

Tòa án resolves civil cases and civil matters to protect rights and legal interests. It is the judicial body responsible for declaring a person dead and for revoking such a declaration. It also has the authority to declare civil transactions as invalid and recognize the validity of certain civil transactions. Tòa án makes decisions regarding legal matters, such as declaring civil transactions invalid or designating legal representatives. It is an organization that has the authority to designate legal representatives in various circumstances and makes decisions regarding the division of shared property. Furthermore, Tòa án makes decisions regarding the handling of assets to fulfill the obligations of the owner. It can be requested to enforce the cessation of infringement and restoration of the original state of the property. Tòa án resolves disputes and enforces the terms of contracts. It can decide on the modification or termination of a contract in the event of a fundamental change in circumstances. Tòa án is the court that resolves contract disputes and is where legal representatives can represent the company.

Tòa án can extend the time limit for dividing an estate if it affects the family's livelihood. It is the court that can issue decisions affecting business registration content and is responsible for making decisions that can lead to changes in the content of the Certificate of Business Registration. Tòa án is the judicial body that declares a member missing or incapacitated and issues decisions regarding the cessation of business activities. It can also issue restrictions on individuals' ability to hold positions or engage in certain activities and can make decisions regarding the prohibition of individuals or entities from certain activities or businesses. Tòa án is a judicial body that can make decisions regarding the validity of company resolutions and the transfer of shares. It is responsible for hearing and deciding legal cases related to the company's management and operations, including the validity of resolutions passed by the Đại hội đồng cổ đông. Shareholders can approach Tòa án to review and potentially annul a resolution of the General Shareholders' Meeting. Tòa án also has authority over arbitration activities and can be appealed to for resolving disputes if the arbitration agreement is deemed invalid or unenforceable. It can issue a decision that leads to the dissolution of a business and can make decisions regarding the revocation of business registration certificates. Tòa án can be requested to summon witnesses and apply emergency measures and can make decisions regarding the jurisdiction of disputes.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa án is the court system responsible for enforcing and reviewing arbitration decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa án is an organization where a person can file a lawsuit for compensation if they are damaged by the application of emergency measures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-985db81e6c3d846511cb280c2983fbf0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-308c6d17c5232c16366d8d919aa0033c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-40ff7c22fcf50ef4a68ba24e88d00b7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10d3e6bb3412e6c6eab3d00101010d92&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fef2e18615af027f8385abdb8209870&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ce4f076c1ad11637bf7e2f3ae95048&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-482a66c12f2040cbc0eabb425e1b6d97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737848ae2370b96df322ed1b985e715f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-053b8a5c1f69c52703201366343dafa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32dad3b53fda840a78aa833f5592a4d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8a3f543a1762069fe562fe6a382e1b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd76a1e6d7896b3bdcaa4bbcae2b9dea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dbdbb74ad11a83bf1856f95ecdfa309&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7934cedd8a058c40a35091be7e3f1c17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b47a7db90a1e526f1797874efef64872</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853990</data>
