<node id="Cơ Quan Nhà Nước Có Thẩm Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Cơ Quan Nhà Nước Có Thẩm Quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">An authorized government agency that can make decisions regarding the examination of a deceased body.&lt;SEP&gt;Authorized government agency where guardianship must be registered.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ Quan Nhà Nước Có Thẩm Quyền refers to government authorities with the power to make decisions regarding the handling of assets and the termination of ownership rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ Quan Nhà Nước Có Thẩm Quyền refers to the government authority with the power to make decisions regarding property boundaries.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ Quan Nhà Nước Có Thẩm Quyền is an authoritative government body that sets regulations for asset quality, pricing, and payment methods.&lt;SEP&gt;An authorized government agency to which property should be handed over if the rightful owner cannot be found.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-053b8a5c1f69c52703201366343dafa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-931c1ae4f95c0b01df5de17931b38de9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4623833cd0cb1b86833b9050e09612fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-821c3a34361b8add641406062fd4a10e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851194</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tòa Án">
  <data key="d0">Tòa Án</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tòa Án is a judicial body in Vietnam responsible for legal proceedings and decisions. It serves as a court that can rule on various matters, including the protection of an individual's reputation and dignity, the appointment of guardians and supervisors, and disputes regarding pathways and drainage systems. Tòa Án plays a crucial role in the Vietnamese legal system by providing a framework for resolving a wide range of legal disputes and ensuring justice is served.

Tòa Án also resolves disputes related to collateral and the interpretation of a will. It has the authority to declare a person dead and to designate legal representatives to participate in legal proceedings. In cases where the division of an estate affects the living conditions of the surviving spouse or family, Tòa Án may be involved in determining the division. Additionally, Tòa Án can be requested to invalidate decisions made by the Hội Đồng Thành Viên if they do not comply with the law or the company's charter. The court also has the authority to prohibit individuals from practicing certain professions or engaging in specific business activities.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa Án is the court that can issue a judgment affecting the transfer of private bonds.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa Án is the court that can be requested by shareholders to stop or revoke resolutions or decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa Án is a judicial body that can be requested to invalidate a resolution of the Đại Hội Đồng Cổ Đông.&lt;SEP&gt;The court has the authority to prohibit an owner of a private enterprise from practicing or engaging in certain activities within the scope of the business.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa Án is the court that has the authority to apply, change, or cancel emergency measures.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa Án is the court where the arbitration decision can be registered.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651dc401f3963fbef4dfe8d51ab78119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c073500583c9779361c25123a562132&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63e06b29bf3043507cfbd43beb81a47f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b5f857bd7e099346e71679265152a98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c152b6a16d5764e941499e3920fc0f1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71c1c580c8f92c3838ab0f997647d588&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65946ae20fedf99884e4b9e9ee2eea91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-444a844ae4151849d71498d312b5d52d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a95c0aafb09aeaffa31c143eaf83c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d59be88d8f39c9fce708d8b3f0c8014&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a36e099bae803eeaad0a5160e83464d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6520e05120076623f2042182e932b3ec</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854008</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
