</node>
<node id="Cá Nhân">
  <data key="d0">Cá Nhân</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">An individual whose dignity, reputation, and honor are protected by law.&lt;SEP&gt;Cá Nhân refers to individuals who can initiate the establishment of a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-846633705870effa2d882763f1693f90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bộ Luật">
  <data key="d0">Bộ Luật</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">A legal document that outlines the rights and regulations concerning the examination of deceased bodies and the protection of individual rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Bộ Luật refers to the legal code that defines the conditions for establishing and terminating ownership rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Bộ Luật refers to the legal code that includes provisions for interest rates on delayed payments.&lt;SEP&gt;Bộ Luật is the legal code that includes provisions on the validity and execution of contracts.&lt;SEP&gt;Bộ Luật is the legal code that governs the rights and obligations of cooperative members and the conditions for the operation and dissolution of the cooperative.&lt;SEP&gt;The legal code that outlines the regulations and responsibilities regarding the possession, use, and return of property.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63e06b29bf3043507cfbd43beb81a47f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63bea5bd12d1af991f494c7882f65825&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-821c3a34361b8add641406062fd4a10e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851194</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
