</node>
<node id="Cha">
  <data key="d0">Cha</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Father, who can give consent for the examination of a deceased body if the deceased did not provide prior consent.&lt;SEP&gt;A father who may become a guardian if his child has lost civil capacity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849064</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Mẹ">
  <data key="d0">Mẹ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Mother, who can give consent for the examination of a deceased body if the deceased did not provide prior consent.&lt;SEP&gt;A mother who may become a guardian if her child has lost civil capacity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849064</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vợ">
  <data key="d0">Vợ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Wife, who can give consent for the examination of a deceased body if the deceased did not provide prior consent.&lt;SEP&gt;A wife who may become a guardian if her husband has lost civil capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Wife is a person with a family relationship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chồng">
  <data key="d0">Chồng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Husband, who can give consent for the examination of a deceased body if the deceased did not provide prior consent.&lt;SEP&gt;A husband who may become a guardian if his wife has lost civil capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Husband is a person with a family relationship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Con Thành Niên">
  <data key="d0">Con Thành Niên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Adult child, who can give consent for the examination of a deceased body if the deceased did not provide prior consent.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848901</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Giám Hộ">
  <data key="d0">Người Giám Hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Guardian, who can give consent for the examination of a deceased body if the deceased did not provide prior consent.&lt;SEP&gt;Individuals or legal entities appointed to care for and protect the rights and interests of those under guardianship.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Giám Hộ is a person appointed to oversee and manage the affairs of a person who lacks full legal capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Giám Hộ refers to individuals who can act as guardians and must meet certain conditions to do so.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba16bb9ed3be84682d4bd14bebf5eaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651dc401f3963fbef4dfe8d51ab78119</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849023</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người vắng mặt">
  <data key="d0">Người vắng mặt</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người vắng mặt refers to a person who has been missing for a certain period of time.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10d3e6bb3412e6c6eab3d00101010d92</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người có quyền, lợi ích liên quan">
  <data key="d0">Người có quyền, lợi ích liên quan</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người có quyền, lợi ích liên quan refers to individuals who have rights or interests related to the missing person.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10d3e6bb3412e6c6eab3d00101010d92</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quản lý tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Quản lý tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quản lý tài sản refers to the management of assets belonging to a missing person.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10d3e6bb3412e6c6eab3d00101010d92</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tuyên bố mất tích">
  <data key="d0">Tuyên bố mất tích</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Tuyên bố mất tích is the declaration of a person as missing after they have been absent for two years.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10d3e6bb3412e6c6eab3d00101010d92</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bộ luật này">
  <data key="d0">Bộ luật này</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bộ luật này refers to the legal code being discussed, which encompasses a wide range of provisions and regulations. This Civil Code defines the legal status, legal standards for behavior, rights, and obligations of individuals and legal entities in civil relations. It includes provisions for managing the assets of a missing person, the application of time limits, and the formation of legal entities. Additionally, Bộ luật này covers shared property ownership and management, and it contains specific provisions such as Điều 219, Điều 220, and others. The legal document also includes regulations and rules related to collateral and its management, providing a comprehensive framework for various civil and legal matters.&lt;SEP&gt;Bộ luật này refers to the legal code that governs the conditions for contract termination and the responsibilities of the parties involved.&lt;SEP&gt;This law refers to the legal document containing the articles and clauses related to performing work without authorization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10d3e6bb3412e6c6eab3d00101010d92&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c55b09e479fc060292314cb4f8f8302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ce4f076c1ad11637bf7e2f3ae95048&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4a95c6c117e21012baec10d4e1fb78c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8a3f543a1762069fe562fe6a382e1b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-35e5b9d9646a1753edafbdf0516edae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd76a1e6d7896b3bdcaa4bbcae2b9dea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người thân thích">
  <data key="d0">Người thân thích</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người thân thích refers to close relatives of the missing person who may be appointed to manage the missing person's assets.&lt;SEP&gt;The close relative of the person for whom the work is performed may be informed if the person performing the work without authorization cannot continue the work.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10d3e6bb3412e6c6eab3d00101010d92&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Được Giám Hộ">
  <data key="d0">Người Được Giám Hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">People who are under guardianship, including minors without parents, individuals with cognitive or behavioral difficulties, and those with legal disabilities.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Được Giám Hộ is a person who lacks full legal capacity and is under the supervision of a Guardian.&lt;SEP&gt;Người được giám hộ refers to individuals under guardianship, whose place of residence is typically determined by their guardian.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Được Giám Hộ refers to individuals who are under guardianship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-846633705870effa2d882763f1693f90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651dc401f3963fbef4dfe8d51ab78119</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849023</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nơi Cư Trú">
  <data key="d0">Nơi Cư Trú</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The place of residence for individuals, including military personnel, itinerant workers, and spouses.&lt;SEP&gt;Nơi cư trú refers to the place where an individual resides and is legally recognized as their residence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-846633705870effa2d882763f1693f90</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848981</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quân Nhân">
  <data key="d0">Quân Nhân</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Military personnel whose place of residence is the location where their unit is stationed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848936</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vợ, Chồng">
  <data key="d0">Vợ, Chồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Spouses whose place of residence is where they commonly live together.&lt;SEP&gt;Vợ, chồng refers to spouses, whose place of residence is typically determined by their shared living arrangements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-846633705870effa2d882763f1693f90</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848981</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Làm Nghề Lưu Động">
  <data key="d0">Người Làm Nghề Lưu Động</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Itinerant workers whose place of residence is the location where their vessel or mobile equipment is registered.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848936</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ủy Ban Nhân Dân Cấp Xã">
  <data key="d0">Ủy Ban Nhân Dân Cấp Xã</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Local People's Committee that appoints guardians.&lt;SEP&gt;Ủy Ban Nhân Dân Cấp Xã is a local administrative body responsible for managing community affairs.&lt;SEP&gt;Ủy Ban Nhân Dân Cấp Xã is the local government body that appoints supervisors if no close relatives are available.&lt;SEP&gt;Ủy Ban Nhân Dân Cấp Xã is a local government body responsible for handling discovered property or assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Ủy Ban Nhân Dân Cấp Xã is a local government body that can authenticate and witness the signing of a di chúc.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651dc401f3963fbef4dfe8d51ab78119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-abefb366f0615b56504281fccf7e1528&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a522f9aff4b603ac455ec99a8440d150</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851182</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 44">
  <data key="d0">Điều 44</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 44 of the law specifies the place of residence for military personnel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848936</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 45">
  <data key="d0">Điều 45</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 45 of the law specifies the place of residence for itinerant workers.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều  45 is a legal provision that outlines the authority of the arbitration board to verify facts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-868a62477b36c9e43bd19ac6e811469e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854018</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 46">
  <data key="d0">Điều 46</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Article  46 of the law defines guardianship and the responsibilities of guardians.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều  46 is a legal provision that outlines the authority of the arbitration board to gather evidence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-868a62477b36c9e43bd19ac6e811469e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854018</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 47">
  <data key="d0">Điều 47</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 47 of the law lists the categories of people who are under guardianship.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 47 of the law, which outlines the rules for capital contribution and issuance of capital contribution certificates.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851722</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 48">
  <data key="d0">Điều 48</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 48 of the law specifies the conditions for individuals or legal entities to be appointed as guardians.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 48 is a regulation that outlines the requirements for maintaining the Sổ Đăng Ký Thành Viên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851802</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 49">
  <data key="d0">Điều 49</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 49 of the law outlines the conditions for individuals to be eligible to serve as guardians.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều  49 is a regulation that outlines the rights of members of the Hội Đồng Thành Viên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab2df971c594abe37164d58e7533c291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851802</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cơ Quan Cử, Chỉ Định Người Giám Hộ">
  <data key="d0">Cơ Quan Cử, Chỉ Định Người Giám Hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ Quan Cử, Chỉ Định Người Giám Hộ is an organization responsible for appointing and designating Guardians.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848943</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Giám Sát Việc Giám Hộ">
  <data key="d0">Người Giám Sát Việc Giám Hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Giám Sát Việc Giám Hộ is a person responsible for overseeing the actions of the Guardian.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Giám Sát Việc Giám Hộ refers to individuals or legal entities appointed to supervise the guardianship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651dc401f3963fbef4dfe8d51ab78119</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849023</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chuyển Giao Giám Hộ">
  <data key="d0">Chuyển Giao Giám Hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Chuyển Giao Giám Hộ is the process of transferring guardianship from one Guardian to another.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848943</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chấm Dứt Việc Giám Hộ">
  <data key="d0">Chấm Dứt Việc Giám Hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">#|&gt;Chấm Dứt Việc Giám Hộ is the event of terminating guardianship under certain conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848943</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tìm Kiếm Người Vắng Mặt">
  <data key="d0">Tìm Kiếm Người Vắng Mặt</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Tìm Kiếm Người Vắng Mặt is the process of searching for a missing person at their place of residence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848943</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quản Lý Tài Sản">
  <data key="d0">Quản Lý Tài Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quản Lý Tài Sản refers to the management of assets belonging to a person under guardianship or a missing person.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848944</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thủ Tục Thay Đổi Người Giám Hộ">
  <data key="d0">Thủ Tục Thay Đổi Người Giám Hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thủ Tục Thay Đổi Người Giám Hộ refers to the legal procedures for changing the Guardian.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848944</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Biên Bản">
  <data key="d0">Biên Bản</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Biên Bản is a written record of the transfer of guardianship, detailing the status of the assets and related issues of the person under guardianship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848944</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài Sản">
  <data key="d0">Tài Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài Sản refers to assets or property that can be owned by individuals or entities. These assets can range from movable and immovable property to investments of enterprises and their owners, which are protected by law and cannot be nationalized or confiscated without proper compensation. Tài Sản can be subject to various legal conditions, including those that terminate ownership rights, such as during the termination of guardianship. It can also be owned jointly and is often the subject of the right to use. Tài Sản is involved in various legal transactions, including leasing, ownership retention, and guarantees, and can be subject to specific conditions and obligations in these transactions.

Tài Sản encompasses a wide range of goods or property that can be bought and sold under contracts. It can also refer to assets being transported, which have specific conditions and responsibilities associated with their transport. Additionally, Tài Sản can be lent under a Hợp đồng mượn tài sản, which includes all non-consumable assets. These assets are also involved in legal provisions and can be inherited. Furthermore, Tài Sản refers to property that is possessed, used, or benefited from without legal basis and must be returned to the rightful owner. The legal status of Tài Sản is determined by the laws of the country where the assets are located.&lt;SEP&gt;Tài Sản refers to the assets of the company, which can be sold or restructured.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-053b8a5c1f69c52703201366343dafa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b8a779de69d8737ce9995cfb0f3f049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e4f3de95acd7468b8d781714a57816a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7c9b850c56df03c6a0092f33eddd51c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4623833cd0cb1b86833b9050e09612fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ff345e6f27025707a8c3c4dd1e82b5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9006f99cc5f37528caabd57619fb67d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1dd682bb7148dad05854b2b5ef20db9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71c1c580c8f92c3838ab0f997647d588&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-821c3a34361b8add641406062fd4a10e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Thừa Kế">
  <data key="d0">Người Thừa Kế</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Thừa Kế refers to an individual who inherits assets, property, or a portion of an estate upon the death of the person under guardianship or the owner of the property. This inheritance can be specified in a will or determined by law. The term also encompasses the rights and responsibilities that come with inheriting property, including gaining ownership rights and potentially becoming a member or owner of a company or private enterprise. In some cases, multiple heirs may inherit parts of the estate and may have agreements on how to divide it.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Thừa Kế refers to the heir of a deceased member who can inherit the member's share of the company's assets and potentially become a new member if approved by the board.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63e06b29bf3043507cfbd43beb81a47f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71c1c580c8f92c3838ab0f997647d588&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65946ae20fedf99884e4b9e9ee2eea91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d59be88d8f39c9fce708d8b3f0c8014&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-111878a66be557377de6fec57d456ed2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Quản Lý Di Sản">
  <data key="d0">Người Quản Lý Di Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Quản Lý Di Sản is a person responsible for managing the estate of the deceased person under guardianship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72f8448fcb5f40c271736a6505e9763f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848944</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người giám hộ">
  <data key="d0">Người giám hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người giám hộ is responsible for managing the affairs of a person who lacks civil capacity or has difficulties in perception and behavior.&lt;SEP&gt;A guardian who is responsible for the care and management of a person who has lost their civil capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Người giám hộ refers to a guardian who is a legal representative for those under guardianship.&lt;SEP&gt;Người giám hộ is a guardian who can be designated as a legal representative for individuals with difficulties in perception and behavior.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-482a66c12f2040cbc0eabb425e1b6d97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737848ae2370b96df322ed1b985e715f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849397</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người được giám hộ">
  <data key="d0">Người được giám hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người được giám hộ is the individual under the guardianship of another person, who lacks civil capacity or has difficulties in perception and behavior.&lt;SEP&gt;A person under guardianship who has lost their civil capacity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849064</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 57">
  <data key="d0">Điều 57</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 57 outlines the obligations of a guardian towards a person who lacks civil capacity or has difficulties in perception and behavior.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 57 is a specific article or section within the legal document that outlines the procedures for convening meetings of the company's governing body.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 57 is a legal provision that describes the process for postponing dispute resolution proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853933</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 58">
  <data key="d0">Điều 58</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 58 outlines the rights of a guardian towards a person who lacks civil capacity or has difficulties in perception and behavior.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 58 is a legal provision that details the mediation process and the recognition of a successful mediation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853933</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 59">
  <data key="d0">Điều 59</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 59 outlines the management of the assets of a person under guardianship.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 59 is a legal provision that outlines the conditions under which a dispute resolution process can be suspended.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853933</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 60">
  <data key="d0">Điều 60</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 60 outlines the procedures for changing a guardian.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848971</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người giám hộ đương nhiên">
  <data key="d0">Người giám hộ đương nhiên</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người giám hộ đương nhiên refers to a natural guardian who is appointed by law to manage the affairs of a person who lacks civil capacity or has difficulties in perception and behavior.&lt;SEP&gt;A natural guardian who is automatically assigned based on familial relationships.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849065</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người giám sát việc giám hộ">
  <data key="d0">Người giám sát việc giám hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người giám sát việc giám hộ is the supervisor who oversees the actions of the guardian and must agree to certain transactions involving the assets of the person under guardianship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-48499f3fba1cf01598d43ec529fd4797</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773848971</data>
