<node id="Pháp nhân">
  <data key="d0">Pháp nhân</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Legal entities are subjects of civil law with rights and obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;A legal entity that may be appointed to perform guardianship duties.&lt;SEP&gt;Pháp nhân refers to a legal entity recognized by law.&lt;SEP&gt;Pháp nhân refers to a legal entity that has civil rights and obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;Pháp nhân refers to a legal entity that can have legal representatives designated by the entity itself, by law, or by the court.&lt;SEP&gt;A legal entity responsible for compensating damages caused by its employees while performing assigned tasks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c55b09e479fc060292314cb4f8f8302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12ce4f076c1ad11637bf7e2f3ae95048&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d584ac3c571de434dd905552d6d296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737848ae2370b96df322ed1b985e715f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f476c4f267fa92420ccea7f2351f4dd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851061</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quan hệ dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Quan hệ dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Civil relations are formed on the basis of equality, freedom of will, and independent property.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c55b09e479fc060292314cb4f8f8302</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849050</data>
