<node id="Cộng hòa xã hội chủ nghĩa Việt Nam">
  <data key="d0">Cộng hòa xã hội chủ nghĩa Việt Nam</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The Socialist Republic of Vietnam is the country where civil rights are recognized, respected, protected, and ensured according to the Constitution and laws.&lt;SEP&gt;Cộng hòa xã hội chủ nghĩa Việt Nam is a member of international treaties that determine the applicable law for civil relations with foreign elements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c55b09e479fc060292314cb4f8f8302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người mất năng lực hành vi dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Người mất năng lực hành vi dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A person who has lost their civil capacity and requires a guardian.&lt;SEP&gt;Người mất năng lực hành vi dân sự refers to individuals who have lost their legal capacity due to mental illness or other conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;People who have lost their capacity for civil conduct.&lt;SEP&gt;Người mất năng lực hành vi dân sự refers to individuals who have lost their legal capacity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fef2e18615af027f8385abdb8209870&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4a95c6c117e21012baec10d4e1fb78c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849188</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người con cả">
  <data key="d0">Người con cả</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The eldest child who may become a guardian if both parents have lost civil capacity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849064</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bác ruột">
  <data key="d0">Bác ruột</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A paternal or maternal uncle who may become a guardian if there is no other guardian.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849064</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chú ruột">
  <data key="d0">Chú ruột</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A paternal or maternal uncle who may become a guardian if there is no other guardian.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849064</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
