  <data key="d0">Dì ruột</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-215d052b0c761e4d27801c92b8990219</data>
  <data key="d2">A paternal or maternal aunt may become a guardian if there is no other guardian.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849065</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người đại diện theo pháp luật">
  <data key="d0">Người đại diện theo pháp luật</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người đại diện theo pháp luật is a legal representative who acts on behalf of individuals with limited or no legal capacity, as well as a legal representative designated for a legal entity or an individual by the entity, by law, or by the court. In the context of business entities, Người đại diện theo pháp luật acts on behalf of the company in various legal and administrative matters. This role includes signing the amended company charter for various types of companies and being included in the Certificate of Business Registration for limited liability companies or joint-stock companies. The legal representative is responsible for ensuring the company's legal interests and adhering to the law and the company's charter.&lt;SEP&gt;Người đại diện theo pháp luật is the legal representative of the company, responsible for ensuring the accuracy and timeliness of the information published.&lt;SEP&gt;Người đại diện theo pháp luật is the legal representative who has the right to demand the company to stop using the name of a former member.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737848ae2370b96df322ed1b985e715f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7934cedd8a058c40a35091be7e3f1c17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853244</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người có khó khăn trong nhận thức, làm chủ hành vi">
  <data key="d0">Người có khó khăn trong nhận thức, làm chủ hành vi</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người có khó khăn trong nhận thức, làm chủ hành vi refers to individuals who have difficulties in understanding and controlling their behavior but have not lost their legal capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;People who have difficulties in understanding and controlling their actions.&lt;SEP&gt;Người có khó khăn trong nhận thức, làm chủ hành vi refers to individuals with difficulties in perception and control of behavior.&lt;SEP&gt;Người có khó khăn trong nhận thức, làm chủ hành vi refers to individuals with difficulties in perception and behavior who may require a legal guardian as a legal representative.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fef2e18615af027f8385abdb8209870&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4a95c6c117e21012baec10d4e1fb78c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737848ae2370b96df322ed1b985e715f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849397</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người bị hạn chế năng lực hành vi dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Người bị hạn chế năng lực hành vi dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người bị hạn chế năng lực hành vi dân sự refers to individuals whose legal capacity is restricted due to drug addiction or other conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;People whose capacity for civil conduct is limited.&lt;SEP&gt;Người bị hạn chế năng lực hành vi dân sự refers to individuals with restricted legal capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Người bị hạn chế năng lực hành vi dân sự refers to individuals with restricted civil capacity who may require a legal representative designated by the court.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fef2e18615af027f8385abdb8209870&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4a95c6c117e21012baec10d4e1fb78c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737848ae2370b96df322ed1b985e715f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849397</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giao dịch dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Giao dịch dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Giao dịch dân sự refers to civil transactions that are subject to legal regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Civil transactions that can be declared invalid under certain conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Giao dịch dân sự refers to civil transactions that can be declared invalid due to various reasons such as lack of recognition and control over one's actions or non-compliance with formal requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Civil transactions are legal actions or agreements conducted between parties in a civil context.&lt;SEP&gt;Giao dịch dân sự refers to civil transactions that generate civil rights and obligations for the legal entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Giao dịch dân sự refers to civil transactions that are subject to legal provisions regarding their validity and protection of rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fef2e18615af027f8385abdb8209870&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d584ac3c571de434dd905552d6d296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-482a66c12f2040cbc0eabb425e1b6d97</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849361</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bất động sản">
  <data key="d0">Bất động sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bất động sản refers to real estate properties that require legal registration.&lt;SEP&gt;Bất động sản refers to immovable property, which has specific legal requirements for the pledge to be effective against third parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae8ba811869db57b94f6d4864d7901d2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850096</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Động sản phải đăng ký">
  <data key="d0">Động sản phải đăng ký</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Động sản phải đăng ký refers to movable properties that require legal registration.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849086</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người từ đủ mười lăm tuổi đến chưa đủ mười tám tuổi">
  <data key="d0">Người từ đủ mười lăm tuổi đến chưa đủ mười tám tuổi</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người từ đủ mười lăm tuổi đến chưa đủ mười tám tuổi refers to individuals between the ages of 15 and 18 who can independently engage in civil transactions, except for certain types of transactions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b10203f42f3e19a8ee82cd4453e46d58</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849086</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người đại diện">
  <data key="d0">Người đại diện</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người đại diện refers to a legal representative who acts on behalf of another person or entity for civil transactions. This individual or entity is authorized to conduct such transactions on behalf of another party, including those who are not fully capable of civil conduct due to restrictions or incapacitation. The role of Người đại diện can be assumed by either an individual or a legal entity, and they can act either by legal authority or by specific authorization. In cases where the original person dies, the Người đại diện may take over the work performed on behalf of the original individual. This role is crucial in ensuring that civil transactions can be carried out effectively and legally on behalf of those who are unable to do so themselves.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fef2e18615af027f8385abdb8209870&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4a95c6c117e21012baec10d4e1fb78c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d584ac3c571de434dd905552d6d296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-482a66c12f2040cbc0eabb425e1b6d97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7934cedd8a058c40a35091be7e3f1c17</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851694</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
