  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 150">
  <data key="d0">Điều 150</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 150 defines various types of time limits in legal proceedings, including civil rights, exemption from civil obligations, and the right to initiate a lawsuit.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 151">
  <data key="d0">Điều 151</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 151 explains how time limits are calculated, starting from the first day and ending on the last day of the time limit.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 152">
  <data key="d0">Điều 152</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 152 specifies the effectiveness of time limits for enjoying civil rights or being exempt from civil obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 153">
  <data key="d0">Điều 153</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 153 discusses the continuous nature of time limits for enjoying civil rights or being exempt from civil obligations, including interruptions and their consequences.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 154">
  <data key="d0">Điều 154</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đиều 154 outlines when time limits for initiating a civil lawsuit or requesting resolution of a civil matter begin.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 154 is a regulation that defines the term and number of members of the board of directors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-444a844ae4151849d71498d312b5d52d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853023</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 155">
  <data key="d0">Điều 155</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đиều 155 lists situations where the time limit for initiating a lawsuit does not apply.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 155 is a regulation that defines the organizational structure, standards, and conditions for becoming a member of the board of directors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-444a844ae4151849d71498d312b5d52d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853023</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hiệu hưởng quyền dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Thời hiệu hưởng quyền dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hiệu hưởng quyền dân sự is the time limit for enjoying civil rights, which ends when the subject is entitled to such rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hiệu miễn trừ nghĩa vụ dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Thời hiệu miễn trừ nghĩa vụ dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hiệu miễn trừ nghĩa vụ dân sự is the time limit for being exempt from civil obligations, which ends when the person with such obligations is relieved of them.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hiệu khởi kiện">
  <data key="d0">Thời hiệu khởi kiện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hiệu khởi kiện is the time limit for initiating a lawsuit to request the court to resolve a civil case to protect rights and legal interests.&lt;SEP&gt;Thời hiệu khởi kiện refers to the statute of limitations for initiating legal proceedings.&lt;SEP&gt;Thời hiệu khởi kiện refers to the statute of limitations or the time period within which a lawsuit can be filed.&lt;SEP&gt;Thời hiệu khởi kiện is the statute of limitations for initiating arbitration proceedings, typically two years from the date of the infringement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4a95c6c117e21012baec10d4e1fb78c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hiệu yêu cầu giải quyết việc dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Thời hiệu yêu cầu giải quyết việc dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hiệu yêu cầu giải quyết việc dân sự is the time limit for requesting the court to resolve a civil matter to protect individual, legal entity, national, ethnic, and public interests.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người được hưởng lợi">
  <data key="d0">Người được hưởng lợi</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người được hưởng lợi refers to individuals who benefit from the application of time limits and have the right to refuse the application of time limits, except in cases where refusal is aimed at evading obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ thể">
  <data key="d0">Chủ thể</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ thể is the individual or entity entitled to civil rights when the time limit for enjoying civil rights concludes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người có nghĩa vụ dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Người có nghĩa vụ dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người có nghĩa vụ dân sự is the individual or entity who is relieved of civil obligations when the time limit for exemption from civil obligations concludes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6b3f59800e76e08387285066f5f36cdf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
