  <data key="d0">Bên có nghĩa vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên có nghĩa vụ refers to the party that has an obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên có nghĩa vụ is the party that has obligations to fulfill in a contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên có nghĩa vụ refers to the party responsible for fulfilling obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;The obligor is the party who is responsible for fulfilling the obligation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4a95c6c117e21012baec10d4e1fb78c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef889492cadc79ff9fffe71fb37a420f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce4d817feffbe4339c332e36ad5b2bea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
