  <data key="d0">Điều 77</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 77 is a legal provision that outlines the charter requirements for a legal entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 77 outlines the obligations of the company owner, including capital contribution, compliance with the company charter, and separation of personal and company assets.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851936</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 78">
  <data key="d0">Điều 78</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 78 is a legal provision that specifies the naming requirements for a legal entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 78 details the implementation of the owner's rights in special circumstances, such as transfer of ownership, death, or incapacitation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851936</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 79">
  <data key="d0">Điều 79</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 79 is a legal provision that defines the headquarters requirements for a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 80">
  <data key="d0">Điều 80</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 80 is a legal provision that defines the nationality of a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 81">
  <data key="d0">Điều 81</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều  81 is a legal provision that outlines the assets of a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 82">
  <data key="d0">Điều 82</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 82 is a legal provision that outlines the establishment and registration requirements for a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 83">
  <data key="d0">Điều 83</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 83 is a legal provision that defines the organizational structure of a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 84">
  <data key="d0">Điều 84</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 84 is a legal provision that defines the requirements for branches and representative offices of a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Charters">
  <data key="d0">Charters</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Charters are documents that contain the main contents of a legal entity, such as its name, purpose, headquarters, capital, and organizational structure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên Gọi">
  <data key="d0">Tên Gọi</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tên Gọi is the name of a legal entity, which must be in Vietnamese and reflect the type of organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trụ Sở Chính">
  <data key="d0">Trụ Sở Chính</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trụ Sở Chính is the headquarters of a legal entity, where the management body is located.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vốn Điều Lệ">
  <data key="d0">Vốn Điều Lệ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Vốn Điều Lệ is the charter capital of a legal entity, if applicable.&lt;SEP&gt;The total value of assets contributed or committed by members when establishing a limited liability company or partnership; the total face value of shares sold or registered when establishing a joint-stock company.&lt;SEP&gt;Vốn Điều Lệ is the total value of assets contributed or committed by members or owners when establishing a limited liability company, partnership, or joint-stock company.&lt;SEP&gt;The registered capital of a company, which can be increased or decreased based on the owner's contributions or by raising additional capital from other individuals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851979</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đại Diện Theo Pháp Luật">
  <data key="d0">Đại Diện Theo Pháp Luật</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đại Diện Theo Pháp Luật is the legal representative of a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cơ Cấu Tổ Chức">
  <data key="d0">Cơ Cấu Tổ Chức</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ Cấu Tổ Chức is the organizational structure of a legal entity, including the management body and other bodies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849230</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chi Nhánh">
  <data key="d0">Chi Nhánh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chi Nhánh is a branch of a legal entity, which is not a separate legal entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Chi Nhánh refers to a branch of a business that has ceased operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f6b7c08fc56b324472ca75d1984ba36</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Văn Phòng Đại Diện">
  <data key="d0">Văn Phòng Đại Diện</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Văn Phòng Đại Diện is a representative office of a legal entity, which is not a separate legal entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Văn Phòng Đại Diện is a subordinate unit of a foreign arbitration organization established in Vietnam to seek and promote arbitration opportunities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44b958e89c37ebae08442548c41df280</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854043</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cơ Quan Nhà Nước">
  <data key="d0">Cơ Quan Nhà Nước</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ Quan Nhà Nước refers to state authorities that can make decisions regarding the establishment of legal entities.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ Quan Nhà Nước refers to governmental bodies at the central and local levels that participate in civil relations and have specific functions, powers, and organizational structures.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan nhà nước refers to the governmental authority that has the power to make decisions regarding the operation and dissolution of a cooperative.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04c5e255f3522d9b4bfb81a7f18084cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-783bed81f26ddc9c02e87c49f593844b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63bea5bd12d1af991f494c7882f65825</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850693</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quy định về hình thức">
  <data key="d0">Quy định về hình thức</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quy định về hình thức refers to the formal requirements that must be met for a civil transaction to be valid.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849266</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hậu quả pháp lý">
  <data key="d0">Hậu quả pháp lý</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hậu quả pháp lý refers to the legal consequences of an invalid civil transaction, including the restoration of the original state and compensation for damages.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849266</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hiệu yêu cầu">
  <data key="d0">Thời hiệu yêu cầu</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hiệu yêu cầu refers to the statute of limitations for requesting the court to declare a civil transaction as invalid.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849266</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 128">
  <data key="d0">Điều 128</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 128 is a legal provision that addresses civil transactions declared invalid due to the person not recognizing and controlling their actions.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 128 of the law, which is referenced in the text.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 128 is a regulation concerning the issuance of private bonds by companies that are not public companies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852630</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 129">
  <data key="d0">Điều 129</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 129 is a legal provision that addresses civil transactions declared invalid due to non-compliance with formal requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 129 of the law, which is referenced in the text.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 129 is a regulation concerning the procedures for issuing and transferring private bonds.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852630</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 130">
  <data key="d0">Điều 130</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 130 is a legal provision that addresses civil transactions declared partially invalid.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 130 is a regulation concerning the decision-making process for issuing private bonds.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852630</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 131">
  <data key="d0">Điều 131</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 131 is a legal provision that addresses the legal consequences of invalid civil transactions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849266</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 132">
  <data key="d0">Điều 132</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều  132 is a legal provision that addresses the statute of limitations for requesting the court to declare a civil transaction as invalid.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 132 is a specific article in the law that outlines the rules for the company to repurchase shares.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 132 is a legal article that specifies regulations related to the operations of a joint-stock company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e91add69ab34542976bf62b9aca43ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852478</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đại diện theo pháp luật">
  <data key="d0">Đại diện theo pháp luật</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Legal representation is a concept that defines the rights and responsibilities of a representative in conducting civil transactions on behalf of another party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người được đại diện">
  <data key="d0">Người được đại diện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The represented party is the individual or entity on whose behalf a representative conducts civil transactions.&lt;SEP&gt;Người được đại diện refers to the person or entity on whose behalf a representative acts.&lt;SEP&gt;Người được đại diện refers to the individual or legal entity on whose behalf another acts for civil transactions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-482a66c12f2040cbc0eabb425e1b6d97</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849361</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phạm vi đại diện">
  <data key="d0">Phạm vi đại diện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The scope of representation defines the limits within which a representative can conduct civil transactions on behalf of another party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyết định của cơ quan có thẩm quyền">
  <data key="d0">Quyết định của cơ quan có thẩm quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Decisions by authorized bodies are official determinations that can establish the scope of representation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều lệ của pháp nhân">
  <data key="d0">Điều lệ của pháp nhân</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The articles of association of a legal entity define the scope of representation for that entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nội dung ủy quyền">
  <data key="d0">Nội dung ủy quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The content of authorization specifies the scope of representation granted to a representative.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quy định khác của pháp luật">
  <data key="d0">Quy định khác của pháp luật</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Other legal provisions are additional laws that can define the scope of representation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người không có quyền đại diện">
  <data key="d0">Người không có quyền đại diện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">An unauthorized representative is an individual or entity that conducts civil transactions without proper authorization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người đã giao dịch">
  <data key="d0">Người đã giao dịch</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The party that conducted the transaction is the individual or entity that engaged in a civil transaction with a representative.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người đại diện xác lập, thực hiện vượt quá phạm vi đại diện">
  <data key="d0">Người đại diện xác lập, thực hiện vượt quá phạm vi đại diện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">A representative who conducts transactions beyond the scope of representation is an individual or entity that exceeds the authorized limits of representation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 141">
  <data key="d0">Điều 141</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 141 is a legal provision that defines the scope of representation in civil transactions.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 141 is a regulation that outlines the creation and management of the Danh sách cổ đông for the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852660</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 142">
  <data key="d0">Điều 142</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 142 is a legal provision that outlines the consequences of civil transactions conducted by unauthorized representatives.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 142 is a regulation that specifies the preparation of the agenda and content for the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852661</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 143">
  <data key="d0">Điều 143</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 113 is a legal provision that outlines the consequences of civil transactions conducted by representatives who exceed their authorized scope.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đại diện theo pháp luật chấm dứt">
  <data key="d0">Đại diện theo pháp luật chấm dứt</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The termination of legal representation occurs under specific conditions such as the represented party reaching adulthood or regaining civil capacity, the death of an individual, or the dissolution of a legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Căn cứ khác theo quy định của Bộ luật này hoặc luật khác có liên quan">
  <data key="d0">Căn cứ khác theo quy định của Bộ luật này hoặc luật khác có liên quan</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Other legal bases for the termination of legal representation are defined by the Civil Code or other related laws.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người được đại diện là cá nhân chết">
  <data key="d0">Người được đại diện là cá nhân chết</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d2">The termination of legal representation occurs when the represented individual dies.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849276</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người được đại diện là pháp nhân chấm dứt tồn tại">
  <data key="d0">Người được đại diện là pháp nhân chấm dứt tồn tại</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5cb7db3cfef705b914008825e4c276e6</data>
  <data key="d2">The termination of legal representation occurs when the represented legal entity ceases to exist.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849276</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 144">
  <data key="d0">Điều 144</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 144 defines the concept of a time limit, which is a period of time from one point to another, and can be measured in minutes, hours, days, weeks, months, years, or by an event that may occur.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849299</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 145">
  <data key="d0">Điều 145</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 145 specifies the application of time limit calculation methods as per the Civil Code, except where there is a different agreement or law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849299</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 146">
  <data key="d0">Điều 146</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 146 provides rules for time limits and the calculation of time points, including specific durations and definitions for the beginning, middle, and end of months and years.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 146 is a legal provision that outlines the procedures for conducting and voting at the shareholders' meeting.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852810</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 147">
  <data key="d0">Điều 147</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 147 outlines the starting point of a time limit, which can be based on minutes, hours, days, weeks, months, or years, and may start from a specific event.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849299</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 148">
  <data key="d0">Điều 148</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 148 details the end of a time limit, which can be based on days, weeks, months, or years, and may end on a specific day or the next working day after a holiday.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849299</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 149">
  <data key="d0">Điều 149</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 149 defines the concept of statute of limitations, which is a time limit set by law that, when expired, results in legal consequences for the subject under the conditions specified by law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849299</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hạn">
  <data key="d0">Thời hạn</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hạn refers to a period of time from one point to another, which can be measured in various units such as minutes, hours, days, weeks, months, or years, or by an event.&lt;SEP&gt;Thời hạn refers to the deadlines for sending out meeting notifications and conducting meetings as specified in the company's charter.&lt;SEP&gt;Thời hạn refers to the deadline or time period specified in the legal framework.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c9b32b2b806556ed1dd36c13de6e313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853604</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời điểm">
  <data key="d0">Thời điểm</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời điểm refers to specific points in time, such as the beginning, middle, or end of a month or year.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7fce420202370c7c711321549129cd6e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849299</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
