  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 88 describes the merger of legal entities, where multiple entities can merge into a new entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 88 is a legal provision that specifies additional conditions for the position of Kiểm soát viên in public companies and state-owned enterprises.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d584ac3c571de434dd905552d6d296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d</data>
