  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 90 covers the division of a legal entity into multiple entities.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 90 is a legal provision that outlines the organizational structure for managing state-owned enterprises.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d584ac3c571de434dd905552d6d296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956</data>
