  <data key="d2">Điều 92 addresses the transformation of a legal entity into a different form.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 92 is a legal provision that specifies the rights and obligations of the Hội đồng thành viên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d584ac3c571de434dd905552d6d296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956</data>
