<node id="Văn phòng đại diện">
  <data key="d0">Văn phòng đại diện</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Văn phòng đại diện refers to a representative office that acts on behalf of the legal entity within the scope and duration of the authorization.&lt;SEP&gt;Văn phòng đại diện is a representative office of a business entity that represents the business entity's interests and protects them.&lt;SEP&gt;Văn phòng đại diện refers to representative offices of a business that can be terminated by the business itself or by the government.&lt;SEP&gt;Văn phòng đại diện is a representative office of a foreign arbitration organization operating in Vietnam.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d584ac3c571de434dd905552d6d296b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828</data>
