  <data key="d2">Điều 124 is a legal provision that is referenced in the context of civil transactions.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 124 is a regulation that specifies the rights of shareholders to purchase shares.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-482a66c12f2040cbc0eabb425e1b6d97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4c6a296c5e1b248b6b79c98f9b16e6d</data>
