  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 167 is a legal provision that is referenced in the context of civil transactions.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 167 is a legal provision that outlines the rights of owners to demand the return of unregistered movable property from good faith possessors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-482a66c12f2040cbc0eabb425e1b6d97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b802398ca6d8541021416cdaf49468d1</data>
