  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ Quan Nhà Nước Ở Địa Phương is responsible for civil obligations using the assets it represents and manages, except when assets are transferred to legal entities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-514f9934c36c74c2f0599ebba354e5f0</data>
