  <data key="d0">Điều 100</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 100 outlines the responsibilities for civil obligations of the state and its agencies in civil relations with foreign states, legal entities, and individuals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-514f9934c36c74c2f0599ebba354e5f0</data>
