  <data key="d2">Điều 101 outlines the subjects in civil relations involving households, cooperatives, and other organizations without legal entity status.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 101 outlines the standards and conditions for Directors and General Directors of a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-514f9934c36c74c2f0599ebba354e5f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7</data>
