<node id="Luật Đất Đai">
  <data key="d0">Luật Đất Đai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Luật Đất Đai is a law that governs the determination of subjects in civil relations involving households using land.&lt;SEP&gt;Luật đất đai is the legal framework that governs the rights and obligations related to land use and is referenced in the Hợp đồng về quyền sử dụng đất.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-514f9934c36c74c2f0599ebba354e5f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9006f99cc5f37528caabd57619fb67d8</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850826</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hộ Gia Đình">
  <data key="d0">Hộ Gia Đình</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hộ Gia Đình is a household entity that can participate in civil relations, with its members being the subjects of such relations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-514f9934c36c74c2f0599ebba354e5f0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849413</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ Hợp Tác">
  <data key="d0">Tổ Hợp Tác</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ Hợp Tác is a cooperative entity that can participate in civil relations, with its members being the subjects of such relations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-514f9934c36c74c2f0599ebba354e5f0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849413</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ Chức Khác Không Có Tư Cách Pháp Nhân">
  <data key="d0">Tổ Chức Khác Không Có Tư Cách Pháp Nhân</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ Chức Khác Không Có Tư Cách Pháp Nhân is an organization without legal entity status that can participate in civil relations, with its members being the subjects of such relations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-514f9934c36c74c2f0599ebba354e5f0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849413</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Luật nhà ở">
  <data key="d0">Luật nhà ở</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Luật nhà ở is a legal document that defines the ownership of shared property in apartment buildings.&lt;SEP&gt;Luật nhà ở is a law that governs the sale of residential properties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd76a1e6d7896b3bdcaa4bbcae2b9dea</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ sở hữu các căn hộ">
  <data key="d0">Chủ sở hữu các căn hộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ sở hữu các căn hộ are the owners of individual apartments within a shared building.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sở hữu chung hợp nhất">
  <data key="d0">Sở hữu chung hợp nhất</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Sở hữu chung hợp nhất is a concept of collective ownership of shared property in apartment buildings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sở hữu chung hỗn hợp">
  <data key="d0">Sở hữu chung hỗn hợp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Sở hữu chung hỗn hợp is a concept of mixed collective ownership of property contributed by owners from different economic sectors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Pháp luật">
  <data key="d0">Pháp luật</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Pháp luật is the legal framework that governs the rights and obligations of property owners.&lt;SEP&gt;Pháp luật refers to the legal provisions and regulations that govern the establishment of ownership rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Pháp luật refers to the legal framework that governs the conditions and procedures for transactions, including auctions and ownership transfers.&lt;SEP&gt;The law refers to the legal framework governing the roles and responsibilities of the Chairman, Board of Members, Director, and General Director.&lt;SEP&gt;Legal regulations that the company must comply with.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853003</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền ưu tiên mua">
  <data key="d0">Quyền ưu tiên mua</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyền ưu tiên mua is the right of existing property owners to purchase a share of property before it is sold to others.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nhà nước">
  <data key="d0">Nhà nước</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nhà nước is the state entity that takes ownership of abandoned property shares.&lt;SEP&gt;Nhà nước is the governing body that determines ownership of cultural heritage artifacts and sets the base salary for financial calculations.&lt;SEP&gt;Nhà nước refers to the state or government, which may inherit assets if there are no eligible heirs.&lt;SEP&gt;The state, which is responsible for compensating damages caused by public officials acting unlawfully.&lt;SEP&gt;The state is the entity that inherits the estate when there are no eligible heirs.&lt;SEP&gt;The State is an entity that the Board of Members must be loyal to and protect its interests.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2acb4f3dcdc42f5db6c9c4797e01299&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f476c4f267fa92420ccea7f2351f4dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd15f05b480bf5c4a3b4b4e068a412cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài sản chung của vợ chồng">
  <data key="d0">Tài sản chung của vợ chồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài sản chung của vợ chồng refers to the shared property of a married couple that can be divided by agreement or court decision.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chế độ tài sản theo thỏa thuận">
  <data key="d0">Chế độ tài sản theo thỏa thuận</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chế độ tài sản theo thỏa thuận is a legal arrangement for the division of shared property based on mutual agreement between spouses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phần diện tích, trang thiết bị và các tài sản khác">
  <data key="d0">Phần diện tích, trang thiết bị và các tài sản khác</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phần diện tích, trang thiết bị và các tài sản khác refers to the shared areas, equipment, and other assets in a shared apartment building.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài sản chung hỗn hợp">
  <data key="d0">Tài sản chung hỗn hợp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài sản chung hỗn hợp refers to mixed collective ownership of property contributed by owners from different economic sectors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quản lý tài sản chung">
  <data key="d0">Quản lý tài sản chung</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quản lý tài sản chung is the concept of managing shared property collectively by all owners.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sử dụng tài sản chung">
  <data key="d0">Sử dụng tài sản chung</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Sử dụng tài sản chung is the concept of using shared property collectively by all owners.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Định đoạt tài sản chung">
  <data key="d0">Định đoạt tài sản chung</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Định đoạt tài sản chung is the concept of disposing of shared property collectively by all owners.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849452</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ sở hữu">
  <data key="d0">Chủ sở hữu</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b345fbbc1125fb4f691693608eb8ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b802398ca6d8541021416cdaf49468d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ sở hữu refers to the owner of a property or asset who holds rights and responsibilities over it. This includes the right to demand the return of the asset from unlawful possessors and the ability to decide to sell the property through an auction. In the context of a company, the Chủ sở hữu is the owner who appoints a representative to act on their behalf and is responsible for signing the amended company charter for a one-member limited liability company. Additionally, the owner is involved in the valuation of assets contributed to capital. The term also applies to mixed collective ownership of property, where owners from different economic sectors contribute to a common asset. Overall, the Chủ sở hữu has rights over the produce or income from the property and is responsible for its management and disposition.</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851903</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ sở hữu chung">
  <data key="d0">Chủ sở hữu chung</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8a3f543a1762069fe562fe6a382e1b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9</data>
  <data key="d2">Quản lý tài sản chung is the concept of managing shared property collectively by all owners.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ sở hữu chung refers to joint owners of a property.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ sở hữu chung refers to co-owners of property who must agree to sell it through an auction.</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850408</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 223">
  <data key="d0">Điều 223</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 223 is a legal provision that establishes ownership rights through contracts such as purchase, gift, exchange, loan, or other ownership transfer agreements.&lt;SEP&gt;Đиều 223 is a legal provision that establishes ownership rights through contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8a3f543a1762069fe562fe6a382e1b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849756</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 224">
  <data key="d0">Điều 224</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 224 is a legal provision that establishes ownership rights over the produce or income from a property, according to agreements or legal provisions, starting from the time the produce or income is obtained.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 225">
  <data key="d0">Điều 225</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 225 is a legal provision that establishes ownership rights in cases of merger of assets, detailing the rights and obligations of the owners involved.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 226">
  <data key="d0">Điều 226</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 226 is a legal provision that establishes ownership rights in cases of mixing assets, detailing the rights and obligations of the owners involved.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người sử dụng tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Người sử dụng tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người sử dụng tài sản refers to the user of a property who has rights over the produce or income from the property.&lt;SEP&gt;Người sử dụng tài sản refers to individuals who use a property or asset, whether legally or unlawfully.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b802398ca6d8541021416cdaf49468d1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849602</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người được giao tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Người được giao tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người được giao tài sản refers to the person who receives property through a contract and gains ownership rights over it.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người sáp nhập tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Người sáp nhập tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người sáp nhập tài sản refers to the person who merges their property with another's, creating new ownership rights and obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hoa lợi, lợi tức">
  <data key="d0">Hoa lợi, lợi tức</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hoa lợi, lợi tức refers to the produce or income from a property, which is subject to ownership rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vật chính, vật phụ">
  <data key="d0">Vật chính, vật phụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Vật chính, vật phụ refers to the main and secondary assets involved in the merger of properties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vật mới">
  <data key="d0">Vật mới</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Vật mới refers to the new asset created through the merger or mixing of other assets.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hợp đồng">
  <data key="d0">Hợp đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hợp đồng refers to a contract or agreement between parties, which establishes their obligations and rights. These contracts can cover various types of agreements, such as purchase, gift, exchange, loan, or other ownership transfer agreements that establish ownership rights. Hợp đồng is a legal document that is checked and monitored by the Board of Members. It can also be terminated unilaterally under certain conditions. In a business context, Hợp đồng often refers to contracts or agreements between a company and related parties. Additionally, these contracts may need to be continued and fulfilled even after the termination of a branch.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd76a1e6d7896b3bdcaa4bbcae2b9dea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-795fb9faa3ff64c104def58573301724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853538</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thỏa thuận">
  <data key="d0">Thỏa thuận</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thỏa thuận refers to agreements between parties regarding the ownership of produce or income from a property.&lt;SEP&gt;Thỏa thuận refers to agreements made between parties regarding ownership and division of property.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8a3f543a1762069fe562fe6a382e1b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849756</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sáp nhập">
  <data key="d0">Sáp nhập</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Sáp nhập refers to the process of merging assets, creating new ownership rights and obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trộn lẫn">
  <data key="d0">Trộn lẫn</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trộn lẫn refers to the process of mixing assets, creating new ownership rights and obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-79babcd2cf4aac518b57f409f34a0382</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849467</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ Sở Hữu">
  <data key="d0">Chủ Sở Hữu</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ Sở Hữu refers to the owner of a property or asset. This individual has the right to use the property according to their will, without causing harm or affecting national, ethnic, public interests, or the legal rights and interests of others. The rights of the Chủ Sở Hữu can be terminated under certain legal conditions. Additionally, the owner can transfer ownership rights to others or retain the rights to the property while granting the right of use to another party. If the property was possessed or used without a legal basis, the Chủ Sở Hữu is entitled to have it returned. In the context of a company, the Chủ Sở Hữu can also authorize a representative.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-abefb366f0615b56504281fccf7e1528&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-053b8a5c1f69c52703201366343dafa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d82c525b3c62a646037cf7bc6fec6a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-931c1ae4f95c0b01df5de17931b38de9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63e06b29bf3043507cfbd43beb81a47f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b5f857bd7e099346e71679265152a98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-821c3a34361b8add641406062fd4a10e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851463</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
