  <data key="d2">Nguyên Vật Liệu refers to the raw materials used in the creation of a new object.&lt;SEP&gt;Nguyên Vật Liệu refers to the raw materials used in the processing work.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-abefb366f0615b56504281fccf7e1528&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1c19a83d55829491343a14f74bec683</data>
