<node id="Nhà Nước">
  <data key="d0">Nhà Nước</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nhà Nước refers to the state or government.&lt;SEP&gt;Nhà Nước represents the state, which acts as the owner of public property and manages it uniformly.&lt;SEP&gt;Nhà Nước is the governing body that recognizes and protects the existence and development of various types of enterprises, ensuring equality before the law and protecting the legal rights and interests of enterprises and their owners.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-abefb366f0615b56504281fccf7e1528&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d82c525b3c62a646037cf7bc6fec6a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657</data>
