  <data key="d2">Đиều 229 establishes the rights of ownership for buried, hidden, or sunken property that is found.&lt;SEP&gt;Tài Sản Bị Chôn, Giấu, Bị Vùi Lấp, Chìm Đắm refers to property that has been buried, hidden, covered, or sunk and later discovered.</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
