<node id="Quyền Sở Hữu">
  <data key="d0">Quyền Sở Hữu</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyền Sở Hữu refers to the ownership rights over a property, which can be terminated under various conditions as outlined in the legal provisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyền Sở Hữu refers to the concept of ownership rights that can be established or terminated under various conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyền Sở Hữu refers to the ownership rights that the borrower acquires over the borrowed assets from the moment of receipt.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-053b8a5c1f69c52703201366343dafa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63e06b29bf3043507cfbd43beb81a47f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e641f370052e6c1c0a156d3d338c15a4</data>
