  <data key="d2">Điều 198 is a legal provision that outlines the state's role in managing public property.&lt;SEP&gt;A legal provision that outlines the process for dividing a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7d82c525b3c62a646037cf7bc6fec6a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aff8a680816d92d14d4a77e34dbfc7d</data>
