  <data key="d0">Điều 199</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 199 is a legal provision that specifies the conditions for the use and disposition of public property.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 199 is a regulation concerning the division of companies and the procedures involved.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7d82c525b3c62a646037cf7bc6fec6a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4</data>
