<node id="Doanh Nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Doanh Nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Doanh Nghiệp refers to enterprises that manage and use state-invested assets according to the law.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh Nghiệp is a business entity that has legal representatives and is protected by the law.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh Nghiệp refers to businesses that have the right to operate freely in various industries, provided they comply with the law, and have obligations to maintain certain conditions and report their activities.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp refers to a business entity that must follow naming regulations and must include its name on all transaction documents, financial records, and publications.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp is a business entity responsible for registering changes to its branch or representative office and notifying the business registration authority of its business location.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh Nghiệp is a business entity that engages in commercial activities and is subject to legal and regulatory requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh Nghiệp is a business entity that is responsible for fulfilling contracts, settling debts, and ensuring the rights of workers after the closure of a branch.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7d82c525b3c62a646037cf7bc6fec6a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fef4d2c27b6430834254a2ffeefda111&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f6b7c08fc56b324472ca75d1984ba36</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
