<node id="Thỏa Thuận">
  <data key="d0">Thỏa Thuận</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thỏa Thuận refers to various types of agreements between parties in different contexts. It can establish joint ownership, set terms for the guarantee and its execution, and define the conditions for the right to use a property. Thỏa Thuận also encompasses agreements regarding the processing and handling of collateral, the terms and conditions of transactions between buyers and sellers, and the fulfillment of obligations between parties. In lease agreements, Thỏa Thuận outlines the terms and conditions agreed upon between the tenant and the landlord. Additionally, it can refer to agreements concerning the transportation of assets, including the payment terms and conditions involved in such transactions.&lt;SEP&gt;Thỏa Thuận refers to the agreement between the service provider and the service user regarding the terms and conditions of the service.&lt;SEP&gt;Thỏa Thuận refers to agreements or arrangements made between parties in the context of the legal provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b8a779de69d8737ce9995cfb0f3f049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c152b6a16d5764e941499e3920fc0f1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7c9b850c56df03c6a0092f33eddd51c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e892e20c0d7efd608322517a03188b51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ff345e6f27025707a8c3c4dd1e82b5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e729376fa2e1544912532baf7015b267&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1dd682bb7148dad05854b2b5ef20db9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
