<node id="Tập Quán">
  <data key="d0">Tập Quán</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tập Quán refers to customs that establish joint ownership.&lt;SEP&gt;Tập Quán refers to established customs or practices used to determine payment methods when there is no clear agreement between the parties.&lt;SEP&gt;Tập Quán refers to customary practices that determine the terms of the lease agreement when specific terms are not explicitly agreed upon.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b8a779de69d8737ce9995cfb0f3f049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4623833cd0cb1b86833b9050e09612fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
