  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 207 defines joint ownership and its types, including joint ownership by shares and joint ownership in unity.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 207 is a regulation concerning the conditions and circumstances for the dissolution of a business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b8a779de69d8737ce9995cfb0f3f049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4</data>
