  <data key="d2">Điều 209 defines joint ownership by shares, where each owner's share is clearly defined.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 209 outlines the procedures for dissolving a business when the business registration certificate is revoked or by a court decision.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b8a779de69d8737ce9995cfb0f3f049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
