  <data key="d2">Điều 177 is a legal provision that ensures safety in cases where trees or structures pose a risk of damage to adjacent properties.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 177 is a legal provision that defines the structure and responsibilities of a công ty hợp danh.</data>
