  <data key="d2">Điều 178 is a legal provision that regulates the opening of doors and windows towards adjacent properties.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều  178 is a legal provision that outlines the procedures for capital contribution and issuance of certificates of capital contribution in a công ty hợp danh.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7b345fbbc1125fb4f691693608eb8ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1efb55d02317343a2ef5f32d5d741bc9</data>
