  <data key="d2">Điều 179 is a legal provision that defines the concept of possession.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 179 is a legal provision that defines the assets of a công ty hợp danh.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7b345fbbc1125fb4f691693608eb8ffa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1efb55d02317343a2ef5f32d5d741bc9</data>
