  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa vụ thanh toán refers to the obligation to make payments, which can affect the division of jointly owned property.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8a3f543a1762069fe562fe6a382e1b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849756</data>
