  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849756</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Bên Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Bảo Lãnh is a party that provides a guarantee for another party's obligations and may receive remuneration for this service.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Bảo Lãnh is the third party that guarantees the obligations of the party being guaranteed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Nhận Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Bên Nhận Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Nhận Bảo Lãnh is the party that receives the guarantee and has the right to demand the fulfillment of the guarantee under certain conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Nhận Bảo Lãnh is the party that receives the guarantee from the third party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Được Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Bên Được Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Được Bảo Lãnh is the party whose obligations are guaranteed by another party.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Được Bảo Lãnh is the party whose obligations are guaranteed by the third party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thù Lao">
  <data key="d0">Thù Lao</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thù Lao refers to the remuneration that the guarantee provider (Bên Bảo Lãnh) can receive if there is an agreement with the guaranteed party (Bên Được Bảo Lãnh).&lt;SEP&gt;Thù Lao refers to the compensation paid to members of the Board of Directors, which is included in the company's business expenses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853131</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nhiệm Vụ Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Nhiệm Vụ Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nhiệm Vụ Bảo Lãnh is the obligation that the guarantee provider (Bên Bảo Lãnh) must fulfill if the guaranteed party (Bên Được Bảo Lãnh) fails to meet their obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Miễn Việc Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Miễn Việc Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Miễn Việc Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Bảo Lãnh is the situation where the guarantee recipient (Bên Nhận Bảo Lãnh) waives the guarantee provider's (Bên Bảo Lãnh) obligation to fulfill the guarantee.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trách Nhiệm Dân Sự Của Bên Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Trách Nhiệm Dân Sự Của Bên Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trách Nhiệm Dân Sự Của Bên Bảo Lãnh refers to the civil liability of the guarantee provider (Bên Bảo Lãnh) when they fail to fulfill their guarantee obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chấm Dứt Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Chấm Dứt Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chấm Dứt Bảo Lãnh is the termination of the guarantee under certain conditions, such as the fulfillment of the guaranteed obligation or mutual agreement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nhiệm Vụ Phát Sinh Trong Tương Lai">
  <data key="d0">Nhiệm Vụ Phát Sinh Trong Tương Lai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nhiệm Vụ Phát Sinh Trong Tương Lai refers to obligations that arise in the future and are covered by the guarantee until the death of the guarantor or the dissolution of the legal entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Pháp Nhân Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Pháp Nhân Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Pháp Nhân Bảo Lãnh refers to a legal entity that provides a guarantee and is subject to termination upon dissolution.&lt;SEP&gt;Pháp Nhân Bảo Lãnh is a legal entity that provides a guarantee for the obligations of another party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bảo Đảm Bằng Tài Sản">
  <data key="d0">Bảo Đảm Bằng Tài Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bảo Đảm Bằng Tài Sản refers to the use of property as collateral to secure the fulfillment of the guarantee.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dac1d82b1ca37e1ac9e9211b39cad02e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Thứ Ba">
  <data key="d0">Người Thứ Ba</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Thứ Ba is responsible for holding and managing the collateral asset, ensuring its preservation and returning it as required.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Thứ Ba refers to a third party who may benefit from the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Thứ Ba is a third party who may dispute the ownership of the purchased property, leading to potential cancellation of the contract and compensation claims by the buyer.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Thứ Ba refers to a third party who may have rights and obligations in a contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Thứ Ba refers to a third party involved in the execution of the authorization contract.&lt;SEP&gt;A third party who receives property from someone who possessed or used it without legal basis and has the obligation to return it.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fb0e6ef087a638bbb3f5e1626539a69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9979a7994ede77b3cd590f1eb4f836e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-315d7e31800029ff10aa10797b03fa33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-821c3a34361b8add641406062fd4a10e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851194</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Nhận Thế Chấp">
  <data key="d0">Bên Nhận Thế Chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Nhận Thế Chấp is the party that receives the collateral asset from the collateral holder.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Thế Chấp">
  <data key="d0">Bên Thế Chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Thế Chấp is the party that provides the collateral asset.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thế Chấp Quyền Sử Dụng Đất">
  <data key="d0">Thế Chấp Quyền Sử Dụng Đất</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thế Chấp Quyền Sử Dụng Đất refers to the collateralization of land use rights without collateralizing the assets attached to the land.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thế Chấp Tài Sản Gắn Liền Với Đất">
  <data key="d0">Thế Chấp Tài Sản Gắn Liền Với Đất</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thế Chấp Tài Sản Gắn Liền Với Đất refers to the collateralization of assets attached to the land without collateralizing the land use rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chấm Dứt Thế Chấp Tài Sản">
  <data key="d0">Chấm Dứt Thế Chấp Tài Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chấm Dứt Thế Chấp Tài Sản refers to the termination conditions of collateralization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đặt Cọc">
  <data key="d0">Đặt Cọc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đặt Cọc is a form of security where one party (the depositor) provides another party (the recipient) with an asset to ensure the execution of a contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ký Cược">
  <data key="d0">Ký Cược</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Ký Cược is a form of security where the lessee provides the lessor with an asset to ensure the return of the leased asset.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài Sản Đặt Cọc">
  <data key="d0">Tài Sản Đặt Cọc</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài Sản Đặt Cọc is the asset provided as security in a placement deposit.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài Sản Ký Cược">
  <data key="d0">Tài Sản Ký Cược</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài Sản Ký Cược is the asset provided as security in a pledge.&lt;SEP&gt;Tài Sản Ký Cược is the asset that is deposited as collateral and can be claimed by the lessor if the leased asset is not returned.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ refers to the obligations that are secured by collateral and can lead to the termination of collateralization.&lt;SEP&gt;Nghĩa Vụ is a legal concept that refers to obligations or duties that one party must fulfill for the benefit of another party.&lt;SEP&gt;Nghĩa Vụ refers to obligations or duties that must be fulfilled by one party to another.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e4f3de95acd7468b8d781714a57816a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e892e20c0d7efd608322517a03188b51</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850480</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Khác">
  <data key="d0">Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Khác</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Khác refers to alternative security measures that can replace collateralization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài Sản Đã Được Xử Lý">
  <data key="d0">Tài Sản Đã Được Xử Lý</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài Sản Đã Được Xử Lý refers to the condition where the collateral asset has been processed, leading to the termination of collateralization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thỏa Thuận Của Các Bên">
  <data key="d0">Thỏa Thuận Của Các Bên</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thỏa Thuận Của Các Bên refers to an agreement among the parties that can lead to the termination of collateralization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ Sở Hữu Tài Sản Gắn Liền Với Đất">
  <data key="d0">Chủ Sở Hữu Tài Sản Gắn Liền Với Đất</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ Sở Hữu Tài Sản Gắn Liền Với Đất is the owner of the assets attached to the land and may or may not be the user of the land.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Thuê">
  <data key="d0">Bên Thuê</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Thuê is the lessee who provides an asset (Tài Sản Ký Cược) to ensure the return of the leased asset.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Thuê is the party that leases an asset and is responsible for returning it or paying for it if they do not return it.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Thuê is a party in a lease agreement who has the right to use the leased property and is responsible for paying rent and maintaining the property.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Thuê is the lessee in a leasing contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1dd682bb7148dad05854b2b5ef20db9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Cho Thuê">
  <data key="d0">Bên Cho Thuê</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Cho Thuê is the lessor who receives the asset (Tài Sản Ký Cược) to ensure the return of the leased asset.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Cho Thuê is the party that provides the leased asset and has the right to reclaim it if the lease terms are not met.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Cho Thuê is a party in a lease agreement who provides the leased property and is responsible for delivering the property and maintaining its usability.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Cho Thuê is the lessor in a leasing contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1dd682bb7148dad05854b2b5ef20db9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài Sản Thế Chấp">
  <data key="d0">Tài Sản Thế Chấp</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef30533c311bc88d4ba5ae54e8e8cca7</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Thứ Ba is responsible for managing and preserving the collateral asset and returning it as required.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849809</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Trong Tương Lai">
  <data key="d0">Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Trong Tương Lai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Trong Tương Lai refers to the legal concept of securing future obligations, allowing parties to agree on the scope and duration of the secured obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849830</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài Sản Bảo Đảm">
  <data key="d0">Tài Sản Bảo Đảm</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài Sản Bảo Đảm refers to the asset used as collateral, which must belong to the guarantor and can be either existing or future assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Tài Sản Bảo Đảm is collateral that is subject to legal provisions for processing and handling.&lt;SEP&gt;Tài Sản Bảo Đảm is collateral that is used to secure the performance of obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c152b6a16d5764e941499e3920fc0f1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3cdb3cd8d8583064c0301937b6f4744a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850053</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hiệu Lực Đối Kháng Với Người Thứ Ba">
  <data key="d0">Hiệu Lực Đối Kháng Với Người Thứ Ba</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hiệu Lực Đối Kháng Với Người Thứ Ba refers to the legal effect of collateral measures against third parties, which arises from registration or possession of the collateral asset.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849830</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đăng Ký Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm">
  <data key="d0">Đăng Ký Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Đăng Ký Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm refers to the registration of collateral measures, which is a condition for the collateral transaction to be effective.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849830</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Các Trường Hợp Xử Lý Tài Sản Bảo Đảm">
  <data key="d0">Các Trường Hợp Xử Lý Tài Sản Bảo Đảm</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Các Trường Hợp Xử Lý Tài Sản Bảo Đảm refers to the circumstances under which collateral assets can be processed, such as when the secured obligation is due and the debtor fails to fulfill it.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849830</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Hiện Tại">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Hiện Tại</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Hiện Tại refers to current obligations that can be secured.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849830</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Có Điều Kiện">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Có Điều Kiện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Có Điều Kiện refers to obligations that are subject to certain conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849830</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Pháp Luật">
  <data key="d0">Pháp Luật</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Pháp Luật refers to the legal framework that governs various aspects of legal obligations, agreements, and regulations in Vietnamese society. It encompasses the conditions and agreements related to securing obligations, the fulfillment of obligations, and the procedures and regulations related to collateral and its valuation. Additionally, Pháp Luật governs the terms and conditions of lease agreements and the execution of contracts, including the responsibilities of the parties involved.

Pháp Luật also regulates the rights and obligations of parties involved in the transportation of assets and the operations and decisions of the Hội Đồng Quản Trị (Board of Directors). Furthermore, it governs the rights and obligations of the company owner, including capital contributions, compliance with the company charter, and the separation of personal and company assets. Overall, Pháp Luật provides a comprehensive legal framework that ensures the proper execution and enforcement of various legal and contractual obligations in Vietnamese society.&lt;SEP&gt;Pháp Luật refers to the legal framework that governs the inclusion of compensation and salaries in the company's business expenses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3cdb3cd8d8583064c0301937b6f4744a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-315d7e31800029ff10aa10797b03fa33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ff345e6f27025707a8c3c4dd1e82b5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a95c0aafb09aeaffa31c143eaf83c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853131</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Thay Thế Được">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Thay Thế Được</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Thay Thế Được refers to an obligation that can be replaced by another obligation if the original obligation cannot be fulfilled, provided it is accepted by the party with the right.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Riêng Rẽ">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Riêng Rẽ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Riêng Rẽ is an obligation where multiple people are responsible for a specific part of the obligation, and each person is only required to fulfill their own part.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Liên Đới">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Liên Đới</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Liên Đới is an obligation where multiple people are jointly responsible for fulfilling the obligation, and the party with the right can demand any one of them to fulfill the entire obligation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Đối Với Nhiều Người Có Quyền Liên Đới">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Đối Với Nhiều Người Có Quyền Liên Đới</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Đối Với Nhiều Người Có Quyền Liên Đới is an obligation where each of the multiple parties with the right can demand the fulfillment of the entire obligation from the party with the obligation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Phân Chia Được Theo Phần">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Phân Chia Được Theo Phần</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Phân Chia Được Theo Phần is an obligation where the object of the obligation can be divided into parts for fulfillment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Không Phân Chia Được Theo Phần">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Không Phân Chia Được Theo Phần</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Không Phân Chia Được Theo Phần is an obligation where the object of the obligation must be fulfilled all at once.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d0">Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ includes various measures to ensure the fulfillment of obligations, such as collateral, mortgage, deposit, and guarantee.&lt;SEP&gt;Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ refers to the measures that ensure the fulfillment of obligations in a contract, which are not affected by the invalidity of the main contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850298</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phạm Vi Nghĩa Vụ Được Bảo Đảm">
  <data key="d0">Phạm Vi Nghĩa Vụ Được Bảo Đảm</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phạm Vi Nghĩa Vụ Được Bảo Đảm refers to the scope of an obligation that can be secured, which can be partial or full, and can include current, future, or conditional obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d0">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ refers to the party that is responsible for fulfilling an obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ refers to the party that is responsible for fulfilling an obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ is the party responsible for fulfilling certain obligations, such as making payments or performing specific actions.&lt;SEP&gt;The party with the obligation is responsible for performing the task and compensating for damages.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ refers to the party that is obligated to fulfill a duty or obligation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e892e20c0d7efd608322517a03188b51</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850480</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Có Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Bên Có Quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Có Quyền refers to the party that has the right to demand the fulfillment of an obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Có Quyền refers to the party that has the right to demand the fulfillment of an obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Có Quyền is the party that has the right to enforce the obligations of the other party, such as receiving payment or compensation.&lt;SEP&gt;The party with the right has the ability to demand performance of obligations and can transfer the right to demand to a substitute party.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Có Quyền refers to the party that has the right to demand the fulfillment of an obligation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e892e20c0d7efd608322517a03188b51</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850480</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Ban Đầu">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Ban Đầu</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa Vụ Thay Thế Được can replace the original obligation if it cannot be fulfilled, provided it is accepted by the party with the right.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nhiều Người">
  <data key="d0">Nhiều Người</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d2">Nhiều Người are responsible for their specific parts of the obligation, and each person is only required to fulfill their own part.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nhiều Người Có Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Nhiều Người Có Quyền</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d2">Nhiều Người Có Quyền can each demand the fulfillment of the entire obligation from the party with the obligation.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đối Tượng Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d0">Đối Tượng Nghĩa Vụ</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d2">Đối Tượng Nghĩa Vụ can be divided into parts for fulfillment.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền Hưởng Dụng">
  <data key="d0">Quyền Hưởng Dụng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyền Hưởng Dụng is a legal right that allows an individual or entity to exploit and benefit from the utility and income of another's property for a specified period.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyền Hưởng Dụng is the right to use a property and enjoy its benefits.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b5f857bd7e099346e71679265152a98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849921</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Hưởng Dụng">
  <data key="d0">Người Hưởng Dụng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Hưởng Dụng is the individual or entity that has the right to exploit and benefit from the utility and income of another's property for a specified period.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Hưởng Dụng is an individual who has the right to use a property and is entitled to the benefits derived from it.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b5f857bd7e099346e71679265152a98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849921</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bất Động Sản">
  <data key="d0">Bất Động Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bất Động Sản refers to real estate property that can be subject to rights of use and ownership.&lt;SEP&gt;Bất Động Sản refers to real estate or immovable property.&lt;SEP&gt;Bất động sản refers to real estate assets, and the applicable law for inheritance and contracts involving real estate is determined by the law of the country where the real estate is located.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b5f857bd7e099346e71679265152a98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e4f3de95acd7468b8d781714a57816a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cda21c37a8b4d265d1fff1cf5f7aea</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851572</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 255">
  <data key="d0">Điều 255</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 255 is a legal provision that allows the owner of real estate to install power lines and communication lines through other properties reasonably, ensuring safety and convenience.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b5f857bd7e099346e71679265152a98</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
