<node id="Lãi Suất">
  <data key="d0">Lãi Suất</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Lãi Suất refers to the interest rate applied for delayed payments.&lt;SEP&gt;Lãi Suất refers to the interest rate agreed upon between the buyer and seller, which is used to calculate the interest on late payments.&lt;SEP&gt;Lãi Suất refers to the interest rate agreed upon in a loan agreement, with a maximum limit of 20% per year unless otherwise specified by law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7c9b850c56df03c6a0092f33eddd51c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e641f370052e6c1c0a156d3d338c15a4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850865</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền Bề Mặt">
  <data key="d0">Quyền Bề Mặt</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyền Bề Mặt is the right of an entity to use the surface of the land, water, and airspace above the land and water that belongs to another entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyền Bề Mặt is a legal concept that refers to the rights associated with the surface of land, water, and airspace.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e4f3de95acd7468b8d781714a57816a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850056</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ Thể Quyền Bề Mặt">
  <data key="d0">Chủ Thể Quyền Bề Mặt</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ Thể Quyền Bề Mặt is an individual or entity that has the right to use the surface of the land, water, and airspace above the land and water that belongs to another entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ Thể Quyền Bề Mặt refers to the individual or entity that holds the rights associated with the surface of land, water, and airspace.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e4f3de95acd7468b8d781714a57816a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850056</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
