  <data key="d0">Chủ Sở Hữu Tài Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ Sở Hữu Tài Sản is the owner of the property.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849921</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hoa Lợi, Lợi Tức">
  <data key="d0">Hoa Lợi, Lợi Tức</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Hoa Lợi, Lợi Tức refers to the benefits and profits derived from the property.&lt;SEP&gt;Income or profits derived from the possession or use of another's property without legal basis and must be returned.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-821c3a34361b8add641406062fd4a10e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851194</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền Sử Dụng Đất">
  <data key="d0">Quyền Sử Dụng Đất</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyền Sử Dụng Đất is the right to use land.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyền sử dụng đất refers to the rights to use land, which can be transferred, leased, subleased, gifted, mortgaged, or used as capital contribution under a Hợp đồng về quyền sử dụng đất.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9006f99cc5f37528caabd57619fb67d8</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850826</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ Thể Quyền Sử Dụng Đất">
  <data key="d0">Chủ Thể Quyền Sử Dụng Đất</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ Thể Quyền Sử Dụng Đất is an individual or entity that has the right to use land.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849921</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di Chúc">
  <data key="d0">Di Chúc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Di Chúc is a legal document that specifies the distribution of assets after the death of an individual.&lt;SEP&gt;Di Chúc is a legal document that expresses the testator's wishes regarding the distribution of their estate after death.&lt;SEP&gt;Di Chúc is the will that determines the distribution of property.&lt;SEP&gt;Di Chúc is the document that specifies the allocation of an estate and the conditions under which it is distributed.&lt;SEP&gt;Di Chúc is a legal document that specifies the distribution of a person's assets after their death.&lt;SEP&gt;A will that specifies the division of the estate and may include provisions for the executor and heirs.&lt;SEP&gt;Di chúc is a legal document that specifies the distribution of assets after death. The capacity to create, modify, or revoke a di chúc is determined by the law of the country where the testator had citizenship at the time of the action.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71c1c580c8f92c3838ab0f997647d588&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65946ae20fedf99884e4b9e9ee2eea91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a522f9aff4b603ac455ec99a8440d150&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cda21c37a8b4d265d1fff1cf5f7aea</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851572</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài sản thế chấp">
  <data key="d0">Tài sản thế chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài sản thế chấp refers to the collateral asset used to secure a debt or obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;Tài sản thế chấp refers to the property used as collateral in a pledge agreement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35e5b9d9646a1753edafbdf0516edae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e01f265574843f568ac9f6ea2cd861c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849950</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên thế chấp">
  <data key="d0">Bên thế chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên thế chấp is the party that provides the collateral asset to secure a debt or obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên thế chấp is the party that uses their own property to secure an obligation and does not transfer the property to the other party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35e5b9d9646a1753edafbdf0516edae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e01f265574843f568ac9f6ea2cd861c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849950</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên nhận thế chấp">
  <data key="d0">Bên nhận thế chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên nhận thế chấp is the party that receives the collateral asset to secure a debt or obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên nhận thế chấp is the party that receives the property as collateral for an obligation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35e5b9d9646a1753edafbdf0516edae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e01f265574843f568ac9f6ea2cd861c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849950</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người thứ ba giữ tài sản thế chấp">
  <data key="d0">Người thứ ba giữ tài sản thế chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người thứ ba giữ tài sản thế chấp is a third party who holds the collateral asset on behalf of the parties involved.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35e5b9d9646a1753edafbdf0516edae4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849941</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hàng hóa luân chuyển">
  <data key="d0">Hàng hóa luân chuyển</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Hàng hóa luân chuyển refers to goods that are in circulation during the production and business processes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35e5b9d9646a1753edafbdf0516edae4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849941</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Kho hàng">
  <data key="d0">Kho hàng</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Kho hàng refers to a warehouse or storage facility that holds goods as collateral.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35e5b9d9646a1753edafbdf0516edae4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849941</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
