<node id="Bảo lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Bảo lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bảo lãnh is a form of guarantee that ends under certain conditions such as the fulfillment of obligations or replacement by another form of security.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef889492cadc79ff9fffe71fb37a420f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tín chấp">
  <data key="d0">Tín chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tín chấp is a form of guarantee provided by political-social organizations for individuals or poor households to borrow money from financial institutions for production, business, or consumption.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef889492cadc79ff9fffe71fb37a420f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ chức chính trị - xã hội">
  <data key="d0">Tổ chức chính trị - xã hội</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ chức chính trị - xã hội are political-social organizations that can provide guarantees for individuals or poor households to borrow money from financial institutions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef889492cadc79ff9fffe71fb37a420f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cầm giữ tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Cầm giữ tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cầm giữ tài sản is the act of holding assets legally when the debtor fails to fulfill their obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ef889492cadc79ff9fffe71fb37a420f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773849980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
