<node id="Ký Quỹ">
  <data key="d0">Ký Quỹ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Ký quỹ is the act of depositing a sum of money, precious metals, precious stones, or valuable documents into a blocked account at a financial institution to ensure the fulfillment of obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bảo Lưu Quyền Sở Hữu">
  <data key="d0">Bảo Lưu Quyền Sở Hữu</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bảo lưu quyền sở hữu is the retention of ownership rights by the seller until the buyer has fully fulfilled their payment obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bảo Lãnh">
  <data key="d0">Bảo Lãnh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bảo lãnh is a third party's commitment to fulfill the obligations of the party being guaranteed if they fail to do so.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Bán">
  <data key="d0">Bên Bán</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Bán is the party that sells an asset and retains ownership until the buyer has fully paid for it.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Bán refers to the seller in a transaction, who has various responsibilities such as delivering goods, providing information, and compensating for damages.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Bán is responsible for providing information and guidance on the use of the purchased property, ensuring the ownership rights of the purchased property, and guaranteeing the quality of the purchased item.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7c9b850c56df03c6a0092f33eddd51c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fb0e6ef087a638bbb3f5e1626539a69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4623833cd0cb1b86833b9050e09612fd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850373</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Mua">
  <data key="d0">Bên Mua</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Mua is the party that purchases an asset and has the right to use it during the period of retained ownership.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Mua refers to the buyer in a transaction, who has various rights and obligations such as receiving goods, paying for them, and seeking compensation for damages.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Mua is the buyer who has the right to request information and guidance on the purchased property, to cancel the contract if ownership rights are disputed, and to request repairs, replacements, or refunds for defective items within the warranty period.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7c9b850c56df03c6a0092f33eddd51c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fb0e6ef087a638bbb3f5e1626539a69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4623833cd0cb1b86833b9050e09612fd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850373</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài Sản Thuê">
  <data key="d0">Tài Sản Thuê</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài Sản Thuê is the asset that is leased and must be returned or paid for by the lessee.&lt;SEP&gt;Tài Sản Thuê refers to the leased property that is the subject of the lease agreement, which must be delivered in the agreed-upon condition and used for the agreed-upon purpose.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài Khoản Phong Tỏa">
  <data key="d0">Tài Khoản Phong Tỏa</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài Khoản Phong Tỏa is a blocked account at a financial institution where the collateral is deposited.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ Chức Tín Dụng">
  <data key="d0">Tổ Chức Tín Dụng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ Chức Tín Dụng is a financial institution that manages the blocked account where the collateral is deposited.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 330">
  <data key="d0">Điều 330</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 330 is a legal provision that defines the concept of ký quỹ, which involves depositing collateral into a blocked account at a financial institution to ensure the fulfillment of obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 331">
  <data key="d0">Điều 331</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 331 is a legal provision that defines the concept of bảo lưu quyền sở hữu, which involves the seller retaining ownership of an asset until the buyer has fully fulfilled their payment obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 332">
  <data key="d0">Điều 332</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 332 is a legal provision that outlines the rights of the seller to reclaim an asset if the buyer fails to fulfill their payment obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 333">
  <data key="d0">Điều 333</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 333 is a legal provision that outlines the rights and obligations of the buyer during the period of retained ownership.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 334">
  <data key="d0">Điều 334</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 334 is a legal provision that outlines the conditions under which the retention of ownership rights is terminated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 335">
  <data key="d0">Điều 335</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 335 is a legal provision that defines the concept of bảo lãnh, which involves a third party guaranteeing the obligations of another party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 336">
  <data key="d0">Điều 336</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 336 is a legal provision that outlines the scope and conditions of a guarantee.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
