<node id="Người chuyển giao quyền yêu cầu">
  <data key="d0">Người chuyển giao quyền yêu cầu</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The person who transfers the right to claim must notify the obligor in writing about the transfer of the right to claim.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người thế quyền">
  <data key="d0">Người thế quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The person who takes over the right to claim must be provided with necessary information and related documents by the person transferring the right to claim.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người thế nghĩa vụ">
  <data key="d0">Người thế nghĩa vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The person who takes over the obligation becomes the new obligor if the transfer of the obligation is agreed upon by the party with the right.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 366">
  <data key="d0">Điều 366</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 366 outlines the obligations to provide information and transfer documents when transferring the right to claim.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 367">
  <data key="d0">Điều 367</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 367 states that the person transferring the right to claim is not responsible for the obligor's ability to fulfill the obligation after the transfer, except in cases of different agreements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 368">
  <data key="d0">Điều 368</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 368 specifies that the transfer of the right to claim includes any security measures for the fulfillment of the obligation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 369">
  <data key="d0">Điều 369</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 369 describes the right of the obligor to refuse to fulfill the obligation if they were not notified about the transfer of the right to claim.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 370">
  <data key="d0">Điều 370</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 370 explains the conditions under which an obligation can be transferred to another party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 371">
  <data key="d0">Điều 371</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 371 states that when an obligation with security measures is transferred, the security measures are terminated unless there is a different agreement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 372">
  <data key="d0">Điều 372</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 372 lists the circumstances under which an obligation is terminated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 373">
  <data key="d0">Điều 373</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 373 defines the completion of an obligation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa vụ">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">An obligation is a duty or commitment that must be fulfilled.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7676f54dc24423d8f0801960c11c6cf7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850154</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 421">
  <data key="d0">Điều 421</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 421 is a legal provision that outlines the conditions and procedures for modifying a contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 422">
  <data key="d0">Điều 422</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 422 is a legal provision that specifies the circumstances under which a contract can be terminated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 423">
  <data key="d0">Điều 423</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 423 is a legal provision that details the conditions under which a contract can be canceled and the rights of the parties involved.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 424">
  <data key="d0">Điều 424</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 424 is a legal provision that describes the circumstances under which a contract can be canceled due to a party's failure to perform its obligations within a reasonable time.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 425">
  <data key="d0">Điều 425</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 425 is a legal provision that outlines the conditions under which a contract can be canceled due to a party's inability to perform its obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 426">
  <data key="d0">Điều 426</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 426 is a legal provision that specifies the circumstances under which a contract can be canceled due to the loss or damage of the subject matter of the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 427">
  <data key="d0">Điều 427</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 427 is a legal provision that describes the consequences of canceling a contract, including the obligations of the parties and the resolution of disputes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bộ luật">
  <data key="d0">Bộ luật</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bộ luật refers to a legal code or set of laws that governs the procedures and conditions for modifying, terminating, and canceling contracts.&lt;SEP&gt;Bộ luật is a legal document that contains regulations and rules for various aspects of transportation and contractual obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850856</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người có nghĩa vụ">
  <data key="d0">Người có nghĩa vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người có nghĩa vụ refers to the party in a contract who is responsible for performing certain obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;Người có nghĩa vụ refers to the party that is responsible for fulfilling the terms of the contract and is subject to penalties or compensation if they violate the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người có quyền">
  <data key="d0">Người có quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người có quyền refers to the party in a contract who has the right to demand the performance of certain obligations from the other party.&lt;SEP&gt;Người có quyền refers to the party that has the right to claim compensation for damages resulting from a breach of contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên kia">
  <data key="d0">Bên kia</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên kia refers to the other party in a contract, typically in the context of one party's obligations or rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên vi phạm">
  <data key="d0">Bên vi phạm</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên vi phạm refers to the party in a contract who has breached the terms of the agreement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên hủy bỏ hợp đồng">
  <data key="d0">Bên hủy bỏ hợp đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên hủy bỏ hợp đồng refers to the party in a contract who has the right to cancel the contract under certain conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên bị thiệt hại">
  <data key="d0">Bên bị thiệt hại</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên bị thiệt hại refers to the party in a contract who suffers a loss or damage due to the other party's breach of the agreement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850167</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 417">
  <data key="d0">Điều 417</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 417 states that a contract for the benefit of a third party cannot be modified or canceled once the third party has agreed to benefit from it, unless the third party consents to the modification or cancellation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều  418">
  <data key="d0">Điều  418</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 418 outlines the agreement on penalties for contract violations, including the amount of the penalty and the conditions under which the penalty is applied.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 419">
  <data key="d0">Điều 419</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 419 defines the compensation for damages resulting from a breach of contract, including the right to claim compensation for the benefits that would have been received from the contract and the right to claim compensation for costs incurred due to the breach.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 420">
  <data key="d0">Điều 420</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 420 addresses the execution of a contract when there is a fundamental change in circumstances, including the conditions for such a change and the rights of the affected party to renegotiate or terminate the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phạt vi phạm">
  <data key="d0">Phạt vi phạm</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phạt vi phạm refers to the penalty agreed upon in a contract for the party that violates the terms of the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thiệt hại được bồi thường">
  <data key="d0">Thiệt hại được bồi thường</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thiệt hại được bồi thường refers to the compensation for damages resulting from a breach of contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hoàn cảnh thay đổi cơ bản">
  <data key="d0">Hoàn cảnh thay đổi cơ bản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hoàn cảnh thay đổi cơ bản refers to a fundamental change in circumstances that affects the execution of a contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên giao kết hợp đồng">
  <data key="d0">Bên giao kết hợp đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên giao kết hợp đồng refers to the parties involved in the contract who are responsible for its execution and fulfillment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên vi phạm nghĩa vụ">
  <data key="d0">Bên vi phạm nghĩa vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên vi phạm nghĩa vụ refers to the party that violates the terms of the contract and is subject to penalties or compensation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên thụ hưởng">
  <data key="d0">Bên thụ hưởng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên thụ hưởng refers to the party that is entitled to receive the benefits from the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 418">
  <data key="d0">Điều 418</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 418 outlines the agreement on penalties for contract violations, including the amount of the penalty and the conditions under which the penalty is applied, affecting the party that violates the terms of the contract.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đиều 419">
  <data key="d0">Đиều 419</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d2">Đиều 419 defines the compensation for damages resulting from a breach of contract, including the right to claim compensation for the benefits that would have been received from the contract and the right to claim compensation for costs incurred due to the breach, affecting the party that has the right to claim compensation.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đиều 420">
  <data key="d0">Đиều 420</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f99273835b3b6031602578494c58acd7</data>
  <data key="d2">Đиều 420 addresses the execution of a contract when there is a fundamental change in circumstances, including the conditions for such a change and the rights of the affected party to renegotiate or terminate the contract, affecting the parties involved in the contract.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850193</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Địa Điểm Giao Kết Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d0">Địa Điểm Giao Kết Hợp Đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The location where a contract is concluded is agreed upon by the parties; if there is no agreement, it is the residence of an individual or the headquarters of a legal entity that proposed the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850221</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời Điểm Giao Kết Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d0">Thời Điểm Giao Kết Hợp Đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">The time when a contract is concluded is when the proposing party receives acceptance. If there is an agreement that silence is acceptance, the time is the end of the agreed period. For oral contracts, it is when the parties agree on the content. For written contracts, it is when the last party signs or accepts in another form.&lt;SEP&gt;Thời Điểm Giao Kết Hợp Đồng refers to the time and place where the contract is agreed upon, which is used to determine the payment method based on local customs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4623833cd0cb1b86833b9050e09612fd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850373</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hiệu Lực Của Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d0">Hiệu Lực Của Hợp Đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">A legally concluded contract becomes effective from the time of conclusion, unless otherwise agreed or provided by law. Once effective, the parties must perform their rights and obligations as committed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850221</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Các Loại Hợp Đồng Chủ Yếu">
  <data key="d0">Các Loại Hợp Đồng Chủ Yếu</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Contracts can be categorized into bilateral, unilateral, main, subsidiary, for the benefit of a third party, and conditional contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850221</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phụ Lục Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d0">Phụ Lục Hợp Đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">An annex to a contract can provide detailed terms and has the same effect as the contract itself. If the annex contradicts the contract, the conflicting clause is invalid unless agreed otherwise.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850221</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giải Thích Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d0">Giải Thích Hợp Đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Interpretation of a contract involves understanding unclear terms based on the parties' intentions, the purpose of the contract, and local customs. Contradictions between the parties' common will and the contract language are resolved in favor of the common will.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850221</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Đề Nghị">
  <data key="d0">Bên Đề Nghị</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Đề Nghị refers to the party that proposes the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Đề Nghị is the party proposing to enter into a contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b76bceedbe3231fcd1a7081ac9ec062b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850346</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Ký Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d0">Bên Ký Hợp Đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Ký Hợp Đồng refers to the parties that sign the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-260bea9c64a292b86aedaae3fb25a8dc</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850221</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Lãi Suất Phát Sinh Do Chậm Trả Tiền">
  <data key="d0">Lãi Suất Phát Sinh Do Chậm Trả Tiền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Lãi suất phát sinh do chậm trả tiền is determined by the agreement of the parties but cannot exceed the interest rate specified in Article 468 of this Civil Code; if there is no agreement, it is executed according to the provisions of Article 468.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trách Nhiệm Do Không Thực Hiện Hoặc Không Được Thực Hiện Một Công Việc">
  <data key="d0">Trách Nhiệm Do Không Thực Hiện Hoặc Không Được Thực Hiện Một Công Việc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Responsibility for not performing or not being allowed to perform a task includes the right to demand the other party to continue performing the task, perform it themselves, or have someone else perform it and demand reasonable costs and compensation for damages.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trách Nhiệm Do Chậm Tiếp Nhận Việc Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d0">Trách Nhiệm Do Chậm Tiếp Nhận Việc Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Responsibility for delayed acceptance of the performance of obligations includes compensation for damages and bearing all risks and costs incurred from the time of delayed acceptance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trách Nhiệm Bồi Thường Thiệt Hại Do Vi Phạm Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d0">Trách Nhiệm Bồi Thường Thiệt Hại Do Vi Phạm Nghĩa Vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Responsibility for compensating damages caused by the violation of obligations includes full compensation for damages, except for agreements or legal provisions to the contrary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thiệt Hại Do Vi Phạm Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d0">Thiệt Hại Do Vi Phạm Nghĩa Vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Damages caused by the violation of obligations include material and non-material damages.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa Vụ Ngăn Chặn, Hạn Chế Thiệt Hại">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa Vụ Ngăn Chặn, Hạn Chế Thiệt Hại</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The obligation to prevent and limit damages includes taking necessary and reasonable measures to prevent or limit damages.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bồi Thường Thiệt Hại Trong Trường Hợp Bên Bị Vi Phạm Có Lỗi">
  <data key="d0">Bồi Thường Thiệt Hại Trong Trường Hợp Bên Bị Vi Phạm Có Lỗi</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Compensation for damages when the party being violated is at fault includes compensation proportional to the degree of fault.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Lỗi Trong Trách Nhiệm Dân Sự">
  <data key="d0">Lỗi Trong Trách Nhiệm Dân Sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Fault in civil liability includes intentional fault and unintentional fault.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chuyển Giao Quyền Yêu Cầu">
  <data key="d0">Chuyển Giao Quyền Yêu Cầu</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Transfer of the right to demand includes transferring the right to demand to a substitute party according to an agreement, except for certain cases.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Thế Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Người Thế Quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The substitute party becomes the party with the right to demand after the transfer of the right to demand.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850228</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
