  <data key="d0">Article 358</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 358 of the Civil Code outlines the responsibilities for not performing or not being allowed to perform a task.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
