</node>
<node id="Bên bán">
  <data key="d0">Bên bán</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên bán is a party in a transaction who is responsible for transferring ownership and may be required to compensate the buyer under certain conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850408</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên mua">
  <data key="d0">Bên mua</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên mua is a party in a transaction who is responsible for purchasing and may be required to take necessary measures to prevent or limit damage.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850408</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Quyền tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyền tài sản refers to the rights associated with property, including the right to demand payment and the transfer of ownership.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850408</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người mắc nợ">
  <data key="d0">Người mắc nợ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người mắc nợ is a debtor who is responsible for making payments and whose ability to pay may be guaranteed by the seller.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850408</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên dùng thử">
  <data key="d0">Bên dùng thử</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên dùng thử is a party who is allowed to use an item for a trial period before deciding to purchase it.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850408</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đấu giá tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Đấu giá tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Đấu giá tài sản is an auction event where property is sold according to the principles of fairness, transparency, and legality.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850408</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hạn dùng thử">
  <data key="d0">Thời hạn dùng thử</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hạn dùng thử is the trial period during which the buyer can use the item before deciding to purchase it.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb927ff207ca7e0465d21f05d999a0f9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850408</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
