  <data key="d2">Đиều  507 outlines the rights and obligations of cooperative members, including enjoying profits, participating in decision-making, compensating for damages, and fulfilling other rights and obligations as per the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d2cf1280fe7dc5dd2f57d5818548506</data>
