<node id="Thời Gian Hợp Lý">
  <data key="d0">Thời Gian Hợp Lý</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời Gian Hợp Lý is a reasonable period of time required for one party to notify the other party before terminating the lease agreement.&lt;SEP&gt;Thời Gian Hợp Lý refers to a reasonable time period that must be adhered to in the context of the legal provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1dd682bb7148dad05854b2b5ef20db9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chất Lượng">
  <data key="d0">Chất Lượng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chất Lượng refers to the condition and standard of the leased property as agreed upon in the lease agreement.&lt;SEP&gt;Chất Lượng refers to the quality of the service provided.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e729376fa2e1544912532baf7015b267</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850702</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sửa Chữa">
  <data key="d0">Sửa Chữa</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Sửa Chữa is the process of repairing any defects or damages to the leased property to ensure its usability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giảm Giá Thuê">
  <data key="d0">Giảm Giá Thuê</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Giảm Giá Thuê refers to a reduction in the rental fee due to issues with the leased property.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đổi Tài Sản Khác">
  <data key="d0">Đổi Tài Sản Khác</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đổi Tài Sản Khác refers to the replacement of the leased property with another property if the original property is defective or cannot be repaired.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tranh Chấp Về Quyền Sở Hữu">
  <data key="d0">Tranh Chấp Về Quyền Sở Hữu</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Tranh Chấp Về Quyền Sở Hữu is a dispute over the ownership of the leased property that affects the tenant's ability to use the property.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hao Mòn Tự Nhiên">
  <data key="d0">Hao Mòn Tự Nhiên</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hao Mòn Tự Nhiên refers to natural wear and tear that occurs from the use of the leased property, for which the tenant is not responsible.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tu Sửa">
  <data key="d0">Tu Sửa</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Tu Sửa is the process of improving or enhancing the leased property, which can increase its value if approved by the landlord.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thông Báo">
  <data key="d0">Thông Báo</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thông Báo refers to the notification required by one party to the other before terminating the lease agreement or making certain decisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cho Thuê Lại">
  <data key="d0">Cho Thuê Lại</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cho Thuê Lại refers to the act of subleasing the leased property with the landlord's consent.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giao Tài Sản Thuê">
  <data key="d0">Giao Tài Sản Thuê</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Giao Tài Sản Thuê is the event where the landlord delivers the leased property to the tenant as agreed upon in the lease agreement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chấm Dứt Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d0">Chấm Dứt Hợp Đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Chấm Dứt Hợp Đồng refers to the termination of the lease agreement by either party under certain conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bảo Dưỡng">
  <data key="d0">Bảo Dưỡng</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Bảo Dưỡng is the process of maintaining the leased property to prevent damage and ensure its usability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hợp đồng dịch vụ">
  <data key="d0">Hợp đồng dịch vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hợp đồng dịch vụ is a contract for services where the service provider continues to perform the work after the initial contract period, and the service user is aware but does not object.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab83736c7458e42bbefffad0de52acd0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850572</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hợp đồng vận chuyển hành khách">
  <data key="d0">Hợp đồng vận chuyển hành khách</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hợp đồng vận chuyển hành khách is a contract for passenger transportation where the carrier transports passengers and luggage to a specified location, and passengers must pay the transportation fee.&lt;SEP&gt;Hợp đồng vận chuyển hành khách is a contract for passenger transportation that outlines the rights and responsibilities of both the passenger and the transportation company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab83736c7458e42bbefffad0de52acd0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850856</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên vận chuyển">
  <data key="d0">Bên vận chuyển</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên vận chuyển is the party responsible for transporting passengers and luggage to the agreed-upon destination safely and on time.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên vận chuyển is the transportation company or entity responsible for transporting passengers and goods, and has specific obligations and liabilities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab83736c7458e42bbefffad0de52acd0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850856</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hành khách">
  <data key="d0">Hành khách</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hành khách is the passenger who uses the transportation service and is required to pay the transportation fee.&lt;SEP&gt;Hành khách refers to passengers who are transported and have rights and responsibilities under the transportation contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab83736c7458e42bbefffad0de52acd0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850856</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hành lý">
  <data key="d0">Hành lý</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Hành lý is the luggage that is transported along with the passenger.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab83736c7458e42bbefffad0de52acd0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850572</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vé">
  <data key="d0">Vé</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Vé is the ticket that serves as evidence of the contract between the carrier and the passenger.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab83736c7458e42bbefffad0de52acd0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850572</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phương tiện vận chuyển">
  <data key="d0">Phương tiện vận chuyển</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Phương tiện vận chuyển is the mode of transportation used to transport passengers and luggage.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab83736c7458e42bbefffad0de52acd0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850572</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 522">
  <data key="d0">Điều 522</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 522 defines the contract for passenger transportation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab83736c7458e42bbefffad0de52acd0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850572</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
