<node id="Bên Gửi">
  <data key="d0">Bên Gửi</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Gửi is a party in a contract who is responsible for sending and retrieving assets, and paying for the storage and labor costs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-315d7e31800029ff10aa10797b03fa33</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850592</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Nhận Giữ Tài Sản">
  <data key="d0">Bên Nhận Giữ Tài Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Nhận Giữ Tài Sản is a party in a contract who is responsible for holding and safeguarding the assets sent by the other party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-315d7e31800029ff10aa10797b03fa33</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850592</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hợp Đồng Ủy Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Hợp Đồng Ủy Quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hợp Đồng Ủy Quyền is a contract where one party (bên ủy quyền) authorizes another party (bên được ủy quyền) to perform tasks on their behalf.&lt;SEP&gt;Hợp Đồng Ủy Quyền is a contract that defines the terms and conditions of the authority granted from one party to another.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-315d7e31800029ff10aa10797b03fa33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Ủy Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Bên Ủy Quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Ủy Quyền is a party in a contract who authorizes another party to perform tasks on their behalf.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Ủy Quyền is the party that grants authority to another party to perform certain tasks and is responsible for providing necessary information, documents, and means.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-315d7e31800029ff10aa10797b03fa33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên Được Ủy Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Bên Được Ủy Quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên Được Ủy Quyền is a party in a contract who is authorized by another party to perform tasks on their behalf.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Được Ủy Quyền is the party that is granted authority to perform certain tasks and is responsible for carrying out the tasks within the scope of the authority granted.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-315d7e31800029ff10aa10797b03fa33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
