  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hợp đồng về quyền sử dụng đất is a legal agreement where one party transfers or grants rights to use land to another party, and the other party performs rights and obligations according to the contract.</data>
