  <data key="d0">Vận đơn</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Vận đơn is a document that serves as evidence of the contract between the parties in a goods transportation contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
