  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cước phí vận chuyển refers to the transportation fees that are agreed upon between the parties in a transportation contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850856</data>
