  <data key="d3">chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên thuê vận chuyển has the obligation to pay the Cước phí vận chuyển after the goods are loaded onto the transportation vehicle.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
