  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hợp đồng vay tài sản is an agreement where the lender provides assets to the borrower, and the borrower returns the same type of assets in the agreed quantity and quality.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e641f370052e6c1c0a156d3d338c15a4</data>
