</node>
<node id="Người tổ chức các cuộc thi">
  <data key="d0">Người tổ chức các cuộc thi</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The organizer of the contests is responsible for announcing the contest conditions, scoring system, prizes, and the amount of each prize.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người đoạt giải">
  <data key="d0">Người đoạt giải</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The prize winner has the right to request the contest organizer to award the prize as announced.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thực hiện công việc không có ủy quyền">
  <data key="d0">Thực hiện công việc không có ủy quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Performing work without authorization is when a person voluntarily performs a task for the benefit of another person without being obligated to do so.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người thực hiện công việc không có ủy quyền">
  <data key="d0">Người thực hiện công việc không có ủy quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The person performing work without authorization has the obligation to perform the work in accordance with their abilities and conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người có công việc được thực hiện">
  <data key="d0">Người có công việc được thực hiện</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The person for whom the work is performed must accept the work and pay reasonable expenses incurred by the person performing the work without authorization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Khoản 5 Điều 575">
  <data key="d0">Khoản 5 Điều 575</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Clause 5 of Article 575 specifies the conditions under which a person performing work without authorization can no longer continue the work.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 574">
  <data key="d0">Điều 574</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 574 defines the concept of performing work without authorization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 575">
  <data key="d0">Điều 575</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 575 outlines the obligations of the person performing work without authorization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 576">
  <data key="d0">Điều 576</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 576 specifies the payment obligations of the person for whom the work is performed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 577">
  <data key="d0">Điều 577</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 577 details the liability for damages when performing work without authorization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 578">
  <data key="d0">Điều 578</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 578 defines the conditions under which the performance of work without authorization is terminated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-50c919d97de369bc8d7562186f764b91</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Hứa Thưởng">
  <data key="d0">Người Hứa Thưởng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Hứa Thưởng is the party that publicly promises a reward for the completion of a specific task.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Thực Hiện Công Việc">
  <data key="d0">Người Thực Hiện Công Việc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Thực Hiện Công Việc is the party that completes the task for which a reward has been promised.&lt;SEP&gt;A person who performs a task without authorization and cannot continue performing the task as per the regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-821c3a34361b8add641406062fd4a10e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851194</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Tổ Chức Thi">
  <data key="d0">Người Tổ Chức Thi</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Tổ Chức Thi is the party responsible for organizing competitions and is required to publish the conditions for participation, scoring criteria, and prizes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Đạt Giải">
  <data key="d0">Người Đạt Giải</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Đạt Giải is the party that wins a prize in a competition and has the right to request the organizer to award the prize as announced.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 568">
  <data key="d0">Điều 568</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 568 outlines the rights of the party granting authority, including the right to request reports and the right to compensation for damages.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850908</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 569">
  <data key="d0">Điều 569</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 569 describes the unilateral termination of the authority contract by either party, with conditions for notice and compensation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 570">
  <data key="d0">Điều 570</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 570 specifies the obligation to pay a reward to the party that completes the promised task.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 571">
  <data key="d0">Điều 571</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 571 allows the party that promised a reward to retract the promise before the deadline for starting the task.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 572">
  <data key="d0">Điều 572</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 572 details the distribution of rewards to the party or parties that complete the promised task.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 573">
  <data key="d0">Điều 573</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 573 outlines the rules for organizing competitions, including the publication of conditions and prizes, and the rights of winners.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thi Có Giải">
  <data key="d0">Thi Có Giải</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Thi Có Giải refers to organized competitions in various fields such as culture, arts, sports, science, and technology, which must not violate legal prohibitions or social morals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-25258e0d46bb04acb5e0308a2108c231</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850909</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Lập Di Chúc">
  <data key="d0">Người Lập Di Chúc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Lập Di Chúc is the individual who creates and signs a will, expressing their wishes regarding the distribution of their estate.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Lập Di Chúc is the individual who creates a will and specifies the allocation of their estate.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Lập Di Chúc is the individual who creates and signs the di chúc, specifying the distribution of their assets.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65946ae20fedf99884e4b9e9ee2eea91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a522f9aff4b603ac455ec99a8440d150</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851182</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Làm Chứng">
  <data key="d0">Người Làm Chứng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Làm Chứng are individuals present to witness the signing of a will, ensuring its validity.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Làm Chứng is a witness who attests to the authenticity of the di chúc, ensuring that the signatures or marks are genuine.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Làm Chứng is a witness invited to the dispute resolution meeting.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a522f9aff4b603ac455ec99a8440d150&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a36e099bae803eeaad0a5160e83464d5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853928</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cơ Quan, Tổ Chức">
  <data key="d0">Cơ Quan, Tổ Chức</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ Quan, Tổ Chức are entities that can be designated as beneficiaries in a will.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời Điểm Mở Thừa Kế">
  <data key="d0">Thời Điểm Mở Thừa Kế</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời Điểm Mở Thừa Kế is the moment when the estate is distributed according to the will or legal provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di Sản">
  <data key="d0">Di Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Di Sản refers to the estate or assets left by the deceased, which are to be distributed according to the will or legal provisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Di Sản refers to the inheritance that is distributed according to a will or by law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71c1c580c8f92c3838ab0f997647d588</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851025</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phần Di Sản Dùng Vào Việc Thờ Cúng">
  <data key="d0">Phần Di Sản Dùng Vào Việc Thờ Cúng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phần Di Sản Dùng Vào Việc Thờ Cúng is a portion of the estate designated for religious purposes and is not subject to inheritance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Quản Lý Di Sản Thờ Cúng">
  <data key="d0">Người Quản Lý Di Sản Thờ Cúng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Quản Lý Di Sản Thờ Cúng is the individual designated to manage the portion of the estate used for religious purposes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bản Di Chúc">
  <data key="d0">Bản Di Chúc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bản Di Chúc is a specific instance of a will that is subject to legal requirements and can be lost or damaged.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chữ Ký">
  <data key="d0">Chữ Ký</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Chữ Ký refers to the signatures required on a will by the person giving it, the recipient, and at least two witnesses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời Hiệu Yêu Cầu Chia Di Sản">
  <data key="d0">Thời Hiệu Yêu Cầu Chia Di Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời Hiệu Yêu Cầu Chia Di Sản is the period during which claims for the division of the estate can be made.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di Chúc Bị Thất Lạc, Hư Hại">
  <data key="d0">Di Chúc Bị Thất Lạc, Hư Hại</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Di Chúc Bị Thất Lạc, Hư Hại refers to the event where a will is lost or damaged to the point where it cannot be fully understood.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hiệu Lực Của Di Chúc">
  <data key="d0">Hiệu Lực Của Di Chúc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hiệu Lực Của Di Chúc refers to the legal validity and enforceability of a will.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Thừa Kế Không Phụ Thuộc Vào Nội Dung Của Di Chúc">
  <data key="d0">Người Thừa Kế Không Phụ Thuộc Vào Nội Dung Của Di Chúc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Thừa Kế Không Phụ Thuộc Vào Nội Dung Của Di Chúc refers to individuals who are entitled to a portion of the estate regardless of the will's content.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di Sản Dùng Vào Việc Thờ Cúng">
  <data key="d0">Di Sản Dùng Vào Việc Thờ Cúng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Di Sản Dùng Vào Việc Thờ Cúng refers to a portion of the estate designated for religious purposes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850948</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di chúc">
  <data key="d0">Di chúc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Di chúc is a legal document expressing an individual's intent to transfer their assets to others after death.&lt;SEP&gt;Di chúc is a will, a legal document that specifies how a person's assets should be distributed after their death.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c45985a08d6e2c0940eda170510a01</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851042</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hiệu thừa kế">
  <data key="d0">Thời hiệu thừa kế</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hiệu thừa kế is the time limit within which heirs can claim inheritance, varying for different types of assets.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người lập di chúc">
  <data key="d0">Người lập di chúc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người lập di chúc is the individual who creates a will to distribute their assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Người lập di chúc is the person who creates a will.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c45985a08d6e2c0940eda170510a01</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851042</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di sản">
  <data key="d0">Di sản</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Di sản refers to the assets or estate left by the deceased.&lt;SEP&gt;Di sản includes the personal property of the deceased and their share in jointly owned property.&lt;SEP&gt;The estate is the property or assets left by the deceased person to be managed and inherited.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dbdbb74ad11a83bf1856f95ecdfa309&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd15f05b480bf5c4a3b4b4e068a412cd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851129</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người làm chứng">
  <data key="d0">Người làm chứng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người làm chứng is a witness who attests to the validity of a will, particularly in cases of oral wills.&lt;SEP&gt;Người làm chứng is a witness to the creation of a will.&lt;SEP&gt;Người làm chứng is a witness who is summoned to attend a hearing to provide evidence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c45985a08d6e2c0940eda170510a01&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công chứng viên">
  <data key="d0">Công chứng viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công chứng viên is a notary public who verifies and authenticates the signatures or marks of witnesses in an oral will.&lt;SEP&gt;Công chứng viên is a person authorized to witness and authenticate wills.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c45985a08d6e2c0940eda170510a01</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851042</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di chúc hợp pháp">
  <data key="d0">Di chúc hợp pháp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Di chúc hợp pháp is a legally valid will that meets all required conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di chúc miệng">
  <data key="d0">Di chúc miệng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Di chúc miệng is an oral will made in emergency situations when a written will is not possible.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Di chúc bằng văn bản">
  <data key="d0">Di chúc bằng văn bản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Di chúc bằng văn bản is a written will that can be made with or without witnesses and may be notarized or authenticated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 622">
  <data key="d0">Điều 622</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 622 is a legal provision that addresses the situation where there are no eligible heirs to inherit assets, and the remaining assets belong to the state.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 622 deals with estates that have no heirs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd15f05b480bf5c4a3b4b4e068a412cd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851129</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 624">
  <data key="d0">Điều 624</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều  624 defines what a will is, which is a legal document expressing an individual's intent to transfer their assets to others after death.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 625">
  <data key="d0">Điều 625</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 625 outlines the conditions under which a person can create a will, including age and mental capacity requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 626">
  <data key="d0">Điều 626</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 626 details the rights of the person creating a will, including the ability to designate heirs and assign specific portions of the estate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 627">
  <data key="d0">Điều 627</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Đиều 627 specifies that a will must be in written form, unless it is an oral will made in emergency situations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 628">
  <data key="d0">Điều 628</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 628 describes the different forms of written wills, including those with and without witnesses, and those that are notarized or authenticated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 629">
  <data key="d0">Điều 629</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 629 outlines the conditions under which an oral will can be made and the process for validating it.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 630">
  <data key="d0">Điều 630</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 630 defines the conditions for a will to be considered legally valid, including the mental capacity of the person creating the will and the content of the will.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
