  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời Hạn 05 Ngày Làm Việc is the period within which an oral will must be authenticated by a notary or authorized body.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a522f9aff4b603ac455ec99a8440d150</data>
