<node id="Luật này">
  <data key="d0">Luật này</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Luật này is a specific legal document in Vietnam that governs various aspects of company operations, management, and corporate governance. This law outlines the responsibilities and conditions for individuals acting as representatives for shareholders, members, or owners of a company. It includes detailed provisions such as Điều 51, Điều 52, and Điều 53, which establish the legal framework for the operations and management of companies. The law specifies the responsibilities and rights of the board of members and the supervisory board, ensuring that these bodies operate within the legal parameters set forth.

Luật này also governs the management structure and operations of state-owned enterprises, providing a comprehensive legal framework for the roles and responsibilities of key positions such as the Chairman, Board of Members, Director, and General Director. It is a critical document for business registration procedures and the overall regulation of corporate activities in Vietnam. The law covers the responsibilities of the Board of Members and the procedures for initiating lawsuits. It also governs the rights and obligations of shareholders and the management of the company, including the procedures and decisions of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông. Additionally, it outlines the rights and responsibilities of the Ban kiểm soát and its members, ensuring that all aspects of corporate governance are covered under the legal framework.

Furthermore, Luật này refers to the legal framework governing arbitration and dispute resolution in Vietnam, including the establishment and operation of arbitration centers such as the Trung tâm trọng tài. This law came into effect on January 1, 2021, and is a key regulation for the activities of arbitration centers and the resolution of disputes within the corporate sector.&lt;SEP&gt;Luật này refers to the legal document or law that governs the procedures for resolving disputes and the authority of the arbitration council.&lt;SEP&gt;Luật này refers to the specific law or regulation being discussed, which includes provisions related to arbitration proceedings.&lt;SEP&gt;Luật này refers to the law governing the operation of foreign arbitration organizations in Vietnam.&lt;SEP&gt;Luật này refers to the legal framework that governs the procedures for selecting and designating a replacement Arbitrator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7934cedd8a058c40a35091be7e3f1c17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-795fb9faa3ff64c104def58573301724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-752ff3609fa8e883d0e8624f9045b21b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1881019a36e766412bad88d7a1e3d088&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854048</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Hội đồng thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hội đồng thành viên, also known as the Board of Members, is a governing body within a company, typically found in limited liability companies and partnerships. It acts on behalf of the shareholders, members, or owners and is responsible for making decisions regarding the company's operations and governance. The board can appoint a new legal representative and decide on the acceptance of new members. It consists of 3 to 7 members appointed by the company owner, with a term not exceeding 5 years. Hội đồng thành viên convenes for meetings to make decisions and manage the company, representing it and performing its rights and obligations. The board is responsible for appointing the General Director or CEO and making decisions regarding the company's capital and profit distribution. It meets to discuss and decide on issues within its authority and responsibilities, ensuring the company operates effectively and in the best interest of its members.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng thành viên is an organizational body that conducts meetings and makes decisions regarding the company's operations and financial information.&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Members is responsible for appointing the Director or General Director of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng thành viên is the board of members responsible for making decisions and overseeing the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng thành viên is the body that makes decisions regarding the company's members, including the potential exclusion of members who fail to meet their capital contribution obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng thành viên is the governing body of the company that approves the acceptance of new members and makes decisions regarding the company's operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7934cedd8a058c40a35091be7e3f1c17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1efb55d02317343a2ef5f32d5d741bc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853244</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đại hội đồng cổ đông">
  <data key="d0">Đại hội đồng cổ đông</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Đại hội đồng cổ đông, also known as the General Shareholders' Meeting, is a significant event where shareholders gather to make important decisions regarding the company's operations, governance, and capital. This meeting is the highest decision-making body of a company and is crucial for making decisions on various matters, including the nomination of individuals to the Board of Directors and Supervisory Board, the purchase and conversion of preferred shares into common shares, and the sale of shares to raise capital. At this meeting, shareholders can attend, speak, and exercise their voting rights directly or through proxies. The meeting is an organization that makes decisions through resolutions, where shareholders discuss and vote on important matters related to the company's direction and policies. The representative at the meeting acts on behalf of the shareholders, members, or owners, ensuring that their interests are represented and their voices heard in the decision-making process. Typically, this meeting is held annually, providing a platform for shareholders to influence the company's direction and policies.&lt;SEP&gt;The General Shareholders' Meeting has the authority to approve certain transactions and decisions made by the Board of Directors.&lt;SEP&gt;Đại hội đồng cổ đông is a meeting of shareholders of a company to discuss and vote on important matters related to the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Đại hội đồng cổ đông is a meeting of shareholders to discuss and vote on important matters related to the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Đại hội đồng cổ đông is a general meeting of shareholders to discuss and vote on important matters related to the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01b556fba8ab897e9f334300f225003e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c9b32b2b806556ed1dd36c13de6e313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ec32bc0d8c57985cdac3f5a1383a2dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-795fb9faa3ff64c104def58573301724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8031309e714112ffe63df75b002d2d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-952bef1a1bafd78690b17fd797f3d33e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853145</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thành viên refers to a member of a company who appoints a representative to act on their behalf.&lt;SEP&gt;Thành viên refers to the members of the company who have rights and obligations as defined by the company's charter and the law.&lt;SEP&gt;Thành viên refers to the members of the company's governing body who can request meetings and participate in decision-making.&lt;SEP&gt;Thành viên refers to members of the company who can contribute capital and receive profits.&lt;SEP&gt;Thành viên refers to the members of the Board of Members.&lt;SEP&gt;Thành viên refers to members of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852219</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cổ đông">
  <data key="d0">Cổ đông</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cổ đông refers to the shareholders of a company who have purchased shares and have their information recorded in the shareholder register. These shareholders can be either organizations or individuals and have the right to freely transfer their shares. Cổ đông have rights and responsibilities regarding the company's shares, including the right to appoint a representative to act on their behalf. They are required to pay for the shares they have registered to purchase within a specified period. Additionally, Cổ đông have the right to request the Tòa án or Trọng tài to invalidate a resolution if necessary. They also receive the Biên bản kiểm phiếu and Nghị quyết and have the right to attend and vote at the Đại hội đồng cổ đông, where they can participate in the General Shareholders' Meeting and vote on matters discussed. Overall, Cổ đông are integral to the governance and financial structure of a company, holding certain rights and obligations associated with their shareholding.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông refers to shareholders of a company who have the right to receive dividends and participate in the decision-making process of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông is a shareholder of the company who has the right to examine certain reports under specific conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông is a person who owns shares in a company and has certain rights and responsibilities as a shareholder.&lt;SEP&gt;A shareholder who can transfer their shares to another shareholder or a non-shareholder entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-643d72cdd6873e78e2d39abbf824c8bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c9b32b2b806556ed1dd36c13de6e313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0359f960f337b0c62d24c54f784fc5c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853411</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bên thứ ba">
  <data key="d0">Bên thứ ba</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bên thứ ba refers to a third party who is not directly involved in the appointment of a representative but may be affected by the actions of the representative.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851328</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người quản lý công ty">
  <data key="d0">Người quản lý công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người quản lý công ty refers to the manager of a company who is responsible for the day-to-day operations and management of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Người quản lý công ty is a person in a leadership position within the company who can be requested to provide information by the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Người quản lý công ty is the manager of the company, responsible for overseeing the company's operations and management.&lt;SEP&gt;Người quản lý công ty refers to the company's management responsible for providing information from the Sổ đăng ký cổ đông to shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Company managers are responsible for the dissolution process and its compliance with regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853649</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người có thẩm quyền bổ nhiệm người quản lý công ty">
  <data key="d0">Người có thẩm quyền bổ nhiệm người quản lý công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người có thẩm quyền bổ nhiệm người quản lý công ty refers to the person with the authority to appoint the manager of a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851328</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp is a registration certificate for a business entity in Vietnam. It is the official document issued to a company upon its establishment and registration. The certificate is granted when certain conditions are met, such as the submission of valid registration documents and the payment of registration fees. This certificate is essential as it grants legal entity status to a corporation, allowing it to operate legally within the country. It is issued by the Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh, the business registration agency, to confirm the registration of a business. The certificate is also reissued after a company conversion, ensuring that the legal status of the company is updated accordingly.&lt;SEP&gt;Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp is a business registration certificate that can be revoked by the government.&lt;SEP&gt;Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp is a certificate issued to businesses upon successful registration.&lt;SEP&gt;The business registration certificate is a document that can be revoked, leading to the dissolution of a business.&lt;SEP&gt;Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp is a registration certificate for a business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-643d72cdd6873e78e2d39abbf824c8bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1efb55d02317343a2ef5f32d5d741bc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8da64b48c80fc4788c324e08350a340e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a657b345d0676b5a5d6451a2c7c13d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0359f960f337b0c62d24c54f784fc5c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a788d203fae6d3c78c81ae71ea9171e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09d578fe732c3cb08c15e944096d74cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hồ sơ đăng ký doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Hồ sơ đăng ký doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Hồ sơ đăng ký doanh nghiệp is the registration file for a business entity.&lt;SEP&gt;The Business Registration Application is a document submitted to the Business Registration Authority for registering a business.&lt;SEP&gt;The registration documents for a business entity must be valid and complete.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851651</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hồ sơ đăng ký thay đổi nội dung đăng ký doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Hồ sơ đăng ký thay đổi nội dung đăng ký doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Hồ sơ đăng ký thay đổi nội dung đăng ký doanh nghiệp is the registration file for changes to the registration of a business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851328</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vốn điều lệ">
  <data key="d0">Vốn điều lệ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Vốn điều lệ refers to the registered capital of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;The registered capital of a company is included in the Certificate of Business Registration.&lt;SEP&gt;The registered capital of the company, which is the total value of assets committed by the owner.&lt;SEP&gt;Vốn điều lệ refers to the registered capital of a company, which can be increased or decreased under certain conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Vốn điều lệ refers to the registered capital of the company, which can be adjusted based on the payment status of shares.&lt;SEP&gt;Vốn điều lệ is the registered capital of a corporation, which is the total face value of shares sold.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2619cf455665fecc350d8c72d83e850d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852478</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
