  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">The total value of assets contributed or committed by a member to a limited liability company or partnership.&lt;SEP&gt;Phần Vốn Góp refers to the capital contributions made by the members of a limited liability company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fef4d2c27b6430834254a2ffeefda111</data>
