  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Có Liên Qu">
  <data key="d0">Người Có Liên Qu</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d2">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include foreign organizations established abroad under foreign law.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Doanh nghiệp refers to a business entity in Vietnam that must comply with various legal requirements and regulations. These requirements include the need to notify the registration authority of any changes in its registration content and to undergo registration, receiving a Certificate of Business Registration. Doanh nghiệp must publicly announce its registration information on the National Portal for Business Registration and pay the required fees as stipulated by law. The entity is also required to register its main office, branches, representative offices, and business locations with the appropriate authorities.

Doanh nghiệp must adhere to regulations and procedures for suspension, termination, and dissolution. Before dissolution, it is mandatory for the business to ensure that all debts and financial obligations are settled. The registration and supervision of Doanh nghiệp are carried out by the Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh, the official registration authority in Vietnam.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp refers to a business entity that can be subject to having its registration certificate revoked under certain conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09d578fe732c3cb08c15e944096d74cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn">
  <data key="d0">Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn is a limited liability company that can have one or more legal representatives.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn is a type of company with limited liability.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn is a type of limited liability company that can be organized under the management structure defined in the law.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn is a limited liability company.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn is a type of limited liability company that a private enterprise can be converted into.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn is a limited liability company that can convert into a joint-stock company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8da64b48c80fc4788c324e08350a340e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a657b345d0676b5a5d6451a2c7c13d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853384</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công ty cổ phần">
  <data key="d0">Công ty cổ phần</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công ty cổ phần is a joint-stock company that has legal entity status from the date it is issued a business registration certificate. It can have one or more legal representatives and is organized under the management structure defined by law. As a type of corporation, Công ty cổ phần has the right to issue shares, bonds, and other securities. The registered capital of a Công ty cổ phần is divided into equal parts called shares, and shareholders can be organizations or individuals. Ownership in a Công ty cổ phần is divided into shares, which can be purchased using various forms of payment. Additionally, the company must maintain a register of shareholders to keep track of ownership and rights associated with the shares.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty cổ phần is a type of company structure where ownership is divided into shares that can be bought and sold.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty cổ phần is a type of joint-stock company that a private enterprise can be converted into.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty cổ phần is a joint-stock company that can be formed through the conversion of a limited liability company.&lt;SEP&gt;A type of company that can be converted into a single-member limited liability company.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty cổ phần is a type of company that can be converted into a công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-643d72cdd6873e78e2d39abbf824c8bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4c6a296c5e1b248b6b79c98f9b16e6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8da64b48c80fc4788c324e08350a340e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a657b345d0676b5a5d6451a2c7c13d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0359f960f337b0c62d24c54f784fc5c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a788d203fae6d3c78c81ae71ea9171e4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853453</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều lệ công ty">
  <data key="d0">Điều lệ công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều lệ công ty, which translates to the company charter or bylaws, is a fundamental document that governs the structure, operations, and responsibilities of a company's management. It specifies the rights and obligations of shareholders and the procedures for managing the company. The document outlines the number, management titles, and responsibilities of the legal representatives, as well as the total value of capital contributions and other relevant information. It also includes the procedures and regulations for maintaining the Sổ Đăng Ký Thành Viên (register of members) and issuing Giấy Chứng Nhận Phần Vốn Góp (share contribution certificates).

Điều lệ công ty details the rules and procedures for conducting meetings and making decisions, as well as the procedures for convening meetings and making decisions. It defines the rights and obligations of the Chairman, Board of Members, Director, and General Director, and outlines the responsibilities and rights of the Board of Members. The charter specifies the exact ratio required for passing resolutions or decisions by the Board of Members. Additionally, it may contain specific provisions regarding the nomination of individuals to the Board of Directors and Supervisory Board. Overall, Điều lệ công ty serves as a comprehensive guide that outlines the rights and responsibilities of the company and its owners, ensuring clear governance and operational guidelines. It may also have different regulations regarding the process of obtaining shareholder opinions in writing and specific rules for meetings. Furthermore, it defines the rights and obligations of the Trưởng Ban kiểm soát (Supervisory Board Chairman) and must be published on the company's electronic information site.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều lệ công ty is the company's charter or bylaws that outline the rules and procedures for the company's governance.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều lệ công ty is the company's charter or bylaws that outline the rules and procedures for the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều lệ công ty is the charter or bylaws of the company that outlines the rights and obligations of its members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01b556fba8ab897e9f334300f225003e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4c6a296c5e1b248b6b79c98f9b16e6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c9b32b2b806556ed1dd36c13de6e313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ec32bc0d8c57985cdac3f5a1383a2dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-373a8f0d009c4c6073d5e556bc2411e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8031309e714112ffe63df75b002d2d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-952bef1a1bafd78690b17fd797f3d33e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853244</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trọng tài is an arbitration body that serves as an alternative dispute resolution mechanism where a neutral third party makes a binding decision on disputes. This body can be approached by legal representatives to represent the company in arbitration proceedings. Trọng tài has the authority to issue decisions that can affect the content of the Certificate of Business Registration, including changes to the validity of company resolutions. Specifically, it can review and potentially annul resolutions passed by the Đại hội đồng cổ đông, which is the General Shareholders' Meeting. Thus, Trọng tài plays a crucial role in resolving conflicts and ensuring the legality and validity of business decisions and registrations.&lt;SEP&gt;Trọng tài refers to the process of arbitration used to resolve disputes.&lt;SEP&gt;Trọng tài is the arbitration body involved in the dispute resolution process.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-868a62477b36c9e43bd19ac6e811469e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854019</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hội đồng quản trị">
  <data key="d0">Hội đồng quản trị</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hội đồng quản trị, which translates to the Board of Directors, is a governing body in joint-stock companies responsible for managing the company's affairs and making key decisions. This board has the authority to appoint a new legal representative and oversees the timely payment of shares by shareholders. The actions of Hội đồng quản trị can be reviewed by shareholders, ensuring accountability and transparency in the management of the company. As a governing body, Hội đồng quản trị plays a crucial role in the strategic direction and operational oversight of the company it governs. It is responsible for making key decisions and overseeing the management of the company, ensuring that the company operates effectively and in the best interest of its shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị is the board of directors in a company, responsible for managing and overseeing the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Directors appoints or hires the Director or General Director and oversees their activities.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị is a governing body of a company responsible for making decisions and overseeing the management of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị is a governing body responsible for managing the company and making important decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị is a governing body responsible for managing the company and making important decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị is an organizational body within a company, and Kiểm soát viên cannot be a family member of its members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01b556fba8ab897e9f334300f225003e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4c6a296c5e1b248b6b79c98f9b16e6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ec32bc0d8c57985cdac3f5a1383a2dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-795fb9faa3ff64c104def58573301724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8031309e714112ffe63df75b002d2d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-952bef1a1bafd78690b17fd797f3d33e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853165</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ sở hữu công ty">
  <data key="d0">Chủ sở hữu công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ sở hữu công ty is the company owner who can appoint a new legal representative.&lt;SEP&gt;The owner of a one-member limited liability company, responsible for the company's financial obligations and has specific rights as defined by law.&lt;SEP&gt;The owner of the company is responsible for the accuracy of the dissolution file.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853649</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="30 ngày">
  <data key="d0">30 ngày</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">30 ngày refers to the period during which a legal representative must be present in Việt Nam or appoint a substitute.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851411</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Nước Ngoài">
  <data key="d0">Người Nước Ngoài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">People from other countries who are present in Việt Nam and are subject to certain legal provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền Sở Hữu Trí Tuệ">
  <data key="d0">Quyền Sở Hữu Trí Tuệ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Intellectual property rights are determined by the laws of the country where the intellectual property is sought to be protected.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyền Sở Hữu Trí Tuệ is the legal protection of intellectual property rights as defined by the law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851498</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thừa Kế">
  <data key="d0">Thừa Kế</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Inheritance is determined by the laws of the country where the deceased had citizenship.&lt;SEP&gt;Thừa kế is a legal concept that is determined by the law of the country where the deceased had citizenship immediately before death.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cda21c37a8b4d265d1fff1cf5f7aea</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851572</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Năng Lực Pháp Luật Dân Sự">
  <data key="d0">Năng Lực Pháp Luật Dân Sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Civil legal capacity of an individual is determined by the laws of the country where the individual has citizenship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Năng Lực Hành Vi Dân Sự">
  <data key="d0">Năng Lực Hành Vi Dân Sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Civil conduct capacity of an individual is determined by the laws of the country where the individual has citizenship.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Việc Xác Định Cá Nhân Mất Tích Hoặc Chết">
  <data key="d0">Việc Xác Định Cá Nhân Mất Tích Hoặc Chết</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The determination of a missing or deceased individual is based on the laws of the country where the individual had citizenship at the time of the last known information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền Sở Hữu Và Quyền Khác Đối Với Tài Sản">
  <data key="d0">Quyền Sở Hữu Và Quyền Khác Đối Với Tài Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The establishment, exercise, modification, and termination of ownership and other rights over property are determined by the laws of the country where the property is located.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Đại Diện Theo Pháp Luật">
  <data key="d0">Người Đại Diện Theo Pháp Luật</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Đại Diện Theo Pháp Luật is a legal representative of a business entity who is responsible for acting in the best interest of the business.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Đại Diện Theo Pháp Luật is the legal representative of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851802</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Đại Diện Theo Ủy Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Người Đại Diện Theo Ủy Quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Đại Diện Theo Ủy Quyền is an authorized representative of the owners, members, or shareholders of a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851458</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thành Viên">
  <data key="d0">Thành Viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thành Viên is a member of a company who can authorize a representative.&lt;SEP&gt;Thành Viên is a member of the company who has a capital contribution and certain rights within the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Thành Viên refers to the members of a limited liability company, who can be organizations or individuals and are liable for the company's debts within the scope of their capital contributions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fef4d2c27b6430834254a2ffeefda111</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851865</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cổ Đông">
  <data key="d0">Cổ Đông</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cổ Đông is a shareholder of a company who can authorize a representative.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ Đông refers to the shareholders of the company who must provide updated contact information.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ Đông is a shareholder of the company who receives dividends and has rights related to the shares they own.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ Đông refers to shareholders who have the right to request changes in the shareholder register within 24 hours.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông refers to shareholders of a company who have the right to request the court to stop or revoke resolutions or decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ Đông refers to shareholders who may request the Tòa Án or Trọng Tài to invalidate a resolution of the Đại Hội Đồng Cổ Đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ Đông is a shareholder of a company who holds shares and has the right to participate in the company's decision-making process.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e71cfa12d80240b04312d94d8b626b87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af079df7102c58f84652bfeb21c7a17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-444a844ae4151849d71498d312b5d52d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a95c0aafb09aeaffa31c143eaf83c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853131</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ Chức">
  <data key="d0">Tổ Chức</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ Chức is an organization that can be a member or shareholder of a company and authorize representatives.&lt;SEP&gt;An organization that can be a recipient of the transfer of ownership of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851936</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Văn Bản Cử Người Đại Diện Theo Ủy Quyền">
  <data key="d0">Văn Bản Cử Người Đại Diện Theo Ủy Quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Văn Bản Cử Người Đại Diện Theo Ủy Quyền is a document that authorizes a representative and must be communicated to the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 13">
  <data key="d0">Điều 13</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 13 is a legal provision that outlines the responsibilities of the legal representative of a business entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 13 is a legal provision regarding the loss of the right to object in arbitration.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853604</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 14">
  <data key="d0">Điều 14</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 14 is a legal provision that specifies the conditions for the authorized representative of the owners, members, or shareholders of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 14 is a legal provision regarding the application of laws to resolve disputes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd4fb2094298c5037722675df8cc46f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853604</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 662">
  <data key="d0">Điều 662</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 662 is a legal provision that outlines the division of an estate when a new heir appears or an heir's right to inheritance is denied.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 663">
  <data key="d0">Điều 663</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 663 is a legal provision that defines the scope of application for laws governing civil relations with foreign elements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 664">
  <data key="d0">Điều 664</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 664 is a legal provision that specifies how to determine the applicable law for civil relations with foreign elements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 665">
  <data key="d0">Điều 665</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 665 is a legal provision that outlines the application of international treaties to civil relations with foreign elements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phân chia di sản">
  <data key="d0">Phân chia di sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phân chia di sản refers to the division of an estate among heirs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quan hệ dân sự có yếu tố nước ngoài">
  <data key="d0">Quan hệ dân sự có yếu tố nước ngoài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quan hệ dân sự có yếu tố nước ngoài refers to civil relations that involve foreign elements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Pháp luật áp dụng">
  <data key="d0">Pháp luật áp dụng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Pháp luật áp dụng refers to the applicable law for civil relations with foreign elements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hạn này">
  <data key="d0">Thời hạn này</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thời hạn này refers to the time limit for dividing an estate, which cannot exceed 3 years from the opening of the inheritance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="bên còn sống">
  <data key="d0">bên còn sống</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">bên còn sống is a surviving individual who can request an extension of the time limit for dividing an estate if it affects their family's livelihood.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="di sản">
  <data key="d0">di sản</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">di sản refers to the estate or inheritance that is to be divided among heirs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="quy định khác">
  <data key="d0">quy định khác</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">quy định khác refers to alternative agreements that may exist regarding the division of an estate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="cá nhân, pháp nhân nước ngoài">
  <data key="d0">cá nhân, pháp nhân nước ngoài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">cá nhân, pháp nhân nước ngoài refers to foreign individuals or entities involved in civil relations with foreign elements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="công dân Việt Nam, pháp nhân Việt Nam">
  <data key="d0">công dân Việt Nam, pháp nhân Việt Nam</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">công dân Việt Nam, pháp nhân Việt Nam refers to Vietnamese citizens or entities involved in civil relations with foreign elements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-651ba86aa84dcd7fdcb6fe6cfa6aacef</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851459</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ Chức Chính Trị">
  <data key="d0">Tổ Chức Chính Trị</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ Chức Chính Trị are political organizations that operate within enterprises according to the constitution, laws, and their own bylaws.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851498</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ Chức Chính Trị - Xã Hội">
  <data key="d0">Tổ Chức Chính Trị - Xã Hội</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ Chức Chính Trị - Xã Hội are political and social organizations that operate within enterprises according to the constitution, laws, and their own bylaws.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851498</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ Chức Đại Diện Người Lao Động">
  <data key="d0">Tổ Chức Đại Diện Người Lao Động</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ Chức Đại Diện Người Lao Động are labor representative organizations that operate within enterprises according to the constitution, laws, and their own bylaws.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851498</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Lao Động">
  <data key="d0">Người Lao Động</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Lao Động refers to employees who have the right to participate in labor organizations and are protected by the enterprise in terms of their legal rights and interests.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Lao Động are workers who have worked at a branch and whose rights must be legally addressed after the branch's closure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f6b7c08fc56b324472ca75d1984ba36</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vốn Đầu Tư">
  <data key="d0">Vốn Đầu Tư</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Vốn Đầu Tư refers to the legal investments of enterprises and their owners, which are protected by the law and cannot be nationalized or confiscated without proper compensation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851498</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thu Nhập">
  <data key="d0">Thu Nhập</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thu Nhập refers to the legal income of enterprises and their owners, which is protected by the law and cannot be nationalized or confiscated without proper compensation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851498</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Phân Chia Di Sản">
  <data key="d0">Người Phân Chia Di Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The person responsible for dividing the estate according to the will or the agreement of the heirs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851549</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Để Lại Di Sản">
  <data key="d0">Người Để Lại Di Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The person who left the estate and may have specified the division in their will.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851549</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thứ Tự Ưu Tiên Thanh Toán">
  <data key="d0">Thứ Tự Ưu Tiên Thanh Toán</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The order of priority for paying off debts and expenses related to the inheritance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851549</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phân Chia Di Sản Theo Di Chúc">
  <data key="d0">Phân Chia Di Sản Theo Di Chúc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The division of the estate according to the terms of the will.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851549</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phân Chia Di Sản Theo Pháp Luật">
  <data key="d0">Phân Chia Di Sản Theo Pháp Luật</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The division of the estate according to legal provisions when there is no will.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851549</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hạn Chế Phân Chia Di Sản">
  <data key="d0">Hạn Chế Phân Chia Di Sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Restrictions on the division of the estate, either by the will or by agreement of the heirs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851549</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
