<node id="Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh">
  <data key="d0">Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh, also known as the Business Registration Authority, is a government agency responsible for the registration and management of business entities in Vietnam. This organization reviews and processes changes in business registration content, including the registration of branches, representative offices, and business locations. It is also responsible for issuing the Certificate of Business Registration and reviewing registration documents. Additionally, Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh provides information on business registration content and updates information on changes in registered capital. The authority has the power to reject proposed business names based on specific regulations. It plays a crucial role in ensuring the proper registration and management of businesses within the jurisdiction and updates their legal status in the National Database on Business Registration. The agency is also responsible for registering the conversion of companies and issuing business registration certificates.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh is an organization responsible for registering businesses, issuing certificates, managing information systems, and supervising businesses.&lt;SEP&gt;The business registration authority is responsible for announcing the dissolution process and updating the legal status of the business.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh is an authority responsible for registering businesses and receiving reports from them.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8da64b48c80fc4788c324e08350a340e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a657b345d0676b5a5d6451a2c7c13d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0359f960f337b0c62d24c54f784fc5c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a788d203fae6d3c78c81ae71ea9171e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09d578fe732c3cb08c15e944096d74cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cổ đông sáng lập">
  <data key="d0">Cổ đông sáng lập</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cổ đông sáng lập refers to the founding shareholders of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông sáng lập are the founding shareholders of a company who have specific rights and obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông sáng lập refers to the founding shareholders of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852511</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cổ đông là nhà đầu tư nước ngoài">
  <data key="d0">Cổ đông là nhà đầu tư nước ngoài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cổ đông là nhà đầu tư nước ngoài refers to foreign investors who are shareholders in a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851613</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ngành, nghề kinh doanh">
  <data key="d0">Ngành, nghề kinh doanh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Ngành, nghề kinh do doanh refers to the business sectors or industries in which a company operates.&lt;SEP&gt;Ngành, nghề kinh doanh refers to the business sectors and industries in which a company operates.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851714</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sổ đăng ký cổ đông">
  <data key="d0">Sổ đăng ký cổ đông</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Sổ đăng ký cổ đông is the shareholder register of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Sổ đăng ký cổ đông is the shareholder register where information about shareholders is recorded.&lt;SEP&gt;Sổ đăng ký cổ đông is a shareholder register that records information about the ownership of shares in a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Sổ đăng ký cổ đông is a register that records the ownership of shares in a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Sổ đăng ký cổ đông is a register maintained by the company that contains information about shareholders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4c6a296c5e1b248b6b79c98f9b16e6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852660</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
