</node>
<node id="Trụ sở chính">
  <data key="d0">Trụ sở chính</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trụ sở chính refers to the main office or headquarters of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Trụ sở chính is the main office of a business entity, located within the territory of Vietnam, and serves as the contact address for the business.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851869</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 25">
  <data key="d0">Điều 25</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 25 is a regulation concerning the list of company members and shareholders for various types of companies.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 25 is a section of the law that specifies the registration process for arbitration centers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1881019a36e766412bad88d7a1e3d088</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853762</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 26">
  <data key="d0">Điều 26</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 26 is a regulation concerning the procedures for registering a business.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 26 is a section of the law that outlines the public announcement process for newly established arbitration centers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1881019a36e766412bad88d7a1e3d088</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853762</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The Chairman of the Board of Members, known in Vietnamese as "Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên," is the chairperson of the company's governing body, the Hội đồng thành viên. This individual is responsible for convening and leading meetings, making decisions, and ensuring the company adheres to legal standards and its charter. The Chairman is appointed by the company owner or elected by the board members and plays a crucial role in organizing the collection of opinions and ensuring the accuracy of reports. Additionally, the Chairman is tasked with signing the amended company charter for a partnership company, thereby ensuring the company's legal interests and compliance with the law.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên is the chairperson of the governing body of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên is the chairperson of the board of members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7934cedd8a058c40a35091be7e3f1c17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853534</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cổng thông tin quốc gia về đăng ký doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Cổng thông tin quốc gia về đăng ký doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">The National Business Registration Information Portal is an organization responsible for registering businesses through electronic means.&lt;SEP&gt;The National Portal for Business Registration is a platform where business registration information is publicly announced.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổng thông tin quốc gia về đăng ký doanh nghiệp is the national portal for business registration.&lt;SEP&gt;The national portal for business registration is where the dissolution process is announced.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853649</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hệ thống thông tin quốc gia về đăng ký doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Hệ thống thông tin quốc gia về đăng ký doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">The National Business Registration Information System is an organization responsible for creating business registration accounts.&lt;SEP&gt;The National Information System for Business Registration is a system where business registration information is stored and accessed.&lt;SEP&gt;Hệ thống thông tin quốc gia về đăng ký doanh nghiệp is a national information system for business registration managed by the Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09d578fe732c3cb08c15e944096d74cd</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853595</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài khoản đăng ký kinh doanh">
  <data key="d0">Tài khoản đăng ký kinh doanh</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">The Business Registration Account is an account created by the National Business Registration Information System for individuals to register businesses through electronic means.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chữ ký số">
  <data key="d0">Chữ ký số</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Digital Signature is a method of signing documents electronically.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Danh sách thành viên công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn">
  <data key="d0">Danh sách thành viên công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The list of members of a limited liability company is a required document that includes personal details and contributions of each member.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Danh sách thành viên công ty hợp danh">
  <data key="d0">Danh sách thành viên công ty hợp danh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The list of members of a partnership company is a required document that includes personal details and contributions of each member.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Danh sách cổ đông sáng lập">
  <data key="d0">Danh sách cổ đông sáng lập</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The list of founding shareholders is a required document that includes personal details and contributions of each founding shareholder.&lt;SEP&gt;Danh sách cổ đông sáng lập is the list of founding shareholders of a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851714</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Danh sách cổ đông là nhà đầu tư nước ngoài">
  <data key="d0">Danh sách cổ đông là nhà đầu tư nước ngoài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The list of foreign investor shareholders is a required document that includes personal details and contributions of each foreign investor shareholder.&lt;SEP&gt;Danh sách cổ đông là nhà đầu tư nước ngoài is the list of foreign investor shareholders in a joint-stock company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851714</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phần vốn góp">
  <data key="d0">Phần vốn góp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Capital contribution is the amount of capital each member or shareholder contributes to the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Phần vốn góp refers to the capital contribution of a member in a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Phần vốn góp refers to the capital contribution, which must be conducted through accounts as per foreign exchange management regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Capital contribution made by members of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Phần vốn góp refers to the share of capital that a member contributes to the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Part of the capital contribution refers to the portion of the capital that has been returned or distributed as profit.&lt;SEP&gt;Phần vốn góp is a contribution of capital to the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7934cedd8a058c40a35091be7e3f1c17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853244</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giá trị vốn góp">
  <data key="d0">Giá trị vốn góp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The value of the capital contribution is the monetary value of the capital each member or shareholder contributes to the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tỷ lệ sở hữu phần vốn góp">
  <data key="d0">Tỷ lệ sở hữu phần vốn góp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The ownership ratio of the capital contribution is the percentage of the total capital that each member or shareholder owns.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Loại tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Loại tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The type of asset is the category of assets contributed by members or shareholders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Số lượng tài sản">
  <data key="d0">Số lượng tài sản</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The quantity of assets is the number of assets contributed by members or shareholders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giá trị của từng loại tài sản góp vốn">
  <data key="d0">Giá trị của từng loại tài sản góp vốn</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The value of each type of asset contributed is the monetary value of each type of asset contributed by members or shareholders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thời hạn góp vốn">
  <data key="d0">Thời hạn góp vốn</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The contribution period is the time frame within which members or shareholders must contribute their capital.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Số lượng cổ phần">
  <data key="d0">Số lượng cổ phần</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The number of shares is the quantity of shares held by each shareholder.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Loại cổ phần">
  <data key="d0">Loại cổ phần</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The type of share is the category of shares held by each shareholder.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tỷ lệ sở hữu cổ phần">
  <data key="d0">Tỷ lệ sở hữu cổ phần</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The ownership ratio of shares is the percentage of the total shares that each shareholder owns.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
