<node id="Chuyển quyền sở hữu tài sản góp vốn">
  <data key="d0">Chuyển quyền sở hữu tài sản góp vốn</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The transfer of ownership of capital contribution assets is a process where members or shareholders transfer their ownership rights to the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851713</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Biên bản giao nhận tài sản góp vốn">
  <data key="d0">Biên bản giao nhận tài sản góp vốn</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">The Capital Contribution Asset Transfer Record is a document that includes key information about the transfer of ownership of capital contribution assets.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851714</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ doanh nghiệp tư nhân">
  <data key="d0">Chủ doanh nghiệp tư nhân</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The owner of a private enterprise is responsible for using assets in business activities without the need to transfer ownership to the business.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ doanh nghiệp tư nhân is the owner of a private enterprise who makes the decision to convert the enterprise into another type of company.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ doanh nghiệp tư nhân is the owner of a private enterprise who is personally responsible for all debts incurred before the conversion of the enterprise into a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ doanh nghiệp tư nhân is the owner of a private business entity.&lt;SEP&gt;The owner of a private business is responsible for the accuracy of the dissolution file.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8da64b48c80fc4788c324e08350a340e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853649</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nhà đầu tư nước ngoài">
  <data key="d0">Nhà đầu tư nước ngoài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Foreign investors are required to conduct transactions through accounts as per foreign exchange management regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Nhà đầu tư nước ngoài refers to foreign investors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4c6a296c5e1b248b6b79c98f9b16e6d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852595</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phí">
  <data key="d0">Phí</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phí refers to the fees that must be paid by organizations and individuals for various services related to business registration and information provision.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851714</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền sử dụng đất">
  <data key="d0">Quyền sử dụng đất</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyền sử dụng đất refers to the rights to use land as a form of capital contribution.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyền sử dụng đất refers to the right to use land as a form of payment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852748</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công nghệ">
  <data key="d0">Công nghệ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công nghệ refers to technology that can be used as a capital contribution asset.&lt;SEP&gt;Công nghệ refers to technology used as a form of payment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852748</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
