<node id="Sổ Đăng Ký Thành Viên">
  <data key="d0">Sổ Đăng Ký Thành Viên</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Sổ Đăng Ký Thành Viên is a register maintained by a company to record the ownership of capital contributions by its members, which can be in the form of paper documents or electronic data.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851802</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giấy Chứng Nhận Phần Vốn Góp">
  <data key="d0">Giấy Chứng Nhận Phần Vốn Góp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Giấy Chứng Nhận Phần Vốn Góp is a certificate issued by a company to its members, indicating their capital contribution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851802</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hội Đồng Thành Viên">
  <data key="d0">Hội Đồng Thành Viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hội Đồng Thành Viên is a body within a company that has the authority to make decisions and has members with specific rights and responsibilities.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội Đồng Thành Viên is the governing body of a company, consisting of all members, and has the authority to make decisions on all business matters of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The board of members responsible for making decisions to divide a company.&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Members is responsible for passing resolutions and decisions to split the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội Đồng Thành Viên is the board of members that makes decisions and oversees the company's operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-925f6a057b7d8e551fd4f47576508ca0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aff8a680816d92d14d4a77e34dbfc7d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-111878a66be557377de6fec57d456ed2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công Ty">
  <data key="d0">Công Ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công Ty is a legal entity that maintains the Sổ Đăng Ký Thành Viên, which records shareholder information, and issues Giấy Chứng Nhận Phần Vốn Góp to its members. As a company, it is subject to its charter and the laws of the jurisdiction in which it operates. The company is responsible for updating shareholder information and managing the sale of shares. It must comply with regulations regarding the repurchase and payment of shares, as well as the issuance and transfer of private bonds. Additionally, Công Ty has the authority to increase the number of shares and sell them to existing shareholders. The company has a structured organizational framework, including shareholders and a board of directors, and is governed by specific regulations that define its management and operations. Members of the company have rights and obligations within this structure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e71cfa12d80240b04312d94d8b626b87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af079df7102c58f84652bfeb21c7a17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e31bb2a60b0c3b80bacb62410231f646&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-444a844ae4151849d71498d312b5d52d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-111878a66be557377de6fec57d456ed2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853430</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ Tịch Hội Đồng Thành Viên">
  <data key="d0">Chủ Tịch Hội Đồng Thành Viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ Tịch Hội Đồng Thành Viên is the chairperson of the Hội Đồng Thành Viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ Tịch Hội Đồng Thành Viên is the chairperson of the governing body of a company, responsible for convening meetings and making decisions on business matters.&lt;SEP&gt;The Chairman of the Board of Members is elected or appointed by the members of the new company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-925f6a057b7d8e551fd4f47576508ca0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853308</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giám Đốc">
  <data key="d0">Giám Đốc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Giám Đốc is the director or manager of a company, responsible for overseeing the company's operations and making strategic decisions. This senior management position is appointed by the Hội Đồng Quản Trị, which translates to the Board of Directors, to manage the daily business operations. The role of Giám Đốc involves ensuring that the company's operations run smoothly and that strategic decisions are made effectively. Additionally, the position requires the director to separate personal expenses from the company's finances, maintaining a clear distinction between personal and professional financial matters. The Giám Đốc can be appointed or elected by the governing body or members of the company, emphasizing the importance of the role in the overall management and success of the organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af079df7102c58f84652bfeb21c7a17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a95c0aafb09aeaffa31c143eaf83c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-925f6a057b7d8e551fd4f47576508ca0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d59be88d8f39c9fce708d8b3f0c8014&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853313</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổng Giám Đốc">
  <data key="d0">Tổng Giám Đốc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổng Giám Đốc, which translates to General Director, is a senior management position within a company. This individual is appointed by the Hội Đồng Quản Trị, or the Board of Directors, to oversee daily business operations and make strategic decisions. The General Director is responsible for the company's operations and management, ensuring that personal expenses are separated from the company's financial activities. This role involves managing the company's operations and making key strategic decisions that impact the company's direction and success. The General Director may be appointed or elected by the governing body of the company, reflecting the importance of this position in the overall governance and operational success of the organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af079df7102c58f84652bfeb21c7a17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a95c0aafb09aeaffa31c143eaf83c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-925f6a057b7d8e551fd4f47576508ca0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d59be88d8f39c9fce708d8b3f0c8014&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853315</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Quản Lý Khác">
  <data key="d0">Người Quản Lý Khác</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người Quản Lý Khác refers to other managers within the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Quản Lý Khác refers to other management personnel within a company who are responsible for overseeing specific areas or departments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853130</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hội đồng Thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Hội đồng Thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hội đồng Thành viên is a governing body within a company responsible for making decisions and overseeing the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng Thành viên is a governing body within a company that makes decisions and passes resolutions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghị quyết">
  <data key="d0">Nghị quyết</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghị quyết refers to the resolutions or decisions made by the governing bodies of a company, such as the Hội đồng Thành viên (Board of Members) or the Đại hội đồng cổ đông (General Shareholders' Meeting). These resolutions cover a range of topics, including changes in the company's capital. A Nghị quyết can also be passed through written shareholder opinions, which hold the same value as those passed during the General Shareholders' Meeting. Once a resolution is passed, it must be communicated to the shareholders within 15 days after the vote concludes and can be published on the company's electronic information page.&lt;SEP&gt;Nghị quyết is a resolution or decision document used in the process of dissolving a business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853534</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền và Nghĩa vụ">
  <data key="d0">Quyền và Nghĩa vụ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyền và Nghĩa vụ refers to the rights and obligations of the members of the company as defined by the law and the company's charter.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851807</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sổ đăng ký thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Sổ đăng ký thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Sổ đăng ký thành viên is the register that records the information of the company members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851807</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghĩa vụ của thành viên Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Nghĩa vụ của thành viên Hội đồng thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghĩa vụ của thành viên Hội đồng thành viên refers to the obligations of the members of the Board of Members as defined in the law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851808</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Mua lại phần vốn góp">
  <data key="d0">Mua lại phần vốn góp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Mua lại phần vốn góp refers to the process of a company repurchasing a member's share of capital.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851808</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chuyển nhượng phần vốn góp">
  <data key="d0">Chuyển nhượng phần vốn góp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chuyển nhượng phần vốn góp refers to the transfer of a member's share of capital to another party.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851808</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ tịch Hội đồng Thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Chủ tịch Hội đồng Thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ tịch Hội đồng Thành viên is the chairperson of the company's governing body, responsible for convening meetings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cuộc họp Hội đồng Thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Cuộc họp Hội đồng Thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Cuộc họp Hội đồng Thành viên refers to the meetings held by the governing body of a company to make decisions and pass resolutions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nghị quyết, quyết định">
  <data key="d0">Nghị quyết, quyết định</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nghị quyết, quyết định are the resolutions and decisions made by the governing body of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Nghị quyết, quyết định are the resolutions and decisions made by the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Nghị quyết, quyết định refers to resolutions or decisions made by the Board of Members, which can be passed through written ballots if approved by members holding at least 65% of the company's charter capital.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852147</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Báo cáo tài chính hằng năm">
  <data key="d0">Báo cáo tài chính hằng năm</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Báo cáo tài chính hằng năm is the annual financial report of the company that is approved by the governing body.&lt;SEP&gt;Báo cáo tài chính hằng năm is the annual financial report of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Báo cáo tài chính hằng năm refers to annual financial reports submitted to the governing body.&lt;SEP&gt;Báo cáo tài chính hằng năm is the annual financial report of a company that includes information on the company's financial performance and position.&lt;SEP&gt;Báo cáo tài chính hằng năm is the annual financial report of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853244</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ chức lại, giải thể công ty">
  <data key="d0">Tổ chức lại, giải thể công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ chức lại, giải thể công ty refers to the restructuring or dissolution of the company, which requires a resolution by the governing body.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="65% Vốn Điều Lệ">
  <data key="d0">65% Vốn Điều Lệ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">65% Vốn Điều Lệ is the minimum percentage of capital ownership required for a meeting to be valid.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="50% Vốn Điều Lệ">
  <data key="d0">50% Vốn Điều Lệ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">50% Vốn Điều Lệ is the minimum percentage of capital ownership required for the second meeting to be valid.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="75% Vốn Điều Lệ">
  <data key="d0">75% Vốn Điều Lệ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">75% Vốn Điều Lệ is the minimum percentage of capital ownership required for certain critical decisions to be valid.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cơ Quan Đăng Ký Kinh Doanh">
  <data key="d0">Cơ Quan Đăng Ký Kinh Doanh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ Quan Đăng Ký Kinh Doanh is the authority responsible for approving or rejecting the proposed names of businesses.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ Quan Đăng Ký Kinh Doanh is the authority responsible for registering businesses and their activities.&lt;SEP&gt;The agency responsible for registering businesses and updating the national database.&lt;SEP&gt;The Business Registration Authority is responsible for registering the new companies and updating the legal status of the company being split.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fef4d2c27b6430834254a2ffeefda111&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aff8a680816d92d14d4a77e34dbfc7d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853309</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên Doanh Nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Tên Doanh Nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tên Doanh Nghiệp is the name of a business entity, which must be unique and cannot overlap with existing names.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên Viết Tắt">
  <data key="d0">Tên Viết Tắt</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tên Viết Tắt is the abbreviated name of a business entity, derived from its full Vietnamese name or its foreign language name.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên Chi Nhánh">
  <data key="d0">Tên Chi Nhánh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tên Chi Nhánh is the name of a branch of a business entity, which must include the name of the business and the term "Chi nhánh".</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên Văn Phòng Đại Diện">
  <data key="d0">Tên Văn Phòng Đại Diện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tên Văn Phòng Đại Diện is the name of a representative office of a business entity, which must include the name of the business and the term "Văn phòng đại diện".</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên Địa Điểm Kinh Doanh">
  <data key="d0">Tên Địa Điểm Kinh Doanh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tên Địa Điểm Kinh Doanh is the name of a business location, which must include the name of the business and the term "Địa điểm kinh doanh".</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên Trùng">
  <data key="d0">Tên Trùng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tên Trùng refers to identical names of business entities, which are prohibited.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên Gây Nhầm Lẫn">
  <data key="d0">Tên Gây Nhầm Lẫn</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tên Gây Nhầm Lẫn refers to names that are similar to existing business names, which are also prohibited.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 38">
  <data key="d0">Điều 38</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 38 is a regulation that outlines the prohibitions on naming businesses, including the use of names that are identical or confusingly similar to existing business names.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 39">
  <data key="d0">Điều 39</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 39 is a regulation that specifies the rules for naming businesses in foreign languages and the use of abbreviated names.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 40">
  <data key="d0">Điều 40</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 40 is a regulation that outlines the naming rules for branches, representative offices, and business locations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851843</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 41">
  <data key="d0">Điều 41</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Đиều 41 is a regulation that defines what constitutes identical and confusingly similar business names.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 41 is a regulation that outlines the procedures for forming an arbitration panel and appointing arbitrators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853974</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều  40">
  <data key="d0">Điều  40</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 40 outlines the naming rules for branches, representative offices, and business locations.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851844</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công Ty Trách Nhiệm Hữu Hạn Hai Thành Viên Trở Lên">
  <data key="d0">Công Ty Trách Nhiệm Hữu Hạn Hai Thành Viên Trở Lên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công Ty Trách Nhiệm Hữu Hạn Hai Thành Viên Trở Lên is a limited liability company with 2 to 50 members, which can be organizations or individuals, and has legal entity status from the date of receiving the business registration certificate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fef4d2c27b6430834254a2ffeefda111</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851865</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giấy Chứng Nhận Đăng Ký Hoạt Động Chi Nhánh">
  <data key="d0">Giấy Chứng Nhận Đăng Ký Hoạt Động Chi Nhánh</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Giấy Chứng Nhận Đăng Ký Hoạt Động Chi Nhánh is a certificate for registering the activities of a branch or representative office.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fef4d2c27b6430834254a2ffeefda111</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851865</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giấy Chứng Nhận Đăng Ký Doanh Nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Giấy Chứng Nhận Đăng Ký Doanh Nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Giấy Chứng Nhận Đăng Ký Doanh Nghiệp is a business registration certificate that grants legal entity status to a limited liability company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fef4d2c27b6430834254a2ffeefda111</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851865</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dấu">
  <data key="d0">Dấu</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Dấu is a seal or digital signature used by a business entity in transactions, the type, quantity, form, and content of which are determined by the business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851869</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chi nhánh">
  <data key="d0">Chi nhánh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chi nhánh is a branch of a business entity that performs all or part of the business entity's functions, including representation.&lt;SEP&gt;Chi nhánh refers to branches of a business that can be terminated by the business itself or by the government.&lt;SEP&gt;Chi nhánh is a branch of a foreign arbitration organization operating in Vietnam.&lt;SEP&gt;Chi nhánh is a branch of a foreign arbitration organization established in Vietnam.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44b958e89c37ebae08442548c41df280</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854043</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Địa điểm kinh doanh">
  <data key="d0">Địa điểm kinh doanh</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Địa điểm kinh doanh is the location where a business entity conducts specific business activities.&lt;SEP&gt;Địa điểm kinh doanh refers to business locations that can be terminated by the business itself or by the government.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853535</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hồ sơ đăng ký hoạt động">
  <data key="d0">Hồ sơ đăng ký hoạt động</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Hồ sơ đăng ký hoạt động is the registration file submitted by a business entity to the registration authority for the establishment of branches or representative offices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851869</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký hoạt động">
  <data key="d0">Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký hoạt động</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký hoạt động is the registration certificate issued by the registration authority to a business entity for the establishment of branches or representative offices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851869</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công ty">
  <data key="d0">Công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công ty refers to a business entity that operates under a defined governance structure and is subject to various legal and regulatory requirements. It has a governing body responsible for convening meetings and making decisions. The company can adjust its registered capital, either by increasing or decreasing it, and distribute profits to its members. The management structure of Công ty includes one or more Deputy Directors or Deputy General Directors, whose number and authority are specified in the company's charter. The responsibilities of the managers and representatives of the company are clearly defined, ensuring that the entity operates in accordance with its governance principles.

Công ty is also required to comply with legal obligations, such as publishing regular and abnormal information as mandated by law. Additionally, the company must disclose contracts and related transactions as per the relevant laws. The regulations that govern Công ty include provisions for the payment of dividends and the overall management structure, ensuring transparency and accountability in its operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty is a business entity, and Kiểm soát viên can be a manager or employee of the company unless the company's charter specifies otherwise.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty is a business entity that can accept new members and is subject to the regulations outlined in the text.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty is an entity that can inherit rights and obligations from a private enterprise upon conversion.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-373a8f0d009c4c6073d5e556bc2411e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853315</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chi phí hợp lý">
  <data key="d0">Chi phí hợp lý</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chi phí hợp lý refers to the reasonable costs associated with convening and conducting meetings of the company's governing body.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Kiến nghị">
  <data key="d0">Kiến nghị</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Kiến nghị refers to the proposals or suggestions made by members to add items to the agenda of the company's governing body meetings.&lt;SEP&gt;Kiến nghị refers to proposals submitted by shareholders or groups of shareholders to be included in the agenda of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Kiến nghị refers to proposals or suggestions that must be included in the agenda and content of the meeting, unless specified otherwise.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c9b32b2b806556ed1dd36c13de6e313</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852721</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thông báo mời họp">
  <data key="d0">Thông báo mời họp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thông báo mời họp refers to the notice or invitation sent to members to attend meetings of the company's governing body.&lt;SEP&gt;The meeting invitation notice is a document that must be stored at the main office of the company along with the minutes of the meeting and resolutions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852634</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 36">
  <data key="d0">Điều 36</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 36 is a regulation concerning the valuation of assets contributed to capital.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 37">
  <data key="d0">Điều 37</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 37 is a regulation concerning the naming of businesses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nguyên tắc đồng thuận">
  <data key="d0">Nguyên tắc đồng thuận</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nguyên tắc đồng thuận is a principle of consensus used in the valuation of assets contributed to capital.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ chức thẩm định giá">
  <data key="d0">Tổ chức thẩm định giá</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ chức thẩm định giá is an organization responsible for valuing assets contributed to capital.&lt;SEP&gt;Tổ chức thẩm định giá is an organization that provides valuation services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852749</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tài liệu họp">
  <data key="d0">Tài liệu họp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tài liệu họp refers to the documents and materials used during meetings of the company's governing body.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đồng Việt Nam">
  <data key="d0">Đồng Việt Nam</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đồng Việt Nam is the national currency of Vietnam.&lt;SEP&gt;Đồng Việt Nam is the national currency of Vietnam used for transactions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852748</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ngoại tệ tự do chuyển đổi">
  <data key="d0">Ngoại tệ tự do chuyển đổi</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Ngoại tệ tự do chuyển đổi refers to freely convertible foreign currencies.&lt;SEP&gt;Ngoại tệ tự do chuyển đổi refers to freely convertible foreign currencies used for transactions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852748</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vàng">
  <data key="d0">Vàng</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Vàng refers to gold, which is subject to valuation regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Vàng refers to gold used as a form of payment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852748</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tên doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Tên doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 37 regulates the naming of businesses.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851903</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ Sở Hữu Công Ty">
  <data key="d0">Chủ Sở Hữu Công Ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The owner of the company has rights and obligations as defined by the law, including contributing capital, making business decisions, and managing internal affairs.&lt;SEP&gt;The owner of a company who can decide on the increase or decrease of the registered capital.&lt;SEP&gt;The owner of a company who can make decisions to divide the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aff8a680816d92d14d4a77e34dbfc7d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853233</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ Tịch Công Ty">
  <data key="d0">Chủ Tịch Công Ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The Chairman of the company is a position that the owner must separate personal expenses from.&lt;SEP&gt;The Chairman of the Company is elected or appointed by the members of the new company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853308</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều Lê Công Ty">
  <data key="d0">Điều Lê Công Ty</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The company charter is a document that the owner must comply with and can specify different rules for internal management.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851936</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người Đại Diện">
  <data key="d0">Người Đại Diện</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A representative who can act on behalf of the owner if they are incapacitated or have limited legal capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Đại Diện is the representative of a party in the dispute resolution meeting.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a36e099bae803eeaad0a5160e83464d5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853928</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ tịch công ty">
  <data key="d0">Chủ tịch công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ tịch công ty is the chairman of the company, one of the roles that can be held by a person representing the company legally.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch công ty is the chairman of the company who is part of the management structure of state-owned enterprises.&lt;SEP&gt;The Chairman of the company is appointed by the company owner and acts on behalf of the owner and the company, except for the rights and obligations of the General Director or CEO.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch công ty is the Chairman of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;The Chairman of the company is appointed by the representative body of the owner and has a term of no more than 5 years, with the possibility of reappointment.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch công ty is the chairman of the company, responsible for leading and managing the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852453</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giám đốc">
  <data key="d0">Giám đốc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Giám đốc is the director of a company, a leadership position within the organization responsible for managing the daily business operations. This role is held by a person who represents the company legally and is part of the management structure, particularly in state-owned enterprises. The Director is appointed by the Board of Members or the Chairman of the company and is tasked with ensuring the company's legal interests and adherence to the law and the company's charter. The position requires specific qualifications, and the individual cannot be related to certain company officials. The Hội đồng thành viên, or Board of Members, can request information from the Giám đốc, highlighting the role's accountability and transparency requirements. Overall, the Giám đốc plays a crucial role in the governance and operational management of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Giám đốc is a senior manager in a company who is responsible for the overall management and operations of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Giám đốc is a position within a company, and Kiểm soát viên cannot be a family member of the Giám đốc.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853165</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổng giám đốc">
  <data key="d0">Tổng giám đốc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổng giám đốc, which translates to General Director, is a leadership position within a company, particularly in state-owned enterprises. This role is held by an individual who represents the company legally and is appointed by the Board of Members or the Chairman of the company. The General Director is responsible for managing the company's daily business operations and ensuring that the company's legal interests are protected while adhering to the law and the company's charter.

The General Director must meet specific qualifications and cannot have certain relationships with other company officials. Additionally, the General Director can be requested to provide information by the Hội đồng thành viên, which is the Board of Members. This position involves specific duties and responsibilities that are crucial for the effective operation and legal compliance of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Tổng giám đốc is the highest-ranking executive in a company, responsible for making major corporate decisions and managing the overall operations of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Tổng giám đốc is a senior management position within a company, and Kiểm soát viên cannot be a family member of the Tổng giám đốc.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853165</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Kiểm soát viên">
  <data key="d0">Kiểm soát viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Kiểm soát viên is a member of the Ban kiểm soát, also known as the Supervisory Board, responsible for overseeing the company's operations and ensuring compliance with the law, the company charter, and the decisions of the company owner. This position involves supervising and controlling the company's operations, ensuring the company's legal interests, and adhering to regulations. Kiểm soát viên must meet specific qualifications and cannot be related to certain company officials. As a member of the Supervisory Board, the Kiểm soát viên has the right to attend Board meetings, discuss matters, and access information and reports from the company, although they do not have the right to vote. Their role is crucial in ensuring that the company operates within legal and regulatory frameworks and that the company's interests are protected.&lt;SEP&gt;Kiểm soát viên is a member of the Ban kiểm soát with a term not exceeding 5 years and can be re-elected without limitation.&lt;SEP&gt;Kiểm soát viên is a role within a company responsible for monitoring and ensuring compliance with regulations and duties.&lt;SEP&gt;Kiểm soát viên is a position with specific qualifications and responsibilities, including continuing duties until a new Kiểm soát viên is elected.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ec32bc0d8c57985cdac3f5a1383a2dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-373a8f0d009c4c6073d5e556bc2411e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853165</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="cá nhân">
  <data key="d0">cá nhân</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A cá nhân refers to an individual who may be prohibited from certain activities or businesses by the court.&lt;SEP&gt;cá nhân refers to an individual who may be subject to legal penalties for violating regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="pháp nhân thương mại">
  <data key="d0">pháp nhân thương mại</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A pháp nhân thương mại is a commercial legal entity that may be prohibited from certain business activities by the court.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851942</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều  78">
  <data key="d0">Điều  78</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b489c4747b69390bb9811e4c1b6ee278</data>
  <data key="d2">The owner of the company has rights and obligations in special circumstances as outlined in Article 78, such as transfer of ownership or incapacitation.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851943</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chi phí khởi kiện">
  <data key="d0">Chi phí khởi kiện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The costs associated with initiating a lawsuit, which may be covered by the company under certain conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851973</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyền của chủ sở hữu công ty">
  <data key="d0">Quyền của chủ sở hữu công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The rights of the company owner, which include decision-making powers over various aspects of the company's operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851973</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trình tự, thủ tục khởi kiện">
  <data key="d0">Trình tự, thủ tục khởi kiện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The sequence and procedures for initiating a lawsuit are governed by civil litigation laws.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851973</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
