  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The legal framework governing civil litigation procedures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851973</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bị bác yêu cầu khởi kiện">
  <data key="d0">Bị bác yêu cầu khởi kiện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The scenario where a lawsuit request is rejected.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851973</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công ty Trách Nhiệm Hữu Hạn Một Thành Viên">
  <data key="d0">Công ty Trách Nhiệm Hữu Hạn Một Thành Viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A company with a single shareholder, which can increase or decrease its registered capital through the shareholder's contributions or by raising additional capital from other individuals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851979</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giao Dịch">
  <data key="d0">Giao Dịch</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Transactions between the company and its owner or related individuals must be recorded and kept as a separate file of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851979</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Doanh Nghiệp Nhà Nước">
  <data key="d0">Doanh Nghiệp Nhà Nước</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A state-owned enterprise that can be managed under the form of a limited liability company or a joint-stock company.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh Nghiệp Nhà Nước is a state-owned enterprise with specific regulations regarding the qualifications of board members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-444a844ae4151849d71498d312b5d52d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853023</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tập Đoàn Kinh Tế Nhà Nước">
  <data key="d0">Tập Đoàn Kinh Tế Nhà Nước</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A state-owned economic group managed under the form of a limited liability company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851979</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổng Công Ty Nhà Nước">
  <data key="d0">Tổng Công Ty Nhà Nước</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A state-owned corporation managed under the form of a limited liability company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chính Phủ">
  <data key="d0">Chính Phủ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The government, which specifies the detailed regulations for state-owned enterprises.&lt;SEP&gt;Chính Phủ is the governmental body that provides detailed regulations for the actions of parent and subsidiary companies.&lt;SEP&gt;Chính Phủ is the government entity responsible for providing detailed regulations for the law.&lt;SEP&gt;Chính Phủ is the central government body that oversees the management of enterprises.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b12f2587388d6a4e9e558de512dc2860&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f6b7c08fc56b324472ca75d1984ba36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5a052d442484a7e21099fd9dda00e96</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853724</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tập Đoàn Kinh Tế">
  <data key="d0">Tập Đoàn Kinh Tế</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">An economic group that can be managed under the form of a limited liability company or a joint-stock company.&lt;SEP&gt;An economic group or holding company is a group of companies with interrelated ownership through shares or other forms of association.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d59be88d8f39c9fce708d8b3f0c8014</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853269</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công Ty Mẹ - Công Ty Con">
  <data key="d0">Công Ty Mẹ - Công Ty Con</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">A parent company and its subsidiary, which can be managed under the form of a limited liability company or a joint-stock company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công Ty Độc Lập">
  <data key="d0">Công Ty Độc Lập</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">An independent company that can be managed under the form of a limited liability company or a joint-stock company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công Ty Trách Nhiệm Hữu Hạn Một Thành Viên">
  <data key="d0">Công Ty Trách Nhiệm Hữu Hạn Một Thành Viên</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
  <data key="d2">The owner of a company can decide on the increase or decrease of the registered capital.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773851980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Doanh nghiệp Nhà nước">
  <data key="d0">Doanh nghiệp Nhà nước</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Doanh nghiệp Nhà nước refers to state-owned enterprises that hold more than 50% of the registered capital and are managed under the form of limited liability companies or joint-stock companies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852015</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cơ quan đại diện chủ sở hữu">
  <data key="d0">Cơ quan đại diện chủ sở hữu</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ quan đại diện chủ sở hữu is the entity responsible for deciding the management structure of state-owned enterprises.&lt;SEP&gt;The representative body of the owner is the entity to which reports of violations are submitted.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đại diện chủ sở hữu is the entity representing the owners of the company and has the authority to make certain decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đại diện chủ sở hữu is the body representing the company's owners and is responsible for overseeing the company's management.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852453</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quy định khác của pháp luật có liên quan">
  <data key="d0">Quy định khác của pháp luật có liên quan</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quy định khác của pháp luật có liên quan refers to other related legal provisions that govern the operations of state-owned enterprises.&lt;SEP&gt;Other related legal regulations that define the responsibilities of the Board of Members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 93">
  <data key="d0">Điều 93</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 93 is a legal provision that sets the criteria and conditions for the members of the Hội đồng thành viên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852016</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyết định của Chủ tịch công ty">
  <data key="d0">Quyết định của Chủ tịch công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">The decision of the Chairman of the company regarding the rights and obligations of the company owner becomes effective upon approval by the company owner.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852022</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Biên bản họp Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Biên bản họp Hội đồng thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">The minutes of the Board of Members meeting must be recorded and kept in electronic form.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852022</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quy chế quản lý nội bộ của công ty">
  <data key="d0">Quy chế quản lý nội bộ của công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The internal management regulations of the company are established by the Director or General Director.&lt;SEP&gt;The company's internal management regulations define the rules for internal management, including delegation of authority.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852365</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hợp đồng lao động">
  <data key="d0">Hợp đồng lao động</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">The labor contract defines the rights and obligations of the Director or General Director.&lt;SEP&gt;Hợp đồng lao động refers to employment contracts within the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Employment contracts signed between the company and its employees.&lt;SEP&gt;Hợp đồng lao động is a labor contract that is part of the obligations and liabilities inherited by the company after conversion.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8da64b48c80fc4788c324e08350a340e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853285</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyết định của Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Quyết định của Hội đồng thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">The decision of the Board of Members regarding the rights and obligations of the company owner becomes effective upon approval by the company owner.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852022</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ tịch và thành viên khác của Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Chủ tịch và thành viên khác của Hội đồng thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ tịch and other members of the Board of Members are responsible for adhering to the company's charter, the owner's decisions, and legal regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trụ sở chính của công ty">
  <data key="d0">Trụ sở chính của công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The main headquarters of the company where notifications are collected and stored.&lt;SEP&gt;The main office of the company is where certain documents such as the minutes of the meeting and resolutions are stored.&lt;SEP&gt;Trụ sở chính của công ty is the main office of the company where the documents related to the shareholder opinion process are stored.&lt;SEP&gt;Trụ sở chính của công ty is the main office or headquarters of the company where certain reports must be stored.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852988</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sổ ghi chép">
  <data key="d0">Sổ ghi chép</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Sổ ghi chép refers to record-keeping books that are checked and monitored by the Board of Members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giao dịch">
  <data key="d0">Giao dịch</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Giao dịch refers to transactions that are checked and monitored by the Board of Members.&lt;SEP&gt;Giao dịch refers to transactions that are part of the company's operations and are subject to compensation for any losses incurred.&lt;SEP&gt;Giao dịch is a transaction.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853244</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sổ kế toán">
  <data key="d0">Sổ kế toán</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Sổ kế toán refers to accounting books that are checked and monitored by the Board of Members.&lt;SEP&gt;Sổ kế toán is the accounting ledger or record.&lt;SEP&gt;Sổ kế toán is the accounting ledger of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-795fb9faa3ff64c104def58573301724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853244</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Báo cáo tài chính">
  <data key="d0">Báo cáo tài chính</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Báo cáo tài chính refers to the financial reports of a company, which provide detailed information about the company's financial performance and position. These reports are essential documents that offer an overview of the company's financial status and are typically prepared on an annual basis. The preparation and submission of Báo cáo tài chính are subject to monitoring and oversight by the Board of Members and the Audit Committee. In certain circumstances, such as when a company is reducing its registered capital, Báo cáo tài chính must be included in the relevant documentation. Additionally, these financial reports must be submitted to the Đại hội đồng cổ đông and, if required by law, must be audited to ensure accuracy and compliance with financial regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Báo cáo tài chính is a financial report that provides information about the company's financial performance and position.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-795fb9faa3ff64c104def58573301724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8031309e714112ffe63df75b002d2d14</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sổ biên bản họp Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Sổ biên bản họp Hội đồng thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Sổ biên bản họp Hội đồng thành viên refers to the minutes of the Board of Members meetings that are checked and monitored.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Các giấy tờ và tài liệu khác của công ty">
  <data key="d0">Các giấy tờ và tài liệu khác của công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Các giấy tờ và tài liệu khác của công ty refers to other documents and materials of the company that are checked and monitored.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ tịch và thành viên khác của Hội đồng thành">
  <data key="d0">Chủ tịch và thành viên khác của Hội đồng thành</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe</data>
  <data key="d2">The Board of Members must adhere to other related legal regulations.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Biên bản họp">
  <data key="d0">Biên bản họp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Biên bản họp is the official record of the meeting, which includes the decisions and resolutions made.&lt;SEP&gt;Biên bản họp refers to the minutes of a meeting held by the board of members regarding changes in the company's capital.&lt;SEP&gt;Biên bản họp is the minutes of the meeting, which must be recorded and approved before the meeting ends.&lt;SEP&gt;Biên bản họp is a meeting minutes document used in the process of dissolving a business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853534</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phiếu lấy ý kiến">
  <data key="d0">Phiếu lấy ý kiến</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Phiếu lấy ý kiến is the document used to collect opinions from members of the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Phiếu lấy ý kiến is a document used to collect shareholder opinions and must be stored at the company's main office along with other related documents.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852655</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Báo cáo kết quả kiểm phiếu">
  <data key="d0">Báo cáo kết quả kiểm phiếu</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Báo cáo kết quả kiểm phiếu is the report that summarizes the results of the opinion collection process and is equivalent to the Biên bản họp.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 61">
  <data key="d0">Điều 61</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 61 is a regulation that outlines the procedures for passing resolutions and decisions of the Hội đồng thành viên through written opinions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thẩm quyền và thể thức lấy ý kiến">
  <data key="d0">Thẩm quyền và thể thức lấy ý kiến</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thẩm quyền và thể thức lấy ý kiến refers to the authority and procedure for collecting opinions from members of the Hội đồng thành viên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tờ trình">
  <data key="d0">Tờ trình</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tờ trình is a report or proposal submitted to the Hội đồng thành viên for consideration.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dự thảo nghị quyết, quyết định">
  <data key="d0">Dự thảo nghị quyết, quyết định</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Dự thảo nghị quyết, quyết định is a draft of the resolutions and decisions to be passed by the Hội đồng thành viên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 68">
  <data key="d0">Điều 68</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 68 is a legal provision that outlines the conditions for increasing or decreasing the registered capital of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 68 is a legal provision that lists the conditions under which an arbitration decision can be annulled.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c9e86e115e2f87b380e003f8d31484e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853801</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyết định">
  <data key="d0">Quyết định</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyết định refers to a decision made by the board of members regarding changes in the company's capital.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyết định refers to a decision made by the Board of Members.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyết định refers to decisions made by the governing body of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Quyết định is the decision made by the court regarding the annulment of the arbitration award.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-967ef50a189d7b94846c22abc99c1f09</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853867</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người ký kết hợp đồng">
  <data key="d0">Người ký kết hợp đồng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người ký kết hợp đồng refers to individuals who sign contracts and are responsible for compensating the company for any losses incurred.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852116</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người có liên quan của thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Người có liên quan của thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người có liên quan của thành viên refers to individuals associated with the members of the company and are responsible for compensating the company for any losses incurred.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852116</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thành viên Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Thành viên Hội đồng thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thành viên Hội đồng thành viên are the members of the governing body who participate in meetings and decision-making processes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852124</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phương hướng phát triển công ty">
  <data key="d0">Phương hướng phát triển công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phương hướng phát triển công ty is the strategic direction or plan for the development of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852124</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ chức lại hoặc giải thể công ty">
  <data key="d0">Tổ chức lại hoặc giải thể công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Tổ chức lại hoặc giải thể công ty refers to the restructuring or dissolution of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852124</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Biên bản cuộc họp">
  <data key="d0">Biên bản cuộc họp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Biên bản cuộc họp is the official minutes of the meeting that document the discussions, decisions, and conclusions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852125</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổ chức lại hoặc giải体公司">
  <data key="d0">Tổ chức lại hoặc giải体公司</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816</data>
  <data key="d2">Hội đồng thành viên负责批准公司的重组或解散。</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852125</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ tọa">
  <data key="d0">Chủ tọa</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ tọa refers to the chairperson of the meeting.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tọa is the chairperson who leads the meeting of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852781</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người ghi biên bản">
  <data key="d0">Người ghi biên bản</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người ghi biên bản refers to the person responsible for recording the minutes of the meeting.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852147</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người quản lý khác">
  <data key="d0">Người quản lý khác</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Other managers are responsible for ensuring the company's legal interests and adhering to the law and the company's charter.&lt;SEP&gt;Người quản lý khác refers to other managers in the company who have specific responsibilities and duties.&lt;SEP&gt;Người quản lý khác refers to other management positions within a company, and Kiểm soát viên cannot be a family member of these individuals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853165</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Lợi nhuận đã chia">
  <data key="d0">Lợi nhuận đã chia</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Distributed profit refers to the profit that has been shared among the members of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852187</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giảm vốn điều lệ">
  <data key="d0">Giảm vốn điều lệ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Reducing the registered capital refers to the process of decreasing the registered capital of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852187</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chia lợi nhuận trái phép">
  <data key="d0">Chia lợi nhuận trái phép</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Illegal distribution of profit refers to the distribution of profit that does not comply with the regulations set by the law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852187</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trách nhiệm liên đới">
  <data key="d0">Trách nhiệm liên đới</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Joint liability refers to the responsibility that members of the company must bear together for the debts and financial obligations of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852187</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Khởi kiện trách nhiệm dân sự">
  <data key="d0">Khởi kiện trách nhiệm dân sự</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Civil liability lawsuit refers to the legal action taken by members of the company against managers for failing to fulfill their responsibilities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852187</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người kiểm phiếu">
  <data key="d0">Người kiểm phiếu</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người kiểm phiếu is a person responsible for counting votes and ensuring the accuracy of the voting process.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852219</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nhóm thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Nhóm thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nhóm thành viên refers to a group of members within the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852219</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Kế hoạch kinh doanh">
  <data key="d0">Kế hoạch kinh doanh</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Kế hoạch kinh doanh refers to business plans and investment strategies of the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852219</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quy chế quản lý nội bộ">
  <data key="d0">Quy chế quản lý nội bộ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quy chế quản lý nội bộ refers to internal management regulations of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Internal management regulations proposed by the Director or General Director.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853002</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tiêu chuẩn và điều kiện làm Giám đốc, Tổng giám đốc">
  <data key="d0">Tiêu chuẩn và điều kiện làm Giám đốc, Tổng giám đốc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tiêu chuẩn và điều kiện làm Giám đốc, Tổng giám đốc refers to the standards and conditions required for someone to become a director or general director of a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852219</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cổ phần phổ thông">
  <data key="d0">Cổ phần phổ thông</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Cổ phần phổ thông are common shares in a company, and the owners of these shares are common shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần phổ thông is a type of common stock used as the underlying asset for issuing non-voting deposit certificates.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần phổ thông refers to common shares in a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852331</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cổ phần ưu đãi">
  <data key="d0">Cổ phần ưu đãi</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cổ phần ưu đãi are preferred shares in a company, and the owners of these shares are preferred shareholders. These shares can include dividend preferred shares, redemption preferred shares, voting preferred shares, and other types of preferred shares as defined by the company's charter and securities law.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần ưu đãi refers to preferred shares in a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần ưu đãi refers to preferred shares that have special rights and privileges.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852687</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chứng chỉ lưu ký không có quyền biểu quyết">
  <data key="d0">Chứng chỉ lưu ký không có quyền biểu quyết</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Chứng chỉ lưu ký không có quyền biểu quyết are non-voting depositary receipts that are based on common shares and have economic benefits and corresponding obligations, but lack voting rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Non-voting deposit certificates have economic benefits and corresponding obligations equivalent to common stock, except for voting rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852299</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chính phủ">
  <data key="d0">Chính phủ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chính phủ refers to the government of Vietnam, which plays a significant role in regulating various aspects of business and organizational activities within the country. It is responsible for providing detailed regulations concerning non-voting depositary receipts, legal articles, and the organizational structure of the Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh (Business Registration Agency). The government also authorizes certain organizations to hold special shares and defines the system of organization for the Business Registration Agency, including the registration and operation of household businesses.

Furthermore, Chính phủ sets the procedures for revoking business registration certificates and specifies the detailed procedures for the dissolution of a business. These regulations and procedures are crucial for maintaining order and ensuring compliance with legal standards in Vietnam's business environment.&lt;SEP&gt;Chính phủ is the government body that defines the procedures for revoking business registration certificates.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-643d72cdd6873e78e2d39abbf824c8bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09d578fe732c3cb08c15e944096d74cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-752ff3609fa8e883d0e8624f9045b21b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người được quyền mua cổ phần ưu đãi">
  <data key="d0">Người được quyền mua cổ phần ưu đãi</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều lệ công ty, or the company's charter, regulates who has the right to purchase Cổ phần ưu đãi, or preferred shares.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852269</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 102">
  <data key="d0">Điều 102</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 102 specifies the conditions for the removal and dismissal of Directors, General Directors, and other managers of a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852272</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 103">
  <data key="d0">Điều 103</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 103 details the establishment of the Supervisory Board and the qualifications for Supervisors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852272</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phó giám đốc">
  <data key="d0">Phó giám đốc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phó giám đốc is a Deputy Director of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Phó giám đốc is a person in a leadership position within the company who can be requested to provide information by the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;The Deputy Director is a position within the company, with the number and authority defined in the company's charter.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852365</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phó Tổng giám đốc">
  <data key="d0">Phó Tổng giám đốc</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phó Tổng giám đốc is a Deputy General Director of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Phó Tổng giám đốc is a person in a leadership position within the company who can be requested to provide information by the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;The Deputy General Director is a position within the company, with the number and authority defined in the company's charter.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852365</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Kế toán trưởng">
  <data key="d0">Kế toán trưởng</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Kế toán trưởng is the Chief Accountant of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Kế toán trưởng is a person in a leadership position within the company who can be requested to provide information by the Hội đồng thành viên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
