</node>
<node id="Trưởng Ban kiểm soát">
  <data key="d0">Trưởng Ban kiểm soát</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trưởng Ban kiểm soát is the Head of the Supervisory Board of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Trưởng Ban kiểm soát is a position responsible for supervising and controlling the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Trưởng Ban kiểm soát is the head of the supervisory board who may preside over the meeting if the chairperson is absent.&lt;SEP&gt;Trưởng Ban kiểm soát is the head of the Ban kiểm soát, elected from among the kiểm soát viên, and must have a university degree in economics, finance, accounting, auditing, law, business administration, or a related field.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-373a8f0d009c4c6073d5e556bc2411e7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852926</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cổ đông phổ thông">
  <data key="d0">Cổ đông phổ thông</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Common shareholders have the right to attend, speak, and vote at the General Shareholders' Meeting, receive dividends, and have other rights as specified by the company's articles of association and laws.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông phổ thông refers to common shareholders who have certain rights, including the right to nominate individuals to the Board of Directors and Supervisory Board.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01b556fba8ab897e9f334300f225003e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852383</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
