</node>
<node id="Doanh nghiệp nhà nước">
  <data key="d0">Doanh nghiệp nhà nước</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Doanh nghiệp nhà nước is a state-owned enterprise.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp nhà nước is a state-owned enterprise with specific regulations regarding supervisors.&lt;SEP&gt;State-owned enterprises that must meet certain standards and conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp nhà nước is a state-owned enterprise with specific regulations for the position of Kiểm soát viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp nhà nước is a state-owned enterprise that can convert into a joint-stock company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-795fb9faa3ff64c104def58573301724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a657b345d0676b5a5d6451a2c7c13d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
