<node id="Cổ phần">
  <data key="d0">Cổ phần</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Cổ phần refers to shares in the company that shareholders can purchase and hold.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần refers to shares of a corporation, which can be sold, registered for purchase, and used to raise capital.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần refers to shares of a company's registered capital, which can be freely transferred by shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần refers to shares in a company, which can be bought, sold, and transferred.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần refers to shares in a company that can be purchased and sold.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần is a share of stock.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-643d72cdd6873e78e2d39abbf824c8bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4c6a296c5e1b248b6b79c98f9b16e6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
