  <data key="d2">Điều 113 is a specific article in the law that outlines the rules for the payment of shares and the adjustment of registered capital.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều 113 is a legal article that specifies regulations related to the operations of a joint-stock company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618</data>
