<node id="Hội Đồng Quản Trị">
  <data key="d0">Hội Đồng Quản Trị</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hội Đồng Quản Trị is the board of directors of a company, responsible for managing the company's affairs and making key decisions. This includes overseeing the payment of dividends, deciding on the issuance of private bonds if not specified otherwise in the company's charter, and selling remaining shares if they are not fully subscribed by existing shareholders. The board's membership ranges from three to eleven members, with each member serving a term of up to five years. Hội Đồng Quản Trị is the management body of a company, responsible for executing the rights and obligations of the company, except those belonging to the Đại Hội Đồng Cổ Đông. The board is elected or appointed by the members of the company and is responsible for overseeing the company's operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-af079df7102c58f84652bfeb21c7a17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e31bb2a60b0c3b80bacb62410231f646&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-444a844ae4151849d71498d312b5d52d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a95c0aafb09aeaffa31c143eaf83c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d59be88d8f39c9fce708d8b3f0c8014&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853313</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
