  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cổ Tức refers to dividends paid to shareholders based on the company's profits.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-af079df7102c58f84652bfeb21c7a17a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773852553</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đại Hội Đồng Cổ Đông">
  <data key="d0">Đại Hội Đồng Cổ Đông</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đại Hội Đồng Cổ Đông, which translates to the General Meeting of Shareholders, is the highest decision-making body of a company, responsible for making major decisions that affect the company. This annual meeting brings together shareholders to discuss and vote on important matters related to the company's operations, including decisions regarding dividends, the issuance of private bonds, and the approval of conditions for selling remaining shares. During the meeting, the board of directors is required to report on the qualifications of independent board members. Additionally, the Đại Hội Đồng Cổ Đông has the authority to make decisions that involve dividing or splitting the company, passing necessary resolutions to effect such changes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-af079df7102c58f84652bfeb21c7a17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e31bb2a60b0c3b80bacb62410231f646&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-444a844ae4151849d71498d312b5d52d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a95c0aafb09aeaffa31c143eaf83c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9aff8a680816d92d14d4a77e34dbfc7d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a5aa4a830d11b31ecf4b23667e2bb4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853312</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
