</node>
<node id="Chuyển đổi công ty cổ phần thành công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn một thành viên">
  <data key="d0">Chuyển đổi công ty cổ phần thành công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn một thành viên</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">The event of converting a joint-stock company into a single-member limited liability company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0359f960f337b0c62d24c54f784fc5c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853411</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 203">
  <data key="d0">Điều 203</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 203 is the legal provision that outlines the process for converting a joint-stock company into a single-member limited liability company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0359f960f337b0c62d24c54f784fc5c1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853411</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thành Viên Hợp Dan">
  <data key="d0">Thành Viên Hợp Dan</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-111878a66be557377de6fec57d456ed2</data>
  <data key="d2">The rights and obligations of Thành viên hợp danh are governed by the law.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853430</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công ty bị hợp nhất">
  <data key="d0">Công ty bị hợp nhất</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công ty bị hợp nhất refers to the companies that are being merged into a new company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853442</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Công ty hợp nhất">
  <data key="d0">Công ty hợp nhất</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Công ty hợp nhất is the new company formed by the merger of two or more companies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853442</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hợp đồng hợp nhất">
  <data key="d0">Hợp đồng hợp nhất</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hợp đồng hợp nhất is the contract that outlines the terms and conditions of the merger between companies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853442</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều lệ công ty hợp nhất">
  <data key="d0">Điều lệ công ty hợp nhất</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều lệ công ty hợp nhất is the charter of the new company formed by the merger.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853442</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thủ tục hợp nhất công ty">
  <data key="d0">Thủ tục hợp nhất công ty</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thủ tục hợp nhất công ty refers to the procedures for merging companies, as outlined in the regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853442</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phương án sử dụng lao động">
  <data key="d0">Phương án sử dụng lao động</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phương án sử dụng lao động is the plan for utilizing labor during the merger process.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853442</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thành viên, chủ sở hữu công ty hoặc cổ đông">
  <data key="d0">Thành viên, chủ sở hữu công ty hoặc cổ đông</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thành viên, chủ sở hữu công ty hoặc cổ đông are the members, owners, or shareholders of the company being merged.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853442</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chuyển đổi công ty cổ phần thành công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên">
  <data key="d0">Chuyển đổi công ty cổ phần thành công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Chuyển đổi công ty cổ phần thành công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên is the process of converting a công ty cổ phần into a công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a788d203fae6d3c78c81ae71ea9171e4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853453</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 204">
  <data key="d0">Điều 204</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 204 is the legal provision that outlines the process for converting a công ty cổ phần into a công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a788d203fae6d3c78c81ae71ea9171e4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853453</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Luat Nguoi">
  <data key="d0">Luat Nguoi</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Luat Nguoi is the law that regulates the authority of Commercial Arbitration, various forms of arbitration, the organization of arbitration, arbitrators; the procedures and processes of arbitration; the rights, obligations, and responsibilities of the parties involved in arbitration proceedings; the authority of the Court over arbitration activities; the organization and operation of foreign arbitration in Vietnam, and the enforcement of arbitration decisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trong tai thuong mai">
  <data key="d0">Trong tai thuong mai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Commercial Arbitration is a method of resolving disputes agreed upon by the parties and conducted according to the provisions of the law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tho a quyen trung tai">
  <data key="d0">Tho a quyen trung tai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Arbitration Agreement is an agreement between the parties regarding the resolution of disputes through arbitration that may arise or have already arisen.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cac ben tranh chap">
  <data key="d0">Cac ben tranh chap</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The parties in dispute are individuals, agencies, or organizations from Vietnam or abroad who participate in arbitration proceedings as plaintiffs or defendants.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tranh chap co yeu to nuoc ngoai">
  <data key="d0">Tranh chap co yeu to nuoc ngoai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Disputes with foreign elements are disputes arising from commercial relations or other legal relations with foreign elements as defined in the Civil Code.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trung tai vien">
  <data key="d0">Trung tai vien</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Arbitrator is a person chosen by the parties or designated by the Arbitration Center or the Court to resolve disputes according to the provisions of the law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trung tai quy che">
  <data key="d0">Trung tai quy che</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Institutional Arbitration is a form of dispute resolution at an Arbitration Center according to the provisions of the law and the rules of procedure of that Arbitration Center.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trung tai vu viec">
  <data key="d0">Trung tai vu viec</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Ad hoc Arbitration is a form of dispute resolution according to the provisions of the law and the procedures agreed upon by the parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dia diem giai quyet tranh chap">
  <data key="d0">Dia diem giai quyet tranh chap</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The place of dispute resolution is the location where the Arbitration Tribunal conducts the resolution of disputes according to the agreement of the parties or as decided by the Arbitration Tribunal if the parties have no agreement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyet dinh trung tai">
  <data key="d0">Quyet dinh trung tai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Arbitration Award is a decision of the Arbitration Tribunal during the process of resolving disputes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phan quyet trung tai">
  <data key="d0">Phan quyet trung tai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Arbitration Decision is a decision of the Arbitration Tribunal that resolves the entire content of the dispute and concludes the arbitration proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trung tai nuoc ngoai">
  <data key="d0">Trung tai nuoc ngoai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Foreign Arbitration is arbitration established according to the laws of foreign arbitration by the parties' agreement to conduct dispute resolution outside the territory of Vietnam or within the territory of Vietnam.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phan quyet cua trung tai nuoc ngoai">
  <data key="d0">Phan quyet cua trung tai nuoc ngoai</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Foreign Arbitration Decision is a decision made by foreign arbitration outside the territory of Vietnam or within the territory of Vietnam to resolve disputes as agreed upon by the parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853492</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trung tâm trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Trung tâm trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trung tâm trọng tài is an arbitration center operating in Vietnam, responsible for conducting institutional arbitration according to its rules of procedure. This organization plays a key role in arbitration and dispute resolution services, managing arbitration proceedings and providing related services. Parties involved in disputes may choose Trung tâm trọng tài to resolve their conflicts. The center is also involved in the overall arbitration process and is responsible for storing arbitration case files.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung tâm trọng tài is an organization that oversees the arbitration process and establishes rules for the proceedings.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung tâm trọng tài is the arbitration center that may appoint a single arbitrator if the parties cannot agree.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung tâm trọng tài is the Arbitration Center where disputes are resolved.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-967ef50a189d7b94846c22abc99c1f09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-105aefb96d31bdf83eb8694998c59506&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854048</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The Chairman of the Trung tâm trọng tài is a key figure in the organization, responsible for appointing the General Secretary and is an arbitrator.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài is the chairperson of the arbitration center who appoints a single arbitrator if the parties cannot agree.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài is the Chairman of the Arbitration Center who decides on the change of an Arbitrator if the Arbitration Board has not been established.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854048</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phó Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Phó Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The Vice Chairman of the Trung tâm trọng tài is a member of the management board of the organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tổng thư ký Trung tâm trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Tổng thư ký Trung tâm trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The General Secretary of the Trung tâm trọng tài is appointed by the Chairman and is part of the management board.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trọng tài viên">
  <data key="d0">Trọng tài viên</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trọng tài viên refers to arbitrators who are appointed to resolve disputes through arbitration. These individuals are listed in the Trung tâm trọng tài's roster and are responsible for resolving disputes in accordance with the principles and conditions set forth in the legal framework. Trọng tài viên can be involved in the dispute resolution process either as part of domestic arbitration or appointed by a foreign arbitration organization to serve in Vietnam. They must disclose any circumstances that may affect their impartiality, ensuring the integrity and fairness of the arbitration process.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1881019a36e766412bad88d7a1e3d088&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854050</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bộ Tư pháp">
  <data key="d0">Bộ Tư pháp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The Ministry of Justice is responsible for publishing the list of arbitrators provided by the Trung tâm trọng tài.&lt;SEP&gt;Bộ Tư pháp is the Ministry of Justice in Vietnam.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853604</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sở Tư pháp">
  <data key="d0">Sở Tư pháp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The Provincial Department of Justice is responsible for receiving annual reports from the Trung tâm trọng tài.&lt;SEP&gt;Sở Tư pháp is the local legal affairs department responsible for registering the activities of arbitration centers.&lt;SEP&gt;Sở Tư pháp is the legal affairs department responsible for registering and monitoring the activities of foreign arbitration organizations in Vietnam.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1881019a36e766412bad88d7a1e3d088&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853955</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đơn khởi kiện">
  <data key="d0">Đơn khởi kiện</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">The complaint is a document filed by the plaintiff to initiate arbitration proceedings at the Trung tâm trọng tài.&lt;SEP&gt;Đơn khởi kiện is a legal document filed by the plaintiff to initiate arbitration proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thỏa thuận trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Thỏa thuận trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">The arbitration agreement is a document that accompanies the complaint and is essential for initiating arbitration proceedings.&lt;SEP&gt;Thỏa thuận trọng tài refers to the arbitration agreement.&lt;SEP&gt;Thỏa thuận trọng tài is an arbitration agreement signed before the new law takes effect and is to be executed according to the laws in place at the time of signing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44b958e89c37ebae08442548c41df280</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854043</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 30">
  <data key="d0">Điều 30</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 30 details the requirements for the complaint and accompanying documents in arbitration proceedings.</data>
