<node id="Người quản lý">
  <data key="d0">Người quản lý</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người quản lý refers to a manager or administrator of a business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853534</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cơ quan thuế">
  <data key="d0">Cơ quan thuế</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ quan thuế is the tax authority.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan thuế is a tax authority that must be notified by businesses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chủ nợ">
  <data key="d0">Chủ nợ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chủ nợ refers to creditors of a business entity.&lt;SEP&gt;Creditors of the business are notified of the dissolution process and provided with information on debt repayment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853649</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyết định giải thể doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Quyết định giải thể doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyết định giải thể doanh nghiệp is a decision document for the dissolution of a business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853534</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phương án giải quyết nợ">
  <data key="d0">Phương án giải quyết nợ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phương án giải quyết nợ is a debt resolution plan document used in the process of dissolving a business entity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853534</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người đại diện theo pháp luật của doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Người đại diện theo pháp luật của doanh nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người đại diện theo pháp luật của doanh nghiệp is the legal representative of the business who shares responsibility for the accuracy of the termination documents.&lt;SEP&gt;The legal representative of the business is responsible for the accuracy of the dissolution file.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853649</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Người đứng đầu chi nhánh, văn phòng đại diện">
  <data key="d0">Người đứng đầu chi nhánh, văn phòng đại diện</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Người đứng đầu chi nhánh, văn phòng đại diện is the head of the branch or representative office who shares responsibility for the accuracy of the termination documents.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853535</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hồ sơ chấm dứt hoạt động">
  <data key="d0">Hồ sơ chấm dứt hoạt động</data>
  <data key="d1">VĂN_BẢN_PHÁP_LUẬT</data>
  <data key="d2">Hồ sơ chấm dứt hoạt động refers to the documents related to the termination of branches, representative offices, or business locations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853535</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thanh toán các khoản nợ">
  <data key="d0">Thanh toán các khoản nợ</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thanh toán các khoản nợ refers to the obligation of the business to pay off debts, including taxes, after the termination of a branch.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853535</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Giải quyết đủ quyền lợi hợp pháp cho người lao động">
  <data key="d0">Giải quyết đủ quyền lợi hợp pháp cho người lao động</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Giải quyết đủ quyền lợi hợp pháp cho người lao động refers to the obligation of the business to ensure the legal rights of employees who worked at the terminated branch.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853535</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phá Sản Doanh Nghiệp">
  <data key="d0">Phá Sản Doanh Nghiệp</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Phá Sản Doanh Nghiệp is the event of a business bankruptcy, which is carried out according to the law on bankruptcy.&lt;SEP&gt;Phá Sản Doanh Nghiệp is an event regulated by the law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6f6b7c08fc56b324472ca75d1984ba36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5a052d442484a7e21099fd9dda00e96</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853724</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Điều 214">
  <data key="d0">Điều 214</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Điều 214 is a legal article that outlines the procedures for the bankruptcy of a business.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6f6b7c08fc56b324472ca75d1984ba36</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853554</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Các bên tranh chấp">
  <data key="d0">Các bên tranh chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Các bên tranh chấp refers to the parties involved in a dispute that is to be resolved through arbitration.&lt;SEP&gt;Các bên tranh chấp are the parties involved in the dispute who have the right to request the application of temporary emergency measures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hội đồng trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Hội đồng trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hội đồng trọng tài is an arbitration panel or council responsible for resolving disputes and ensuring that the rights and obligations of the parties involved are fulfilled. This entity makes arbitration awards and decisions, and it also handles emergency measures and the interpretation of arbitration decisions. Hội đồng trọng tài plays a crucial role in managing the arbitration process, including setting arbitration fees and determining the validity and enforceability of arbitration agreements. Its primary function is to provide a structured and fair mechanism for dispute resolution, thereby upholding the legal rights and interests of all parties involved.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng trọng tài is an organization responsible for resolving disputes and has the authority to summon witnesses and apply emergency measures.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng trọng tài is an organization responsible for arbitrating disputes and making decisions regarding the proceedings.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng trọng tài is an organization responsible for applying emergency measures and making decisions regarding disputes.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng trọng tài is the arbitration board responsible for resolving disputes and gathering evidence.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng trọng tài is the Arbitration Board that decides on the change of an Arbitrator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e87b9226945fe55349146eaa7dc3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c9e86e115e2f87b380e003f8d31484e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-967ef50a189d7b94846c22abc99c1f09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-105aefb96d31bdf83eb8694998c59506&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b47a7db90a1e526f1797874efef64872&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-868a62477b36c9e43bd19ac6e811469e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854048</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phán quyết trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Phán quyết trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phán quyết trọng tài is the final decision made by the arbitration panel, which is considered final and binding.&lt;SEP&gt;Phán quyết trọng tài is the arbitration award that may be subject to annulment.&lt;SEP&gt;Phán quyết trọng tài is the content of an arbitration decision.&lt;SEP&gt;Phán quyết trọng tài refers to the decision made by an arbitration tribunal.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-967ef50a189d7b94846c22abc99c1f09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-105aefb96d31bdf83eb8694998c59506&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853954</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thoả thuận trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Thoả thuận trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thoả thuận trọng tài is an agreement between the parties to resolve their dispute through arbitration.&lt;SEP&gt;Thoả thuận trọng tài is an arbitration agreement between parties that may be deemed valid or invalid by the arbitration council.&lt;SEP&gt;Thoả thuận trọng tài is the arbitration agreement that is part of the legal documents.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-967ef50a189d7b94846c22abc99c1f09</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853867</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Toà án">
  <data key="d0">Toà án</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Toà án is the court system that may be involved in arbitration-related matters, such as determining jurisdiction or refusing to hear cases where an arbitration agreement exists.&lt;SEP&gt;Toà án is a legal body with the authority to hear and decide on requests to annul arbitration decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Toà án is the judicial body responsible for examining requests to annul arbitration awards and making decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Toà án is the court system responsible for making final decisions that are enforceable.&lt;SEP&gt;Toà án is the judicial body responsible for resolving disputes and making decisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c9e86e115e2f87b380e003f8d31484e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-967ef50a189d7b94846c22abc99c1f09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-868a62477b36c9e43bd19ac6e811469e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854018</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tòa án nhân dân tỉnh, thành phố trực thuộc trung ương">
  <data key="d0">Tòa án nhân dân tỉnh, thành phố trực thuộc trung ương</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Tòa án nhân dân tỉnh, thành phố trực thuộc trung ương is the specific court system with jurisdiction over arbitration-related activities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853578</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phán quyết của trọng tài nước ngoài">
  <data key="d0">Phán quyết của trọng tài nước ngoài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phán quyết của trọng tài nước ngoài is a foreign arbitration decision made outside or inside Vietnam's territory to resolve disputes agreed upon by the parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853578</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
