  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Ngôn ngữ refers to the language used in arbitration proceedings, which is determined based on the presence or absence of foreign elements in the dispute.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853684</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Địa điểm giải quyết tranh chấp">
  <data key="d0">Địa điểm giải quyết tranh chấp</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Địa điểm giải quyết tranh chấp is the location where disputes are resolved through arbitration, which can be within or outside Vietnam.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853684</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Gửi thông báo và trình tự gửi thông báo">
  <data key="d0">Gửi thông báo và trình tự gửi thông báo</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">Gửi thông báo và trình tự gửi thông báo is the method for sending notifications and the procedure for doing so in arbitration proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853684</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thương lượng, hoà giải trong tố tụng trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Thương lượng, hoà giải trong tố tụng trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thương lượng, hoà giải trong tố tụng trọng tài is the concept of negotiation and mediation during arbitration proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853684</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Decision to Dissolve the Business">
  <data key="d0">Decision to Dissolve the Business</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">The decision to dissolve the business is a critical event that triggers a series of prohibited activities and responsibilities, including the prohibition of certain actions and the requirement to settle outstanding financial obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Business Dissolution Filing">
  <data key="d0">Business Dissolution Filing</data>
  <data key="d1">HÀNH_VI</data>
  <data key="d2">The business dissolution filing is the formal submission of documents to the Business Registration Authority to initiate the dissolution process, which triggers civil and criminal liabilities for the business and its managers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Business Registration Authority">
  <data key="d0">Business Registration Authority</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The Business Registration Authority is the entity responsible for receiving and processing business dissolution filings, ensuring compliance with legal requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Business">
  <data key="d0">Business</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The business is the entity that is being dissolved and is subject to various prohibited activities post-dissolution decision, including the prohibition of certain financial and contractual actions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Business Manager">
  <data key="d0">Business Manager</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">The business manager is responsible for managing the business and is subject to restrictions and responsibilities after the dissolution decision, including the prohibition of certain actions and the requirement to settle outstanding financial obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unpaid Wages">
  <data key="d0">Unpaid Wages</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Unpaid wages are the outstanding wages owed to employees that must be settled by the business or its managers within five years of the business dissolution filing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unpaid Taxes">
  <data key="d0">Unpaid Taxes</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Unpaid taxes are the outstanding tax obligations that must be settled by the business or its managers within five years of the business dissolution filing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unpaid Debts">
  <data key="d0">Unpaid Debts</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Unpaid debts are the outstanding financial obligations that must be settled by the business or its managers within five years of the business dissolution filing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Civil Liability">
  <data key="d0">Civil Liability</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Civil liability refers to the responsibility of individuals to settle unpaid wages, taxes, and debts within five years of the business dissolution filing, as well as the prohibition of certain actions post-dissolution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Criminal Liability">
  <data key="d0">Criminal Liability</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Criminal liability refers to the potential legal consequences for individuals who violate the prohibited activities post-dissolution decision, including financial penalties and criminal prosecution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Prohibited Activities">
  <data key="d0">Prohibited Activities</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Prohibited activities are a set of actions that the business and its managers are strictly forbidden from undertaking after the dissolution decision, including the prohibition of certain financial and contractual actions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Financial Penalties">
  <data key="d0">Financial Penalties</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Financial penalties are the potential fines or sanctions imposed on individuals who violate the prohibited activities post-dissolution decision, as a result of their actions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Criminal Prosecution">
  <data key="d0">Criminal Prosecution</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Criminal prosecution refers to the legal action taken against individuals who violate the prohibited activities post-dissolution decision and cause damage, leading to potential criminal consequences.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bộ">
  <data key="d0">Bộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bộ is a governmental department responsible for specific tasks in managing enterprises.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c5a052d442484a7e21099fd9dda00e96</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853724</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cơ Quan Ngang Bộ">
  <data key="d0">Cơ Quan Ngang Bộ</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Cơ Quan Ngang Bộ is an organization that has the same level of authority as Bộ and is responsible for specific tasks in managing enterprises.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c5a052d442484a7e21099fd9dda00e96</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853724</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
