  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quyết định của Hội đồng trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Quyết định của Hội đồng trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quyết định của Hội đồng trọng tài is a decision made by the arbitration council regarding the validity and enforceability of arbitration agreements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đơn khiếu nại">
  <data key="d0">Đơn khiếu nại</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đơn khiếu nại is a complaint filed by a party against the decision of the arbitration council.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thẩm phán">
  <data key="d0">Thẩm phán</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Thẩm phán is a judge responsible for reviewing and deciding on complaints against the arbitration council's decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Thẩm phán is a judge who is part of the panel examining the request to annul an arbitration award.&lt;SEP&gt;Thẩm phán is a judge who is responsible for issuing summoning decisions for witnesses.&lt;SEP&gt;Thẩm phán is a judge who is assigned to appoint an arbitrator.&lt;SEP&gt;Thẩm phán is the judge assigned to handle requests for evidence collection.&lt;SEP&gt;Thẩm phán is a Judge who is designated to assign an Arbitrator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-967ef50a189d7b94846c22abc99c1f09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-868a62477b36c9e43bd19ac6e811469e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854048</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chánh án Toà án">
  <data key="d0">Chánh án Toà án</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chánh án Toà án is the chief judge of the court who assigns a judge to review complaints against the arbitration council's decisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853804</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nguyên đơn">
  <data key="d0">Nguyên đơn</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nguyên đơn is the plaintiff who initiates a lawsuit or complaint.&lt;SEP&gt;Nguyên đơn is the plaintiff in an arbitration case.&lt;SEP&gt;Nguyên đơn is a party in a dispute who initiates the legal action.&lt;SEP&gt;Nguyên đơn is the plaintiff in a dispute.&lt;SEP&gt;Nguyên đơn is the plaintiff who initiates legal proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-868a62477b36c9e43bd19ac6e811469e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854018</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trọng tài vụ việc">
  <data key="d0">Trọng tài vụ việc</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trọng tài vụ việc is a method of resolving disputes through arbitration proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phí trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Phí trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Phí trọng tài refers to the fees associated with arbitration services, including arbitrator fees, administrative fees, and other related costs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bị đơn">
  <data key="d0">Bị đơn</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bị đơn is the defendant in an arbitration case.&lt;SEP&gt;Bị đơn is a party in a dispute who is the subject of the legal action initiated by the Nguyên đơn.&lt;SEP&gt;Bị đơn is the defendant in a dispute.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853974</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quy tắc tố tụng trọng tài">
  <data key="d0">Quy tắc tố tụng trọng tài</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Quy tắc tố tụng trọng tài are the procedural rules governing arbitration proceedings, which may include specific provisions for document submission and fee determination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853827</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bị Đơn">
  <data key="d0">Bị Đơn</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Bị Đơn is a party in a legal dispute who has the right to file a counterclaim and must submit a self-defense statement.&lt;SEP&gt;Bị Đơn is the party against whom the dispute is initiated in an arbitration case.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4467037e5832a3ba479e5bed20f265c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6520e05120076623f2042182e932b3ec</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854008</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Nguyên Đơn">
  <data key="d0">Nguyên Đơn</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Nguyên Đơn is a party in a legal dispute who initiates the lawsuit and must submit a self-defense statement in response to a counterclaim.&lt;SEP&gt;Nguyên Đơn is the party initiating the dispute in an arbitration case.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4467037e5832a3ba479e5bed20f265c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6520e05120076623f2042182e932b3ec</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854008</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trung Tâm Trọng Tài">
  <data key="d0">Trung Tâm Trọng Tài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Trung Tâm Trọng Tài is an organization responsible for handling arbitration cases and receiving counterclaims and self-defense statements.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung Tâm Trọng Tài is the arbitration center that has rules for dispute resolution proceedings.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung Tâm Trọng Tài is an organization that can be involved in the arbitration process and can provide copies of the arbitration decision.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung Tâm Trọng Tài is an arbitration center established before the law came into effect and must modify its bylaws to comply with the new law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4467037e5832a3ba479e5bed20f265c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a36e099bae803eeaad0a5160e83464d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6520e05120076623f2042182e932b3ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44b958e89c37ebae08442548c41df280</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854043</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hội Đồng Trọng Tài">
  <data key="d0">Hội Đồng Trọng Tài</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Hội Đồng Trọng Tài is a body responsible for resolving counterclaims and making decisions in arbitration cases.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội Đồng Trọng Tài is the arbitration board that can decide on the time and place of dispute resolution meetings.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội Đồng Trọng Tài is the body responsible for making arbitration decisions and is composed of arbitrators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4467037e5832a3ba479e5bed20f265c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a36e099bae803eeaad0a5160e83464d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6520e05120076623f2042182e932b3ec</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854008</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Đơn Kiện Lại">
  <data key="d0">Đơn Kiện Lại</data>
  <data key="d1">QUYỀN_NGHĨA_VỤ</data>
  <data key="d2">Đơn Kiện Lại is a counterclaim filed by Bị Đơn against Nguyên Đơn.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4467037e5832a3ba479e5bed20f265c7</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773853841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
