</node>
<node id="Chánh án Tòa án có thẩm quyền">
  <data key="d0">Chánh án Tòa án có thẩm quyền</data>
  <data key="d1">CHỦ_THỂ</data>
  <data key="d2">Chánh án Tòa án có thẩm quyền is the chief judge of the competent court who assigns a judge to appoint an arbitrator.&lt;SEP&gt;Chánh án Tòa án có thẩm quyền is responsible for assigning a Judge to designate an Arbitrator and notifying the parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773854048</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
