  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A court is responsible for appointing a guardian in case of disputes or if there is no natural guardian.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa án can designate a guardian as a legal representative for individuals with difficulties in perception and behavior.</data>
  <data key="d9">court responsibility,guardianship,legal designation</data>
