  <data key="d12">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Điều  53">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều 53 specifies the role of the court in declaring a member missing or incapacitated and issuing decisions regarding the cessation of business activities.</data>
  <data key="d9">court decision,legal provision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7934cedd8a058c40a35091be7e3f1c17</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851694</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên may be subject to legal restrictions imposed by the court that affect their ability to hold the position.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal restrictions,position eligibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851900</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn một thành viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tòa án issues decisions that can prohibit individuals or entities from certain activities or businesses, affecting the operations of the company.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal decision,prohibition</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851942</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="cá nhân">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The court can prohibit an individual from certain activities or businesses.</data>
  <data key="d9">individual,legal prohibition</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851943</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="pháp nhân thương mại">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The court can prohibit a commercial legal entity from certain business activities.</data>
  <data key="d9">entity,legal prohibition</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851943</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Nghị quyết">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tòa án can make decisions regarding the validity of company resolutions.&lt;SEP&gt;Nghị quyết can be challenged by the Tòa án, which can invalidate the resolution.&lt;SEP&gt;The court can review and potentially annul a resolution of the General Shareholders' Meeting.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration,legal challenge,legal review,legal validity,resolution annulment,resolution validity</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852634</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Công ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty is subject to legal decisions and judgments made by the Tòa án.</data>
  <data key="d9">judgments,legal decisions</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852454</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tòa án makes decisions regarding the transfer of shares by Cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông can request the Tòa án to invalidate a resolution.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông can seek legal recourse through Tòa án in case of disputes.</data>
  <data key="d9">court decision,dispute resolution,legal challenge,legal recourse,resolution validity,share transfer</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853050</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Quyết định hủy bỏ nghị quyết">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tòa án can make a Quyết định hủy bỏ nghị quyết to invalidate a resolution.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal decision,resolution invalidation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852590</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The court can make decisions to suspend or terminate business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp must not be involved in dispute resolution processes at Tòa án during dissolution.</data>
  <data key="d9">dispute resolution,legal decision,legal process,suspension</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853539</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Luat Nguoi">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The law regulates the authority of the Court over arbitration activities.</data>
  <data key="d9">authority,regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e5776688da11e53219ff5c781821e654</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853506</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Giải thể doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The court can issue a decision that leads to the dissolution of a business.</data>
  <data key="d9">dissolution trigger,legal decision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853652</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Đơn khiếu nại">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tòa án reviews Đơn khiếu nại and has the authority to make a final decision.</data>
  <data key="d9">complaint review,legal authority</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853804</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Nguyên đơn">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Nguyên đơn has the right to initiate a lawsuit or complaint with Tòa án if the arbitration agreement is deemed invalid or unenforceable.</data>
  <data key="d9">lawsuit,legal action</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853804</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Người làm chứng">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tòa án can issue a summoning decision for Người làm chứng to attend a hearing.</data>
  <data key="d9">summoning decision,witness attendance</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853899</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Hội đồng trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hội đồng trọng tài can request Tòa án to issue a summoning decision for a witness.&lt;SEP&gt;Tòa án can make decisions regarding the jurisdiction of disputes that are being handled by the Hội đồng trọng tài.&lt;SEP&gt;If the application of emergency measures causes damage, the affected party can file a lawsuit for compensation at Tòa án.</data>
  <data key="d9">dispute resolution,emergency measures,jurisdiction,legal recourse,request authority,summoning decision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b47a7db90a1e526f1797874efef64872</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853990</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Biện pháp khẩn cấp tạm thời">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tòa án can be requested to apply Biện pháp khẩn cấp tạm thời to prevent adverse actions during the arbitration process.</data>
  <data key="d9">application authority,emergency measures</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853900</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Các bên tranh chấp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Các bên tranh chấp can request Tòa án to apply temporary emergency measures.</data>
  <data key="d9">emergency measures,request authority</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c0133fbf4562d8d0b8d51451c1447d8e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853900</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Lệ phí toà án">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Lệ phí toà án are court fees associated with arbitration-related activities.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration,court fees</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853955</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Tòa án" target="Phán quyết trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tòa án is responsible for enforcing and reviewing arbitration decisions.</data>
  <data key="d9">enforcement,review</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d91f2a7788f7464204ab346b8f178828</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853955</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Pháp Luật Việt Nam">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Pháp Luật Việt Nam is the legal framework that governs actions and transactions within Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal jurisdiction,national law</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e84a045f0415483bb286ca0fb434f2f9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851356</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Người đại diện theo pháp luật">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Người đại diện theo pháp luật must reside in Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal representation,residency requirement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ead2cea9ac10e43e52710b6f386da07d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851421</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Người Nước Ngoài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People from other countries are subject to certain legal provisions when present in Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal status,residency</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Pháp Nhân">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Legal entities are subject to the laws of the country where they are established, including Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">establishment,legal status</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Tài Sản">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Assets are subject to the laws of the country where they are located, including Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal status,location</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Quyền Sở Hữu Trí Tuệ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Intellectual property rights are determined by the laws of the country where the intellectual property is sought to be protected, including Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal status,protection</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Thừa Kế">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Inheritance is determined by the laws of the country where the deceased had citizenship, including Việt Nam.&lt;SEP&gt;The law of the country where the deceased had citizenship immediately before death applies to inheritance in Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">inheritance,inheritance law,legal application,legal status</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cda21c37a8b4d265d1fff1cf5f7aea</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851577</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Năng Lực Pháp Luật Dân Sự">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Civil legal capacity of individuals is determined by the laws of the country where they have citizenship, including Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">civil capacity,legal status</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Năng Lực Hành Vi Dân Sự">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Civil conduct capacity of individuals is determined by the laws of the country where they have citizenship, including Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">conduct capacity,legal status</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Việc Xác Định Cá Nhân Mất Tích Hoặc Chết">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The determination of a missing or deceased individual is based on the laws of the country where the individual had citizenship at the time of the last known information, including Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">determination,legal status</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Quyền Sở Hữu Và Quyền Khác Đối Với Tài Sản">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The establishment, exercise, modification, and termination of ownership and other rights over property are determined by the laws of the country where the property is located, including Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal status,property rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-140e730fed36193f2aad721cf39f1907</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851430</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Di Chúc">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The form of a di chúc is recognized in Việt Nam if it is consistent with the laws of the country where the testator resides or has citizenship.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal recognition,testamentary capacity</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b0cda21c37a8b4d265d1fff1cf5f7aea</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851577</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Giám Hộ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The law of the country where the person under guardianship resides applies to guardianship in Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">guardianship law,legal application</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b0cda21c37a8b4d265d1fff1cf5f7aea</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851577</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The applicable law for a hợp đồng is determined by the law of the country with the closest connection to the contract, and the form of the hợp đồng is recognized in Việt Nam if it is consistent with the laws of the country where the contract is made or with Vietnamese law.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract law,legal application</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b0cda21c37a8b4d265d1fff1cf5f7aea</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851577</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Chủ tịch công ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Chairman of the company must obtain permission before leaving Việt Nam for more than 30 days and must delegate authority in writing to another person.</data>
  <data key="d9">delegation of authority,travel authorization</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852369</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Kiểm soát viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">More than half of the kiểm soát viên must reside in Việt Nam.</data>
  <data key="d9">residency requirement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-373a8f0d009c4c6073d5e556bc2411e7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852933</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Việt Nam" target="Chi Nhánh Công Ty Mẹ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The branch of the parent company is located in Vietnam.</data>
  <data key="d9">branch placement,location</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-9aff8a680816d92d14d4a77e34dbfc7d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853234</data>
