<edge source="Cá Nhân" target="Bộ Luật">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">An individual's rights to protect their dignity, reputation, and honor are outlined in the legal document known as the law.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal rights,protection</data>
