</edge>
<edge source="Người Thừa Kế" target="Di Chúc">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The will specifies the distribution of the estate to the designated beneficiaries.&lt;SEP&gt;Di Chúc determines the distribution of inheritance to Người Thừa Kế.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Thừa Kế inherits a portion of the estate according to the will.&lt;SEP&gt;The heirs who inherit parts of the estate as specified in the will.</data>
  <data key="d9">beneficiary,distribution,heir,inheritance,legal document,will inheritance</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-9d35ed796002742aa2467cef9894f826&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71c1c580c8f92c3838ab0f997647d588&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65946ae20fedf99884e4b9e9ee2eea91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1bc911a64bb7c617404a95f58c39105</data>
