  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Người giám hộ is responsible for managing the affairs of Người được giám hộ, including legal transactions and protection of their rights.&lt;SEP&gt;A guardian is responsible for the care and management of a person under guardianship.</data>
  <data key="d9">guardianship,responsibility</data>
