  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Người giám hộ đương nhiên is the natural guardian who is appointed by law to manage the affairs of a person under guardianship.&lt;SEP&gt;A natural guardian is automatically assigned based on familial relationships.</data>
  <data key="d9">guardianship,legal appointment,natural assignment</data>
