</edge>
<edge source="Luật" target="Doanh Nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Luật defines the rights and obligations of enterprises, their owners, and the state.&lt;SEP&gt;The legal framework outlined in the Luật governs the operations and disclosures of a company.</data>
  <data key="d9">compliance,legal framework,rights and obligations</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-870356636a26bb390c46554c34ceb657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65e07d9d273b5f52fb62308b1cffe434</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853131</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Luật" target="Thành Viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Thành Viên's rights and responsibilities within the company are governed by the Luật.</data>
  <data key="d9">responsibilities,rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851803</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Luật" target="Hội đồng Thành viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hội đồng Thành viên operates within the legal framework defined by the Luật.</data>
  <data key="d9">governance,legal framework</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851808</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Luật" target="Tên Doanh Nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Luật provides the legal framework governing the naming of businesses, including regulations on prohibited names and overlapping names.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal framework,naming regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4d52676760b287e9164a8b2a57de3d57</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851844</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Luật" target="Cổ phần ưu đãi">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Luật, or the law, provides the legal framework for the regulation of Cổ phần ưu đãi, or preferred shares.</data>
