  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty cổ phần can have one or more legal representatives.&lt;SEP&gt;Người đại diện theo pháp luật is a legal representative of a company and has certain responsibilities.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal representation,representation,responsibility,rights and obligations</data>
