  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Văn Phòng Đại Diện is a subordinate unit of a foreign arbitration organization established to seek and promote arbitration opportunities in Vietnam.&lt;SEP&gt;Tổ chức trọng tài nước ngoài is responsible for the activities of its representative office and must ensure compliance with Vietnamese law.</data>
