  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Nhà nước inherits Di sản if there are no eligible heirs.&lt;SEP&gt;The state inherits the estate when there are no eligible heirs.</data>
  <data key="d9">asset management,inheritance,state inheritance,unclaimed</data>
