  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều 622 specifies that if there are no eligible heirs, the remaining assets belong to the state.</data>
  <data key="d9">asset management,state inheritance</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
