  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Định đoạt tài sản chung is the concept of disposing of shared property collectively by all owners.</data>
  <data key="d9">collective ownership,property disposal</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3c40b3ec985a74cfbf857d108074883e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849453</data>
