  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The owner has the right to modify the wall up to their boundary limit in the case of adjacent houses with touching walls.</data>
  <data key="d9">boundary modification,property rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7b345fbbc1125fb4f691693608eb8ffa</data>
