  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The owner has a responsibility to protect trees that serve as boundary markers between properties.</data>
  <data key="d9">boundary marker,shared responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7b345fbbc1125fb4f691693608eb8ffa</data>
