  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chủ Sở Hữu has the right to use property according to their will, as long as it does not cause harm or affect national, ethnic, public interests, or the legal rights and interests of others.</data>
  <data key="d9">property rights,usage rights</data>
