  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chủ Sở Hữu must respect and maintain the boundaries between adjacent real properties.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal agreement,property boundary</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-931c1ae4f95c0b01df5de17931b38de9</data>
