  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Thế Chấp Tài Sản Gắn Liền Với Đất involves collateralizing assets attached to the land without collateralizing the land use rights, depending on the relationship between the owner and the user of the land.</data>
  <data key="d9">asset ownership,collateralization</data>
