<edge source="Tài Sản Ký Cược" target="Ký Quỹ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Ký quỹ involves depositing collateral such as money, precious metals, or valuable documents into a blocked account at a financial institution.</data>
  <data key="d9">collateral,financial guarantee</data>
