<edge source="Bên Thuê" target="Tài Sản Thuê">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Thuê leases an asset and is responsible for returning it or paying for it if they do not return it.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Thuê has the right to use the Tài Sản Thuê as agreed upon in the lease agreement.</data>
  <data key="d9">lease agreement,leasing,return obligation,usage rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce15824853c084575e7d85b3e8d79015</data>
