<edge source="Bên Cho Thuê" target="Tài Sản Thuê">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Cho Thuê provides the leased asset and has the right to reclaim it if the lease terms are not met.&lt;SEP&gt;Bên Cho Thuê is responsible for delivering the Tài Sản Thuê in the agreed-upon condition and maintaining its usability.</data>
  <data key="d9">delivery obligations,lease agreement,leasing,reclaim right</data>
