  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The legal framework (Pháp Luật) governs the conditions and agreements related to securing future obligations under Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Trong Tương Lai.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal framework,obligation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
