  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The legal effect of Tài Sản Bảo Đảm against third parties arises from its registration or possession.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal effect,registration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-fc51b56c993488553c56dcd3c101b7ba</data>
