  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ can replace the original obligation with another if it cannot be fulfilled, provided it is accepted by Bên Có Quyền.</data>
  <data key="d9">fulfillment,obligation replacement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Riêng Rẽ" target="Nhiều Người">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Nhiều Người are responsible for their specific parts of the obligation, and each person is only required to fulfill their own part.</data>
  <data key="d9">individual responsibility,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Riêng Rẽ" target="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ is responsible for fulfilling their specific part of the obligation.</data>
  <data key="d9">fulfillment,individual obligation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Liên Đới" target="Nhiều Người">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Nhiều Người are jointly responsible for fulfilling the obligation, and the party with the right can demand any one of them to fulfill the entire obligation.</data>
  <data key="d9">joint responsibility,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Liên Đới" target="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ are jointly responsible for fulfilling the obligation, and Bên Có Quyền can demand any one of them to fulfill the entire obligation.</data>
  <data key="d9">fulfillment,joint obligation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Đối Với Nhiều Người Có Quyền Liên Đới" target="Nhiều Người Có Quyền">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Nhiều Người Có Quyền can each demand the fulfillment of the entire obligation from the party with the obligation.</data>
  <data key="d9">multiple rights holders,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Đối Với Nhiều Người Có Quyền Liên Đới" target="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ must fulfill the entire obligation to any of the multiple rights holders.</data>
  <data key="d9">multiple rights holders,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Phân Chia Được Theo Phần" target="Đối Tượng Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đối Tượng Nghĩa Vụ can be divided into parts for fulfillment.</data>
  <data key="d9">division,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Phân Chia Được Theo Phần" target="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ can fulfill the obligation in parts.</data>
  <data key="d9">divisible obligation,fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Không Phân Chia Được Theo Phần" target="Đối Tượng Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đối Tượng Nghĩa Vụ must be fulfilled all at once.</data>
  <data key="d9">obligation fulfillment,unified fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849853</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Nghĩa Vụ Không Phân Chia Được Theo Phần" target="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ must fulfill the obligation all at once.</data>
  <data key="d9">fulfillment,non-divisible obligation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849854</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ" target="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ includes various measures to ensure the fulfillment of obligations by Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ.</data>
  <data key="d9">obligation fulfillment,security measures</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849854</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Biện Pháp Bảo Đảm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ" target="Bên Soạn Thảo">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The drafting party's measures to ensure the fulfillment of obligations are not affected by the invalidity of the main contract.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract drafting,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850298</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Phạm Vi Nghĩa Vụ Được Bảo Đảm" target="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Phạm Vi Nghĩa Vụ Được Bảo Đảm refers to the scope of an obligation that can be secured for Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ, which can be partial or full, and can include current, future, or conditional obligations.</data>
  <data key="d9">obligation fulfillment,scope of security</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-09260b73faf8f3666f58d4852700adf4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849854</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Trách Nhiệm Dân Sự">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ is responsible for fulfilling an obligation and may be held liable for not doing so.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal obligation,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849907</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Sự Kiện Bất Khả Kháng">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ is exempt from civil liability if the failure to fulfill an obligation is due to an uncontrollable event.</data>
  <data key="d9">exemption,uncontrollable event</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849907</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Bên Có Quyền">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ must fulfill an obligation, and Bên Có Quyền can demand its fulfillment.</data>
  <data key="d9">demand,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849907</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Trách Nhiệm Tiếp Tục Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ must continue to fulfill an obligation if it has not been fulfilled correctly.</data>
  <data key="d9">continuation,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849907</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Chậm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ is responsible for the delay in fulfilling an obligation.</data>
  <data key="d9">delay,obligation fulfillment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849907</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Hoãn Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ must request postponement of fulfilling an obligation if it cannot be fulfilled on time.</data>
  <data key="d9">obligation fulfillment,postponement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849907</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Chậm Tiếp Nhận Việc Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ is responsible for the delay in accepting the fulfillment of an obligation.</data>
  <data key="d9">acceptance,delay</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849907</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Trách Nhiệm Do Không Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Giao Vật">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ is responsible for not fulfilling an obligation to deliver a specific item.</data>
  <data key="d9">delivery,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849908</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Trách Nhiệm Do Chậm Thực Hiện Nghĩa Vụ Trả Tiền">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ is responsible for delaying the payment of money.</data>
  <data key="d9">payment delay,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849908</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Lãi Suất">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ must pay interest on delayed payments.</data>
  <data key="d9">interest rate,payment delay</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e38fe034461862746b38b34d7647cf44</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849908</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Ký Quỹ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ deposits collateral as part of the ký quỹ process to ensure the fulfillment of their obligations.</data>
  <data key="d9">deposit,financial obligation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850113</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Nghĩa Vụ" target="Chuyển Giao Quyền Yêu Cầu">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The transfer of the right to demand is related to the party with the obligation.</data>
  <data key="d9">obligation,transfer</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850228</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Quyền" target="Ký Quỹ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Có Quyền receives financial protection and compensation through the ký quỹ process if the other party fails to fulfill their obligations.</data>
  <data key="d9">compensation,financial protection</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3baa9f51dbe3abee94b2d6af0d80324d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850113</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Có Quyền" target="Chuyển Giao Quyền Yêu Cầu">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The transfer of the right to demand is related to the party with the right.</data>
  <data key="d9">right,transfer</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850228</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Quyền Hưởng Dụng" target="Người Hưởng Dụng">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Quyền Hưởng Dụng grants the right to the user to exploit and benefit from the utility and income of another's property.&lt;SEP&gt;Người Hưởng Dụng has the right to use a property and is entitled to the benefits derived from it.</data>
  <data key="d9">benefit,exploitation,legal right,right</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3b5f857bd7e099346e71679265152a98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10afe4eee3cae5b91c443db8d0e7f12</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773849924</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Quyền Hưởng Dụng" target="Bất Động Sản">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bất Động Sản is the real estate property that can be subject to the right of use.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal right,property use</data>
