  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Nhận Bảo Đảm must comply with legal provisions regarding the processing and handling of collateral.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal compliance,obligation enforcement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c152b6a16d5764e941499e3920fc0f1d</data>
