  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Nhận Bảo Đảm has the right to agree on the value of collateral or to have it valued by an organization as per the regulations outlined in Điều 306.</data>
  <data key="d9">collateral valuation,legal right</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3cdb3cd8d8583064c0301937b6f4744a</data>
