  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bộ luật governs the procedures and conditions for canceling contracts due to the loss or damage of the subject matter of the contract as outlined in Điều 426.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract cancellation,legal code</data>
