<edge source="Điều 427" target="Bộ luật">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bộ luật governs the procedures and conditions for canceling contracts and the consequences thereof as outlined in Điều 427.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract cancellation,legal code</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4ab904047371ae7e8fd73b147f7f0612</data>
