  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Bộ luật provides the legal framework for the Hợp đồng vận chuyển tài sản, outlining the rights and responsibilities of the transportation company and the client.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract regulation,legal framework</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
