<edge source="Bộ luật" target="Cước phí vận chuyển">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Bộ luật provides regulations regarding the Cước phí vận chuyển, including the agreed-upon amount and the conditions for payment.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal regulation,transportation fee</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-1baf5b4c5d9b239e30e1e81e061a24dd</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850856</data>
