  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Article 358 of the Civil Code outlines the responsibilities for not performing or not being allowed to perform a task.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal provision,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-428a1a2119667172b8e431b501835f64</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
