  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">If the subject matter of a contract cannot be performed, the contract is invalid.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract invalidity,unperformable subject matter</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
