<edge source="Ý Chí Chung" target="Ngôn Từ Sử Dụng Trong Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">When there is a conflict between the mutual intent of the parties and the language used in the contract, the mutual intent is used to interpret the contract.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract interpretation,mutual intent</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
