</edge>
<edge source="Bên Soạn Thảo" target="Bên Kia">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">If the drafting party includes terms that are disadvantageous to the other party, the interpretation of the contract must favor the other party.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract drafting,disadvantage</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850298</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Soạn Thảo" target="Bất Lợi">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The drafting party may face a disadvantage when interpreting unclear or unfavorable contract terms.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract drafting,disadvantage</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850298</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Soạn Thảo" target="Miễn Trách Nhiệm">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The drafting party's attempt to include an exemption from liability is not valid if it increases the responsibility or removes the legitimate rights of the other party.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract drafting,invalid term</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850298</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Soạn Thảo" target="Tăng Trách Nhiệm">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The drafting party's attempt to increase the responsibility of the other party is not valid if it removes the legitimate rights of the other party.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract drafting,invalid term</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850298</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Soạn Thảo" target="Loại Bỏ Quyền Lợi Chính Đáng">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The drafting party's attempt to remove the legitimate rights of the other party is not valid if it increases the responsibility or removes the legitimate rights of the other party.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract drafting,invalid term</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850298</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Bên Soạn Thảo" target="Thiệt Hại">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">If the drafting party knows or should know that the contract's subject matter cannot be performed but does not inform the other party, they must compensate for the damages.</data>
  <data key="d9">contract drafting,damages</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-57605bee043e497a16d0db0a26012d1e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850298</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Thiệt Hại" target="Bên Sử Dụng Dịch Vụ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Bên Sử Dụng Dịch Vụ can request compensation for damages if the service provider breaches the agreement.</data>
  <data key="d9">agreement,compensation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e729376fa2e1544912532baf7015b267</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850703</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
