  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Thành viên hợp tác have rights and obligations defined in the Hợp đồng hợp tác, including the conditions for joining, leaving, and the dissolution of the cooperative.</data>
  <data key="d9">contractual relationship,rights and obligations</data>
