  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Thành viên hợp tác are responsible for the civil liabilities of the cooperative using the Tài sản chung, and if the Tài sản chung is insufficient, they must use their Tài sản riêng.</data>
  <data key="d9">asset management,civil liability</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-63bea5bd12d1af991f494c7882f65825</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850693</data>
