  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Di Tặng is the act of allocating a portion of the estate by the deceased person as specified in their will.</data>
  <data key="d9">allocation,will</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-65946ae20fedf99884e4b9e9ee2eea91</data>
