</edge>
<edge source="Công chứng viên" target="Di chúc miệng">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công chứng viên verifies and authenticates the signatures or marks of witnesses in a Di chúc miệng.</data>
  <data key="d9">notary,oral will authentication</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Di chúc hợp pháp" target="Đиều 630">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đиều 630 defines the conditions for a will to be considered legally valid, including the mental capacity of the person creating the will and the content of the will.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal validity,will creation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850995</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Di chúc miệng" target="Đиều 629">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đиều 629 outlines the conditions under which an oral will can be made and the process for validating it.</data>
  <data key="d9">emergency will,oral will</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850995</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Di chúc bằng văn bản" target="Đиều 628">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đиều 628 describes the different forms of written wills, including those with and without witnesses, and those that are notarized or authenticated.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal document,written will</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-47d8802df9ec7324759d67fe67eaf612</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773850994</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
