  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A person who suffers a loss due to another's benefit from their property without legal basis is entitled to have the benefit returned.&lt;SEP&gt;A person who benefits from another's property without legal basis must return the benefit to the person who suffered a loss.</data>
