  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Luật này provides the legal framework that includes the Quy tắc tố tụng trọng tài for arbitration proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal framework,procedural rules</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
