</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Phần vốn góp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The board of members decides on the distribution of capital contributions.</data>
  <data key="d9">board decision,capital contribution</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851722</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên is responsible for convening meetings of the company's governing body.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên is the chairperson of the board of members, appointed by the company owner or elected by the board members.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên is responsible for organizing the collection of opinions and making decisions within the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên is responsible for preparing and leading the meetings of Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên leads the governing body of the company.</data>
  <data key="d9">appointment,chairperson,decision-making,governance,leadership,meeting convening,organizational responsibility,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6291a8ad95bfac807fb62b2e4b103f5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-258ace9c6b166d80918c8f05daed0816&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853252</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Thành viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Thành viên are members of the company's governing body who can request meetings and participate in decision-making.</data>
  <data key="d9">meeting participation,member</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851900</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Công ty">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hội đồng thành viên is the governing body of the company responsible for making decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng thành viên makes decisions regarding the company's capital and profit distribution.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng thành viên is the Board of Members of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty is managed by the Hội đồng thành viên, which makes decisions regarding the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;The company's operations are governed by the Hội đồng thành viên, which makes decisions regarding the acceptance of new members and other matters.</data>
  <data key="d9">board decision,board of members,capital adjustment,company governance,decision-making,governance,management,organization</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853252</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Thông báo mời họp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Thông báo mời họp is the notice sent to members to attend meetings of the company's governing body.</data>
  <data key="d9">attendance,meeting notice</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851900</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Tài liệu họp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tài liệu họp are the documents and materials used during meetings of the company's governing body for decision-making.</data>
  <data key="d9">decision-making,meeting documents</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851900</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Điều 36">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hội đồng thành viên is involved in the valuation of assets contributed to capital in limited liability companies and partnerships.</data>
  <data key="d9">asset valuation,governing body</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-32bedb7a710b05aeaa67ceee9734170a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851903</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn một thành viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hội đồng thành viên is a board of members that manages the company, consisting of 3 to 7 members appointed by the company owner.</data>
  <data key="d9">governance,management</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851943</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Chủ tịch công ty">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chủ tịch công ty is a member of the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;The Chairman of the company is appointed by the company owner and is responsible for representing the owner and the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The Chairman of the company is appointed by the representative body of the owner and has specific duties and responsibilities.</data>
  <data key="d9">appointment,authority,board member,management structure,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852369</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Giám đốc">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Giám đốc is a member of the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Members appoints the Director to manage the company's daily business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Giám đốc or Tổng giám đốc is responsible for daily business operations and reports to Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng thành viên has the right to request information from the Giám đốc regarding the company's financial and operational status.&lt;SEP&gt;The Director is appointed by the Board of Members and has specific duties and responsibilities.</data>
  <data key="d9">appointment,authority,board member,daily operations,information request,leadership,management structure,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852369</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Tổng giám đốc">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tổng giám đốc is a member of the Hội đồng thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Members appoints the General Director to manage the company's daily business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng thành viên has the right to request information from the Tổng giám đốc regarding the company's financial and operational status.&lt;SEP&gt;The General Director is appointed by the Board of Members and has specific duties and responsibilities.</data>
  <data key="d9">appointment,authority,board member,information request,leadership,management,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e6d8ee78ba16dc478897165155df59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17a82be5a9b46c4919412e37814adb6d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852369</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Ban kiểm soát">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Ban kiểm soát is a member of the Hội đồng thành viên.</data>
  <data key="d9">board member,management structure</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-246618b082091a628ff89e93d59fc956</data>
