</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng thành viên" target="Thành viên góp vốn">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hội đồng thành viên can decide to exclude a thành viên góp vốn who fails to meet their capital contribution obligations.</data>
  <data key="d9">decision making,exclusion</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-1efb55d02317343a2ef5f32d5d741bc9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853200</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Cổ phần ưu đãi">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đại hội đồng cổ đông, or the shareholders' meeting, can decide on the purchase of preferred shares and the conversion of preferred shares into common shares.&lt;SEP&gt;Decisions regarding the rights and privileges of Cổ phần ưu đãi are made at the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">conversion,decision making,decision-making,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852687</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Cổ đông phổ thông">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Common shareholders have the right to attend, speak, and vote at the General Shareholders' Meeting.&lt;SEP&gt;Common shareholders must notify the General Shareholders' Meeting about their group meetings for nominating individuals to the Board of Directors and Supervisory Board.</data>
  <data key="d9">meeting,notification,shareholder rights,voting rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01b556fba8ab897e9f334300f225003e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852384</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông participates in the general meeting of shareholders and has the right to vote.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông participate in the Đại hội đồng cổ đông to make decisions regarding the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông have the right to attend and vote at the meeting.&lt;SEP&gt;Shareholders participate in the meeting and vote on matters discussed.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông participates in the Đại hội đồng cổ đông to discuss and vote on important matters related to the company.</data>
  <data key="d9">decision-making,participation,shareholder,shareholder participation,shareholder rights,voting,voting rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c9b32b2b806556ed1dd36c13de6e313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853049</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Hội đồng quản trị">
  <data key="d7">6.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The General Shareholders' Meeting makes decisions regarding the nomination of individuals to the Board of Directors.&lt;SEP&gt;The Đại hội đồng cổ đông elects members of the Hội đồng quản trị.&lt;SEP&gt;The board of directors is involved in the governance decisions made during the meeting of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị is responsible for reporting to and being overseen by Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị is responsible for managing the company and must convene a meeting of Đại hội đồng cổ đông under certain conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị is responsible for organizing and communicating with shareholders at the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">board of directors,decision making,election,governance,management,meeting organization,organizational structure,oversight,reporting,shareholder communication</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-01b556fba8ab897e9f334300f225003e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8031309e714112ffe63df75b002d2d14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-952bef1a1bafd78690b17fd797f3d33e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853145</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Ban kiểm soát">
  <data key="d7">6.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The General Shareholders' Meeting makes decisions regarding the nomination of individuals to the Supervisory Board.&lt;SEP&gt;The Đại hội đồng cổ đông elects members of the Ban kiểm soát.&lt;SEP&gt;The audit committee is involved in the governance decisions made during the meeting of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Ban kiểm soát reports to and receives decisions from Đại hội đồng cổ đông regarding the company's operations and policies.&lt;SEP&gt;Ban kiểm soát reports to and participates in the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Ban kiểm soát is responsible for reporting to and being overseen by Đại hội đồng cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">audit committee,decision making,decision-making,election,governance,oversight,participation,reporting,supervision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-01b556fba8ab897e9f334300f225003e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-795fb9faa3ff64c104def58573301724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852993</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Công ty">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty can reduce its registered capital based on the decision made at the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Đại hội đồng cổ đông is the highest decision-making body of the company and is composed of all shareholders with voting rights.</data>
  <data key="d9">capital reduction,decision making,highest decision-making body,shareholder meeting</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852818</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Cổ phần">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đại hội đồng cổ đông decides on the sale of shares to raise capital for the corporation.</data>
  <data key="d9">capital raising,shareholder decision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852482</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Điều lệ công ty">
  <data key="d7">6.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The procedures and decisions of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông are also regulated by the Điều lệ công ty.&lt;SEP&gt;Decisions at the Đại hội đồng cổ đông are guided by the rules set in the Điều lệ công ty.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều lệ công ty outlines the rules and procedures for conducting the meeting.&lt;SEP&gt;The meeting of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông is governed by the company's charter or bylaws.&lt;SEP&gt;The company's charter or bylaws govern the meeting of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;The company's charter may contain specific rules for the shareholders' meeting.</data>
  <data key="d9">company bylaws,company charter,company governance,decision-making,governance,meeting rules,regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c9b32b2b806556ed1dd36c13de6e313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852817</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Nghị quyết">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Đại hội đồng cổ đông passes Nghị quyết, which are resolutions.&lt;SEP&gt;The resolution is the outcome of the General Shareholders' Meeting.&lt;SEP&gt;Nghị quyết is passed at the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;The Đại hội đồng cổ đông passes resolutions on various issues related to the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The resolutions are passed during the meeting of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">decision making,decision-making,meeting outcome,resolution,resolution passing</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852784</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Biên bản họp Đại hội đồng cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The minutes of the General Shareholders' Meeting document the proceedings of the meeting.</data>
  <data key="d9">event record,meeting documentation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852634</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Báo cáo tài chính">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Đại hội đồng cổ đông reviews and approves the company's financial reports.&lt;SEP&gt;The annual financial report is reviewed and approved during the meeting of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;The Đại hội đồng cổ đông reviews and approves the annual financial report.</data>
  <data key="d9">decision making,decision-making,financial reporting,financial review</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852784</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Biểu quyết">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Decisions at the Đại hội đồng cổ đông are made through the process of biểu quyết.&lt;SEP&gt;Voting is conducted during the shareholders' meeting to make decisions on discussed matters.</data>
  <data key="d9">decision making,decision-making,voting,voting method</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852817</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Tổ chức lại công ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Đại hội đồng cổ đông makes decisions regarding the restructuring of the company.</data>
  <data key="d9">company restructuring,decision-making</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852687</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Giải thể công ty">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Đại hội đồng cổ đông makes decisions regarding the dissolution of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The meeting of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông can make decisions regarding the dissolution or liquidation of the company.</data>
  <data key="d9">company dissolution,decision-making,dissolution,meeting decision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98602a1920269703e171e36e577b9933</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852784</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Bầu dồn phiếu">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The method of bầu dồn phiếu is used during the Đại hội đồng cổ đông for electing members.</data>
  <data key="d9">election,voting method</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0e1d93dc94342974419c33affd5c6109</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852687</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Đại hội đồng cổ đông" target="Người triệu tập họp">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Người triệu tập họp is responsible for organizing the meeting and sending out notifications to all shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;The person who calls the meeting may have certain rights during the shareholders' meeting.</data>
  <data key="d9">meeting convocation,meeting organization,notification,rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3c9b32b2b806556ed1dd36c13de6e313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ec2f0c0c76fa5e26ffa97f0626d61d8</data>
