<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Cổ phần phổ thông">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông, or shareholders, own Cổ phần phổ thông, or common shares, and have rights and obligations associated with these shares.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông holds common shares in a company and has certain rights and obligations.</data>
  <data key="d9">ownership,rights,shareholder rights</data>
