<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Cổ phần ưu đãi">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông, or shareholders, can own Cổ phần ưu đãi, or preferred shares, which come with specific rights and benefits.</data>
  <data key="d9">ownership,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852269</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Người góp vốn">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Người góp vốn, or individuals who contribute capital, become Cổ đông, or shareholders, after paying for their shares.</data>
  <data key="d9">capital contribution,shareholder status</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dd21806392f264f4bbe4bbe4d4c4686a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852269</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Sổ đăng ký cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông's ownership of shares is recorded in the Sổ đăng ký cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">ownership,record</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852299</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Điều lệ công ty">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông's rights and responsibilities are defined by the Điều lệ công ty.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông must comply with the articles of association of the company and has certain rights and obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông must adhere to the rules and regulations outlined in Điều lệ công ty.</data>
  <data key="d9">company rules,compliance,regulations,responsibilities,rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853049</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Đề nghị của cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông makes a request regarding lost, damaged, or destroyed shares and assumes responsibility for any disputes arising from the issuance of new shares.</data>
  <data key="d9">request,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852299</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Công ty cổ phần">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông has rights and responsibilities regarding the company's shares and must notify the company of any changes in contact information.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông are the owners of Công ty cổ phần and have rights and responsibilities regarding the company's debts and assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông are shareholders of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;A shareholder can transfer their shares to another shareholder or a non-shareholder entity.</data>
  <data key="d9">ownership,responsibilities,share transfer,shareholder,shareholder relationship,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-643d72cdd6873e78e2d39abbf824c8bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b892718f9850a0f9775f9a075fb4282&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0359f960f337b0c62d24c54f784fc5c1</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853412</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Cổ phiếu">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông holds a share certificate and has certain rights and obligations.</data>
  <data key="d9">ownership,rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-705217d07d78fdf7f9b9f642d9c62131</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852337</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Hội đồng quản trị">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hội đồng quản trị is responsible for supervising and enforcing the timely payment of shares by Cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">payment enforcement,supervision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852413</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông must pay for the shares they have registered to purchase within 90 days of the company receiving the Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp.</data>
  <data key="d9">payment obligation,registration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852413</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Cổ phần">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông must pay for the Cổ phần they have registered to purchase.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông have the right to freely transfer their Cổ phần to others, except in certain cases defined by the law.</data>
  <data key="d9">ownership,payment obligation,transferability</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-643d72cdd6873e78e2d39abbf824c8bc</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852486</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Điều 113">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều 113 outlines the rules for the payment of shares by Cổ đông and the consequences of non-payment.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal compliance,payment obligation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852413</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Điều 122">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều 122 outlines the rules for the registration of shareholders and the recording of their information in the shareholder register.</data>
  <data key="d9">information recording,registration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852413</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Cổ phần ưu đãi cổ tức">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông has the right to receive higher dividends with Cổ phần ưu đãi cổ tức shares.</data>
  <data key="d9">dividend rights,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852515</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Cổ phần ưu đãi hoàn lại">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông has the right to request the return of capital with Cổ phần ưu đãi hoàn lại shares.</data>
  <data key="d9">capital return,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852515</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Cổ phần ưu đãi biểu quyết">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông has the right to vote with Cổ phần ưu đãi biểu quyết shares.</data>
  <data key="d9">shareholder rights,voting rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852515</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Quyền biểu quyết">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông has the right to vote in the company's decisions.</data>
  <data key="d9">shareholder rights,voting rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852515</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Quyền dự họp Đại hội đồng cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông has the right to attend the General Shareholders' Meeting.</data>
  <data key="d9">meeting attendance,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852515</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Quyền đề cử người vào Hội đồng quản trị và Ban kiểm soát">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông has the right to nominate individuals to the Board of Directors and Supervisory Board.</data>
  <data key="d9">nomination rights,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-202753da85e57657b151764c6fce4516</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852515</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông can also request Trọng tài to invalidate a resolution.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông can use Trọng tài as an alternative mechanism for resolving disputes.</data>
  <data key="d9">alternative dispute resolution,legal challenge,resolution validity</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0d89efd1fdb6a40038e6d94da77b9503&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-954105a0b477a911ae8062a76843dd6d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853050</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Nghị quyết">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Shareholders can request the court or arbitration to review and potentially annul a resolution of the General Shareholders' Meeting.&lt;SEP&gt;Nghị quyết must be sent to Cổ đông within 15 days after the vote concludes.</data>
  <data key="d9">document distribution,legal review,resolution annulment,shareholder communication</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-f51c1c7d8dc322ea0482246dd5006bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852655</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Biên bản kiểm phiếu">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Biên bản kiểm phiếu must be sent to Cổ đông within 15 days after the vote concludes.</data>
  <data key="d9">document distribution,shareholder communication</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-41f68c70a7b80565ad868f52d176ce38</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852655</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Danh sách cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Danh sách cổ đông is created based on the Sổ đăng ký cổ đông and includes shareholders who have the right to attend the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ đông have the right to inspect, verify, extract, and copy their information from the Danh sách cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">attendance rights,information access,shareholder list,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852661</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Kiến nghị">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông have the right to submit proposals to be included in the agenda of the Đại hội đồng cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">meeting agenda,proposal submission</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852661</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Công ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông have the right to receive dividends and participate in the decision-making process of the company.</data>
  <data key="d9">dividend payment,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852818</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Cổ đông" target="Báo cáo">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông has the right to examine certain reports under specific conditions.</data>
  <data key="d9">examination,right</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b0cdd7174a5289f85d735aa45cd8829d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852994</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người quản lý công ty" target="Công ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty is managed by the Người quản lý công ty, who oversees the company's operations.</data>
  <data key="d9">management,oversight</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852454</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người quản lý công ty" target="Danh sách cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Người quản lý công ty is responsible for providing information from the Sổ đăng ký cổ đông and correcting or supplementing inaccurate information in the Danh sách cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">information management,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-29365a5c3fbe3ae076f76826fc009a7a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852661</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người quản lý công ty" target="Giải thể doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Company managers are responsible for the dissolution process and its compliance with regulations.</data>
  <data key="d9">compliance,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853653</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp is the registration certificate for a Doanh nghiệp.&lt;SEP&gt;A business entity is issued a Certificate of Business Registration when it meets certain conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp can have its registration certificate revoked under certain conditions.</data>
  <data key="d9">business entity,issuance,registration,registration certificate,revocation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Business Registration Authority is responsible for issuing the Certificate of Business Registration and reviewing registration documents.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh is responsible for issuing the Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp to a company after it meets the required conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh issues the Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp to confirm the registration of a business.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh issues certificates to businesses upon successful registration.</data>
  <data key="d9">issuance,legal document,registration,review</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8da64b48c80fc4788c324e08350a340e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a788d203fae6d3c78c81ae71ea9171e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09d578fe732c3cb08c15e944096d74cd</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853599</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Arbitration can make decisions that lead to changes in the content of the Certificate of Business</data>
  <data key="d9">change,decision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851651</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
