  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The partner members of a partnership company are included in the Certificate of Business Registration.&lt;SEP&gt;The công ty hợp danh gains legal status upon receiving the Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp.</data>
  <data key="d9">inclusion,legal status,registration</data>
