  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The business registration certificate is issued when a limited liability company with two or more members is formed.</data>
  <data key="d9">company formation,registration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851722</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn một thành viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The one-member limited liability company is recognized legally upon receiving the certificate of business registration.</data>
  <data key="d9">company establishment,legal recognition</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851977</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Sổ đăng ký cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Sổ đăng ký cổ đông must be established from the time the company receives the Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp.</data>
  <data key="d9">registration,requirement</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dc2c4537017d8abf8400a3fc36e9aa3e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852299</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Công ty cổ phần">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty cổ phần gains legal entity status upon receiving the Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty cổ phần obtains legal status from the date it is issued a Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty cổ phần receives a business registration certificate after completing its formation.</data>
  <data key="d9">document issuance,legal entity status,legal registration,legal status,registration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-643d72cdd6873e78e2d39abbf824c8bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4a657b345d0676b5a5d6451a2c7c13d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853385</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Cơ sở dữ liệu quốc gia về đăng ký doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cơ sở dữ liệu quốc gia về đăng ký doanh nghiệp tracks the legal status of registered businesses, including the issuance of the Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal status,tracking</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-8da64b48c80fc4788c324e08350a340e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853285</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn receives a business registration certificate after completing its conversion.</data>
  <data key="d9">document issuance,legal registration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e4a657b345d0676b5a5d6451a2c7c13d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853385</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Chính phủ">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chính phủ sets the procedures for revoking the business registration certificate.&lt;SEP&gt;Chính phủ defines the procedures for revoking a business's registration certificate.</data>
  <data key="d9">procedure,regulation,revocation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-485e8c7bee0cdf1c48988e4c3d34522f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Giải thể doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The revocation of the business registration certificate can lead to the dissolution of a business.</data>
  <data key="d9">dissolution trigger,legal document</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c9f7a6499f6482b84c0cafd640523108</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853652</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hồ sơ đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Đиều 26">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đиều 26 specifies the responsibility of the Business Registration Application to be submitted to the Business Registration Authority for registering a business.</data>
  <data key="d9">regulation,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-65896b1415c5fb67acfcda61d9b89291</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851643</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hồ sơ đăng ký doanh nghiệp" target="Doanh nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A business entity must submit valid and complete registration documents.</data>
  <data key="d9">registration,submission</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a8de4c57592fe998c634734476be0f10</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851651</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Vốn điều lệ" target="Chủ sở hữu công ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The owner of the company is responsible for contributing the registered capital and is liable for the company's financial obligations.</data>
  <data key="d9">capital contribution,financial responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851977</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Vốn điều lệ" target="Công ty">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty can increase or decrease its registered capital, referred to as Vốn điều lệ.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty must adjust its registered capital based on the payment status of shares by Cổ đông.</data>
  <data key="d9">capital adjustment,payment status,registered capital</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-03d808b04d1d049b480a85951d6f999f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afb6321b2b86d4ca9f69b3b408f671a7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852413</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Vốn điều lệ" target="Công ty cổ phần">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty cổ phần's registered capital is determined by the total face value of shares sold.</data>
  <data key="d9">capital,financial regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-181537e875bd1f5ba6572b043272e618</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852482</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Pháp Luật Việt Nam" target="Hành Vi Pháp Lý Đơn Phương">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Pháp Luật Việt Nam governs the legal acts of individuals and legal entities in the context of unilateral legal actions.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal regulation,unilateral acts</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e84a045f0415483bb286ca0fb434f2f9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851355</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Pháp Luật Việt Nam" target="Nghĩa Vụ Hoàn Trả">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Pháp Luật Việt Nam determines the obligations to return assets or benefits obtained without legal basis.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal regulation,obligations</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e84a045f0415483bb286ca0fb434f2f9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851355</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Pháp Luật Việt Nam" target="Thực Hiện Công Việc Không Có Ủy Quyền">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Pháp Luật Việt Nam governs the performance of tasks without authorization.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal regulation,unauthorized actions</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e84a045f0415483bb286ca0fb434f2f9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851356</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Pháp Luật Việt Nam" target="Bồi Thường Thiệt Hại Ngoài Hợp Đồng">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Pháp Luật Việt Nam governs the compensation for damages outside of a contract.</data>
  <data key="d9">compensation,legal regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e84a045f0415483bb286ca0fb434f2f9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851356</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Pháp Luật Việt Nam" target="Điều Khoản Chuyển Tiếp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Pháp Luật Việt Nam outlines the transitional provisions for civil transactions established before the new law takes effect.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal regulation,transitional provisions</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e84a045f0415483bb286ca0fb434f2f9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851356</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Pháp Luật Việt Nam" target="Giao Dịch Dân Sự">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Pháp Luật Việt Nam governs the legal framework for civil transactions, including their content and form.</data>
  <data key="d9">civil transactions,legal regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e84a045f0415483bb286ca0fb434f2f9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851356</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều Khoản Chuyển Tiếp" target="Bộ Luật Dân Sự Số 33/2005/QH11">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The transitional provisions specify the continued application of Bộ Luật Dân Sự Số 33/2005/QH11 for certain civil transactions.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal transition,previous law</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e84a045f0415483bb286ca0fb434f2f9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851355</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Công Ty Mẹ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include the parent company and its managers.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,ownership</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Công Ty Con">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include the subsidiary company and its managers.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,ownership</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Người Quản Lý Doanh Nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include managers of private enterprises and companies.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,management</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Người Thành Lập Doanh Nghiệp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include individuals or organizations that establish or contribute capital to establish a business.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,establishment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Nhà Đầu Tư Nước Ngoài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include foreign individuals or organizations as defined by the Investment Law.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,foreign investment</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851383</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Phần Vốn Góp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include those with the ability to control the business through ownership or capital contribution.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,capital contribution</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851383</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Sản Phẩm, Dịch Vụ Công Ích">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include those involved in essential products and services for the economic and social life of the country, locality, or community.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,public interest</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851383</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Thành Viên Công Ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include individuals or organizations that own a part or the entire registered capital of a limited liability company or partnership.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,ownership</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851383</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Thành Viên Công Ty Hợp Danh">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include members of a partnership, including general partners and capital contributors.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,ownership</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851383</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Vốn Có Quyền Biểu Quyết">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include those with voting rights on issues within the authority of the board of members or the general meeting of shareholders.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,voting rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851383</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Người Có Liên Quan" target="Bố Đẻ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include the biological father of managers and legal representatives.</data>
  <data key="d9">business,family relationship</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851383</data>
