</edge>
<edge source="Tổ Chức Nước Ngoài" target="Người Có Liên Qu">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">People or organizations with direct or indirect relationships to a business include foreign organizations established abroad under foreign law.</data>
  <data key="d9">business relationship,foreign organization</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-6e46e77902b28cf799e37bb0e795f60c</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851382</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Doanh nghiệp" target="Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh">
  <data key="d7">6.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Doanh nghiệp must notify Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh of changes in its registration content.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp registers branches, representative offices, and business locations with the registration authority.&lt;SEP&gt;Business entities must register with the registration authority and follow regulations for suspension, cessation, and termination.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh is responsible for registering the business entity and updating its legal status.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh is responsible for registering businesses and supervising their compliance with legal requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp must report to and register with Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh.</data>
  <data key="d9">approval,legal process,notification,registration,registration change,regulation,reporting,supervision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4751985bdb7ed5cd1ede693d8fa04ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-873972be10253bbd19fcbea390d18db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09d578fe732c3cb08c15e944096d74cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f9f1328d58ac04c74cf2a1422490ab</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853703</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Doanh nghiệp" target="Cổ đông sáng lập">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông sáng lập are the founding shareholders of a Doanh nghiệp.</data>
  <data key="d9">founding,shareholder</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851613</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Doanh nghiệp" target="Cổ đông là nhà đầu tư nước ngoài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ đông là nhà đầu tư nước ngoài are foreign investors who are shareholders in a Doanh nghiệp.</data>
  <data key="d9">foreign investment,shareholder</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851613</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Doanh nghiệp" target="Ngành, nghề kinh doanh">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Ngành, nghề kinh doanh refers to the business sectors or industries in which a Doanh nghiệp operates.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp must include information about the business sectors and industries in which it operates in its registration information.</data>
  <data key="d9">business sector,business sectors,operation,registration information</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851714</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Doanh nghiệp" target="Sổ đăng ký cổ đông">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Sổ đăng ký cổ đông is the shareholder register of a Doanh nghiệp.</data>
  <data key="d9">business entity,shareholder register</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851613</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Doanh nghiệp" target="Hồ sơ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hồ sơ are the documents and records required for the registration and change of a Doanh nghiệp's registration content.</data>
  <data key="d9">business entity,registration document</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851613</data>
