  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trụ sở chính is the main office or headquarters of a Doanh nghiệp.&lt;SEP&gt;Doanh nghiệp has a main office located within the territory of Vietnam.</data>
  <data key="d9">business entity,location,main office</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3fed1e090b51d7382ec575f352792a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7fe6829fe23e522eebc6b5e94e0f4e3</data>
