  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Doanh nghiệp must include the list of foreign investor shareholders in its registration information.</data>
  <data key="d9">foreign investor shareholders,registration information</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-64b8fad75bc3785889ce216fbcf53556</data>
