</edge>
<edge source="Công ty cổ phần" target="Điều 203">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Article 203 provides the legal framework for converting a joint-stock company into a single-member limited liability company.</data>
  <data key="d9">conversion process,legal provision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0359f960f337b0c62d24c54f784fc5c1</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853412</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Công ty cổ phần" target="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên inherits all legal rights and obligations of the công ty cổ phần after conversion.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty cổ phần can be converted into a công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên through various methods.</data>
  <data key="d9">company type,conversion,legal inheritance,successor</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a788d203fae6d3c78c81ae71ea9171e4</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853456</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Phần vốn góp">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The articles of association include the total value of capital contributions made by members.&lt;SEP&gt;The rules and regulations regarding Phần vốn góp are outlined in the Điều lệ công ty.</data>
  <data key="d9">articles of association,capital contribution,governance,ownership</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-2eb9bbbcf6b6e613956612e1bdbdc127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851808</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Thành Viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Thành Viên's rights and responsibilities within the company are governed by the Điều lệ công ty.</data>
  <data key="d9">responsibilities,rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851803</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Công Ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The company follows the procedures and regulations outlined in the Điều lệ công ty for maintaining the Sổ Đăng Ký Thành Viên and issuing Giấy Chứng Nhận Phần Vốn Góp.</data>
  <data key="d9">maintenance,regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-fce2849b8973f1a159252908a132579a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851803</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Hội đồng Thành viên">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hội đồng Thành viên is guided by the Điều lệ công ty in making decisions and overseeing the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng Thành viên follows the rules and procedures outlined in the company's charter or bylaws.</data>
  <data key="d9">charter,governance,governance rules,procedural guidelines</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba435d4c67d66b1792235911ac871358</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851841</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn một thành viên">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều lệ công ty is the charter for a Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn một thành viên.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều lệ công ty outlines the structure, operations, and responsibilities of the company's management.</data>
  <data key="d9">charter,company type,governance,structure</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851943</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều lệ công ty is the charter for a Công ty trách nhiệm hữu hạn hai thành viên trở lên.</data>
  <data key="d9">charter,company_ company type</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4c4083a7e93b6ad10b316c67434aca7b</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851808</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chủ tịch Hội đồng thành viên must follow the procedures outlined in the company's charter or bylaws for convening meetings.</data>
  <data key="d9">bylaw compliance,meeting procedures</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0941ba0e34f54b5fcc1460ed44a10cff</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851900</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Chủ sở hữu công ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The owner of the company has rights and responsibilities as defined by the company's charter.</data>
  <data key="d9">decision-making,ownership rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-21e60fc19506b5cf181276cb00664680</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773851977</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Tổng giám đốc">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The General Director must comply with the company charter and is responsible for managing the company's daily business operations.</data>
  <data key="d9">compliance,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852026</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Giám đốc">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Director must comply with the company charter and is responsible for managing the company's daily business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều lệ công ty defines the rights and obligations of the Giám đốc or Tổng giám đốc.</data>
  <data key="d9">authority,compliance,regulation,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d99794c741473468cfbf38d98973119</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852229</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Chủ tịch công ty">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Chairman of the company must comply with the company charter and is responsible for representing the owner and the company.</data>
  <data key="d9">compliance,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-96b35fb948543da5055202eeb7113790</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852026</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Chủ tịch và thành viên khác của Hội đồng thành viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Board of Members must adhere to the company's charter.</data>
  <data key="d9">adherence,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-021cabd4b6f739295249d57f4b27fdfe</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852051</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Nghị quyết, quyết định">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The company charter (Điều lệ công ty) specifies the exact ratio required for passing resolutions or decisions (Nghị quyết, quyết định) by the Board of Members.</data>
  <data key="d9">governance,regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a4225ac646c0bc252a11873ee034ed86</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852147</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Công ty">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The company charter is the internal document that outlines the responsibilities and procedures within the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty must follow the rules and regulations outlined in the Điều lệ công ty.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều lệ công ty outlines the rules and regulations governing the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Điều lệ công ty outlines the rights and obligations of the company's members.</data>
  <data key="d9">bylaws,charter,company regulations,governance,internal document,regulation,responsibilities</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e45e97cff69c56c799c5135afa6fb9b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41835b63d2a39e7a4ba760332a2b8046&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f4215d40e0caccca1eaa62a7f0ec73</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853252</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Điều lệ công ty" target="Người được quyền mua cổ phần ưu đãi">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều lệ công ty, or the company's charter, regulates who has the right to purchase Cổ phần ưu đãi, or preferred shares.</data>
