<edge source="Hội đồng quản trị" target="Cổ đông phổ thông">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Common shareholders have the right to request the Audit Committee to review specific issues related to the management and operation of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The Board of Directors is responsible for managing the company and making decisions, and its actions can be reviewed by shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Common shareholders have the right to nominate individuals to the Board of Directors.</data>
  <data key="d9">governance,management oversight,management responsibility,nomination rights,rights to request review</data>
