  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Quy chế hoạt động Hội đồng quản trị outlines the procedures and responsibilities for the board's activities.</data>
  <data key="d9">board operations,governance procedures</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5</data>
