</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng quản trị" target="Ủy ban kiểm toán">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The audit committee is directly under the board of directors and is responsible for overseeing the financial activities of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The Audit Committee oversees and has authority over certain financial and internal control matters, reporting to the Board of Directors.&lt;SEP&gt;Ủy ban kiểm toán is a specialized committee under the Hội đồng quản trị responsible for auditing and monitoring the company's financial reports and internal controls.</data>
  <data key="d9">audit committee,authority,governance,organizational structure,oversight</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8031309e714112ffe63df75b002d2d14</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853082</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng quản trị" target="Thư ký công ty">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The secretary of the company supports the organization of meetings of the Board of Directors.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng quản trị appoints the Thư ký công ty to assist in administrative duties and support the board's activities.&lt;SEP&gt;Thư ký công ty supports the Hội đồng quản trị in administrative duties and assists in the board's activities.</data>
  <data key="d9">administrative duties,organization,support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-2ec32bc0d8c57985cdac3f5a1383a2dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-952bef1a1bafd78690b17fd797f3d33e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853145</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng quản trị" target="Kiểm soát viên">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Kiểm soát viên has the right to access information and reports from Hội đồng quản trị and is responsible for overseeing the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Kiểm soát viên cannot be a family member of the members of Hội đồng quản trị.</data>
  <data key="d9">family relationship prohibition,information access,oversight</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8bb762ad781038843f3cf2f3790105d</data>
