<edge source="Cổ Đông" target="Công Ty">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công Ty is responsible for updating shareholder information and is not liable for failing to contact shareholders due to lack of updated address information.&lt;SEP&gt;Công Ty must pay dividends to Cổ Đông according to the regulations and must ensure it can still meet its financial obligations after paying dividends.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ Đông has the right to request changes in the shareholder register within 24 hours, as per the company's regulations.</data>
  <data key="d9">communication,dividend payment,regulation,responsibility,shareholder rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e71cfa12d80240b04312d94d8b626b87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af079df7102c58f84652bfeb21c7a17a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d51bd5f46e7b6f5ff0359fca2898b0ed</data>
