  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Business Registration Agency accesses information on the National Information System for Business Registration.&lt;SEP&gt;Cơ quan đăng ký kinh doanh manages the national information system for business registration.</data>
  <data key="d9">data access,information system,management</data>
