<edge source="Ban kiểm soát" target="Kiểm soát viên">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Kiểm soát viên is a member of the supervisory board, responsible for overseeing the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Ban kiểm soát is composed of Kiểm soát viên who are responsible for supervising the company's operations and ensuring the company's interests are protected.&lt;SEP&gt;Ban kiểm soát consists of 3 to 5 kiểm soát viên, each with a term not exceeding 5 years.</data>
  <data key="d9">membership,organization member,oversight,supervision,supervisory role,term</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-a4cc0849888b2ab85d179a3c3efe5e7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d51643ce273eae22725bc9b7424a745&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-373a8f0d009c4c6073d5e556bc2411e7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852933</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Ban kiểm soát" target="Điều 103">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều 103 details the establishment of the Supervisory Board of a company.</data>
  <data key="d9">establishment,supervisory board</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-33f981a65016c41f688ba0ac17a35ac7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852277</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Ban kiểm soát" target="Cổ đông phổ thông">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Audit Committee is responsible for reviewing specific issues related to the management and operation of the company upon request by shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Common shareholders can request the Audit Committee to review specific issues related to the management and operation of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Common shareholders have the right to nominate individuals to the Supervisory Board.</data>
  <data key="d9">audit request,governance,management oversight,nomination rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c8778f64e7716832bf2ad7d755875a3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01b556fba8ab897e9f334300f225003e</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852384</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Ban kiểm soát" target="Công ty">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Ban kiểm soát is the audit committee of the company, responsible for overseeing the financial activities and ensuring compliance with regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Công ty has a Ban kiểm soát which oversees the company's operations.</data>
  <data key="d9">audit committee,company structure,financial oversight,supervision</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-8245b988239aa1f9c2e280f1734f8ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-373a8f0d009c4c6073d5e556bc2411e7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773852933</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
