  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A state-owned economic group can be managed under the form of a limited liability company or a joint-stock company.</data>
  <data key="d9">management structure,state ownership</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-823e07d4a480b69d7f6ec00924cb4793</data>
