  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Cổ phần phổ thông, or common shares, serve as the basis for the issuance of Chứng chỉ lưu ký không có quyền biểu quyết, or non-voting depositary receipts, which have economic benefits and corresponding obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;Cổ phần phổ thông is used as the underlying asset for issuing non-voting deposit certificates, which have economic benefits and obligations equivalent to common stock.</data>
