  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Audit Committee reviews the internal control systems of the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Ủy ban kiểm toán is responsible for reviewing the company's internal control system and risk management.</data>
  <data key="d9">audit,monitoring,oversight,review</data>
