  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Audit Committee reviews transactions with related parties and recommends approval from the Board of Directors or General Shareholders' Meeting.&lt;SEP&gt;Ủy ban kiểm toán is responsible for reviewing transactions with related parties and providing recommendations for approval.</data>
  <data key="d9">audit,monitoring,recommendation,review</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-df9831e320198a4b066f7cdd1b9bbfe0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8031309e714112ffe63df75b002d2d14</data>
