  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Công ty bị hợp nhất are merged into Công ty hợp nhất, which then inherits all rights, obligations, and legal interests.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal successor,merger</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-87d8fe2bdf778bad13a2e66311b71743</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853442</data>
