  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Phó Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Vice Chairman of the Trung tâm trọng tài is a member of the management board of the organization.</data>
  <data key="d9">appointment,management</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Tổng thư ký Trung tâm trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The General Secretary of the Trung tâm trọng tài is appointed by the Chairman and is part of the management board.</data>
  <data key="d9">appointment,management</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Trọng tài viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Trung tâm trọng tài maintains a list of arbitrators and appoints them to resolve disputes.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration,roster</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Bộ Tư pháp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Trung tâm trọng tài sends the list of arbitrators to the Ministry of Justice for publication.</data>
  <data key="d9">publication,reporting</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Sở Tư pháp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Trung tâm trọng tài submits annual reports to the Provincial Department of Justice.</data>
  <data key="d9">annual report,reporting</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Đơn khởi kiện">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Trung tâm trọng tài receives the complaint filed by the plaintiff to initiate arbitration proceedings.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung tâm trọng tài is responsible for managing and sending copies of the Đơn khởi kiện to the defendant within 10 days of receiving it.</data>
  <data key="d9">dispute resolution,document management,initiation,legal process</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853827</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Thỏa thuận trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Trung tâm trọng tài requires the arbitration agreement to accompany the complaint for initiating arbitration proceedings.</data>
  <data key="d9">dispute resolution,initiation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Đиều 30">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đиều 30 details the requirements for the complaint and accompanying documents in arbitration proceedings at the Trung tâm trọng tài.</data>
  <data key="d9">complaint requirements</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Đиều 31">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đиều 31 defines the starting point of arbitration proceedings at the Trung tâm trọng tài.</data>
  <data key="d9">starting point</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-051c6a2f2eb7c0bc6325f96ce33195d9</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853495</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Hội đồng trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trung tâm trọng tài manages arbitration proceedings and oversees the work of Hội đồng trọng tài.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung tâm trọng tài is an arbitration center that may be chosen by the parties to resolve disputes, and its decisions are reviewed by Hội đồng trọng tài.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung tâm trọng tài oversees the operations of the Hội đồng trọng tài in the arbitration process.&lt;SEP&gt;Trung tâm trọng tài is where disputes are resolved, and Hội đồng trọng tài decides on the change of an Arbitrator.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration,arbitration center,arbitration proceedings,decision-making,dispute resolution,management,oversight</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ebb1fe9cf67432030a08132511452a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-803a122f8a9fdbd56cf33836597c6521&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773854050</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Ngôn ngữ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The language used in arbitration proceedings is determined by Trung tâm trọng tài based on the presence or absence of foreign elements in the dispute.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration proceedings,language use</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853684</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Gửi thông báo và trình tự gửi thông báo">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Gửi thông báo và trình tự gửi thông báo is the method for sending notifications and the procedure for doing so in arbitration proceedings, managed by Trung tâm trọng tài.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration proceedings,notification method</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-61550f768622f38a6cce8665b746a20a</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853684</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Bản tự bảo vệ">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trung tâm trọng tài is responsible for receiving the Bản tự bảo vệ from the defendant within 30 days of receiving the Đơn khởi kiện.</data>
  <data key="d9">document submission,legal process</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853828</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Trọng tài vụ việc">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trọng tài vụ việc is a method of resolving disputes that can be managed by the Trung tâm trọng tài.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration process,dispute resolution</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853828</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Quy tắc tố tụng trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trung tâm trọng tài follows the Quy tắc tố tụng trọng tài to manage arbitration proceedings and document submission.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration management,procedural rules</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853828</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Toà án">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Toà án notifies the arbitration center about the request to annul an arbitration award.</data>
  <data key="d9">communication,notification</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-967ef50a189d7b94846c22abc99c1f09</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853867</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Điều 64">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trung tâm trọng tài is responsible for storing arbitration case files.&lt;SEP&gt;Đиều 64 outlines the rules for storing arbitration case files.</data>
  <data key="d9">case file storage,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-105aefb96d31bdf83eb8694998c59506</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853887</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Thời hạn 05 năm">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trung tâm trọng tài is responsible for storing arbitration case files for the 5-year period.</data>
  <data key="d9">responsibility,storage period</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-105aefb96d31bdf83eb8694998c59506</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853887</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Trọng tài viên duy nhất">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The chairperson of the arbitration center appoints a single arbitrator if the parties cannot agree within 30 days.</data>
  <data key="d9">appointment,arbitration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d4b1824dac8b182589cb4f697dad3e4f</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853974</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Trọng tài viên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài decides on the change of an Trọng tài viên if the Arbitration Board has not been established.</data>
  <data key="d9">change,decision-making</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773854050</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài" target="Điều 42">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Điều 42 specifies the role of Chủ tịch Trung tâm trọng tài in deciding the change of Trọng tài viên.</data>
  <data key="d9">decision-making,regulation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773854050</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trọng tài viên" target="Các bên tranh chấp">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trọng tài viên resolves disputes between the parties involved, adhering to their agreements and legal principles.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration,dispute resolution</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853578</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trọng tài viên" target="Hội đồng trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trọng tài viên is part of the arbitration panel, Hội đồng trọng tài, which makes decisions on disputes.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration panel,decision-making</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-30428dad2333a793ae10d4b854fbe88d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853578</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trọng tài viên" target="Hiệp hội Trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hiệp hội Trọng tài is a professional association for arbitrators.</data>
  <data key="d9">membership,professional association</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-1881019a36e766412bad88d7a1e3d088</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853768</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trọng tài viên" target="Trung tâm Trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trung tâm Trọng tài organizes and coordinates dispute resolution through arbitration involving arbitrators.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration,dispute resolution</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-1881019a36e766412bad88d7a1e3d088</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853768</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trọng tài viên" target="Phí trọng tài">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trọng tài viên receives a portion of the Phí trọng tài for their services.</data>
  <data key="d9">arbitration fees,compensation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ed4ad4b6755ec955ac613350fdb8b3a5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853827</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Trọng tài viên" target="Các bên">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Trọng tài viên resolves disputes and must notify the parties of any circumstances that may affect their impartiality.</data>
  <data key="d9">dispute resolution,notification</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4ad943b03a3a1bf95a1e1d6e04f2b581</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773854050</data>
