</edge>
<edge source="Hội đồng trọng tài" target="Toà án">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Toà án notifies the arbitration panel about the request to annul an arbitration award.&lt;SEP&gt;Toà án must transfer the collected evidence to Hội đồng trọng tài within the specified time frame.&lt;SEP&gt;Hội đồng trọng tài can request Toà án to collect evidence when they cannot do so themselves.</data>
  <data key="d9">communication,evidence collection,evidence transfer,legal authority,legal requirement,notification</data>
