  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Đơn yêu cầu huỷ phán quyết trọng tài is submitted to Toà án to request the annulment of an arbitration decision.&lt;SEP&gt;Toà án examines the request to annul an arbitration award.</data>
