<edge source="Decision to Dissolve the Business" target="Business">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The decision to dissolve the business triggers a series of prohibited activities that the business must not undertake, including the prohibition of certain financial and contractual actions.</data>
  <data key="d9">dissolution trigger,prohibited activities</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Decision to Dissolve the Business" target="Business Manager">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The business manager is responsible for ensuring compliance with the prohibited activities after the decision to dissolve the business, including the prohibition of certain financial and contractual actions.</data>
  <data key="d9">prohibited activities,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853691</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Business Dissolution Filing" target="Business Registration Authority">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Business Registration Authority is responsible for receiving and processing the business dissolution filing, ensuring compliance with legal requirements.</data>
  <data key="d9">processing,registration</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Business" target="Prohibited Activities">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The business is strictly forbidden from undertaking the prohibited activities after the dissolution decision, including the prohibition of certain financial and contractual actions.</data>
  <data key="d9">dissolution,forbidden actions</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853691</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Business Manager" target="Civil Liability">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The business manager is responsible for settling unpaid wages, taxes, and debts within five years of the business dissolution filing, as well as the prohibition of certain actions post-dissolution.</data>
  <data key="d9">financial responsibility,legal obligation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853691</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Business Manager" target="Criminal Liability">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The business manager may face criminal liability for violating the prohibited activities post-dissolution decision, including financial penalties and criminal prosecution.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal consequence,prohibited activities</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853691</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Business Manager" target="Prohibited Activities">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The business manager is strictly forbidden from undertaking the prohibited activities after the dissolution decision, including the prohibition of certain financial and contractual actions.</data>
  <data key="d9">dissolution,forbidden actions</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853691</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Prohibited Activities" target="Financial Penalties">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Financial penalties may be imposed on individuals who violate the prohibited activities post-dissolution decision, as a result of their actions.</data>
  <data key="d9">penalty,violation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853690</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Prohibited Activities" target="Criminal Prosecution">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Criminal prosecution may be initiated against individuals who violate the prohibited activities post-dissolution decision and cause damage, leading to potential criminal consequences.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal action,violation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-92c3918ef1335574a5247e5d95f80ab7</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773853691</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
