  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The chief judge of the competent court assigns a judge to appoint an arbitrator within 7 days of receiving a request.&lt;SEP&gt;Chánh án Tòa án có thẩm quyền assigns a Thẩm phán to designate an Arbitrator.</data>
