  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Chánh Án Tòa Án assigns a Thẩm Phán to examine and resolve requests for emergency measures.&lt;SEP&gt;Chánh Án Tòa Án assigns a Thẩm Phán to examine the registration of an arbitration decision.</data>
  <data key="d9">assignment,examination,registration</data>
